Name: Beko Italia
Company description: Beko Italia is a leading provider of innovative home appliances, specializing in energy-efficient solutions that enhance everyday living. As a subsidiary of Beko, which operates globally with a strong presence in 57 countries, Beko Italia focuses on delivering high-quality products such as refrigerators, washing machines, and kitchen appliances that incorporate advanced technologies like HarvestFresh™ to preserve the nutritional value of food. The company's mission is to create a more livable planet through sustainable practices and cutting-edge technology, while its vision emphasizes improving the quality of life for consumers. Beko Italia serves a diverse clientele, including families and environmentally conscious consumers, and partners with various retailers to ensure accessibility to its products. With a commitment to sustainability, Beko Italia aims to lead the market in eco-friendly innovations, contributing to a healthier lifestyle for its customers.

Name: Casa Mia Srl
Company description: "Casa Mia Srl" è una catena di punti vendita specializzati in tende e tendoni, tappeti d’arredamento, da bagno, stuoie per cucina, zerbini, cuscini e coordinati e tutti gli arredamenti tessili per la casa. Fin dal primo negozio pilota, unico nel suo genere (aperto nel Centro Commerciale Panorama di Settimo Torinese nel Marzo 1993) l’iniziativa si conferma vincente. Conclusa la fase di start-up e d’ottimizzazione della formula, la catena registra una crescita regolare raggiungendo 35 punti vendita in Piemonte, Lombardia, Liguria, Toscana e Veneto. Da aprile 2021 Casa Mia ha anche un e-commerce, visitalo ora www.casamiasrl.shop Perché noi crediamo che ogni cosa che facciamo debba essere fatta con il CUORE.

Name: Hansgrohe Group
Company description: The Hansgrohe Group, headquartered in Schiltach, Germany, has been a leader in innovation, design, and quality within the bath and kitchen industry since its founding in 1901. Operating under two prominent brands, AXOR and hansgrohe, the company specializes in producing high-quality faucets, showerheads, and shower systems that offer holistic bathroom experiences, seamlessly blending functionality with aesthetic appeal. Hansgrohe is committed to sustainability, exemplified by its "ECO 2030" initiative, which aims to equip all water-bearing products with water-saving technologies by 2030, reflecting its dedication to responsible resource management and environmental stewardship. The company serves a diverse clientele, including luxury hotels, spas, and private residences, and has established a robust global presence, operating in over 145 countries with 35 subsidiaries and 22 sales offices. Hansgrohe's innovative partnerships, such as its collaboration with Hydraloop for gray water recycling solutions, further enhance its position as a pioneer in sustainable water management technologies. With a workforce of approximately 5,600 employees, the Hansgrohe Group continues to set the standard for quality and sustainability in the global sanitation industry. Renowned for its pioneering products, Hansgrohe introduced the first handheld shower with multiple spray types and the first pullout kitchen faucet, showcasing its commitment to innovation. The company's dedication to quality and sustainability has earned it numerous awards, solidifying its reputation as a trusted partner in the sanitary industry. Through its focus on design excellence and eco-friendly practices, Hansgrohe aims to create products that not only enhance the user experience but also contribute positively to the environment.

Name: Fiskars Group
Company description: Fiskars Group, established in 1649, is a leading global company renowned for its innovative consumer products, particularly in the areas of gardening, cooking, and crafting. With a mission to enhance everyday life through design and functionality, Fiskars aims to create sustainable solutions that resonate with consumers worldwide. The company operates through two main business areas: BA Vita, which focuses on premium and luxury products in tableware, drinkware, jewelry, and interior design, and BA Fiskars, which specializes in gardening, outdoor, and kitchen products. Fiskars Group serves a diverse clientele, including individual consumers, retailers, and professional users, and partners with various stakeholders to drive growth and innovation. With a strong commitment to sustainability, Fiskars Group aims to minimize its environmental impact through responsible sourcing and manufacturing practices. The company targets markets that value quality and functionality, ensuring that its products not only meet high standards but also contribute positively to the environment. Fiskars Group's vision emphasizes creativity, quality, and a deep understanding of customer needs, positioning it as a leader in the consumer goods industry. The company operates in over 100 countries and employs nearly 7,000 people, reflecting its global reach and influence. Fiskars Group reported global net sales of EUR 1.2 billion in 2024, showcasing its robust market presence. Through its iconic brands, including Fiskars, Georg Jensen, Iittala, and Royal Copenhagen, the company emphasizes innovation and craftsmanship, aiming to make everyday life extraordinary for its customers. By fostering strong partnerships and focusing on direct-to-consumer sales through its extensive network of stores and e-commerce platforms, Fiskars Group continues to enhance its product offerings and expand its market reach.

Name: POCO Einrichtungsmärkte GmbH
Company description: POCO – das ist Schönes Wohnen für weniger Geld. Preisbewusste Kunden finden in den gelben Einrichtungsmärkten ein umfassendes Sortiment von Möbeln und Küchen über Haushaltswaren, Heimtextilien, Farben, Tapeten, Teppichböden, Teppichen und Elektroartikeln bis hin zu Geschenkartikeln. Produkte namhafter Markenhersteller sind genauso im Angebot wie besonders günstige, exklusiv für POCO hergestellte Eigenmarken. Kunden schätzen neben dem exzellenten Preis-Leistungs-Verhältnis besonders den kompetenten Service im Markt vor Ort. In deutschlandweit über 100 Märkten sind aktuell mehr als 7.000 Mitarbeiter tätig. Mit einem Umsatzvolumen von 1,2 Milliarden Euro im Jahr 2012 zählt das Unternehmen zu den großen deutschen Anbietern im Mitnahmebereich und steuert einen konsequenten Wachstumskurs. Jährlich sind rund 6 Neueröffnungen geplant. Die POCO Service AG übernimmt im Konzern sämtliche Verwaltungsaufgaben und stellt somit die Zentrale an den Standort Bergkamen und Hardegsen dar.

Name: NOBIA PRODUCTION SWEDEN AB
Company description: Nobia Production Sweden AB is a leading kitchen specialist in Europe, renowned for its commitment to designing and manufacturing high-quality, sustainable kitchen solutions. The company's mission is to enhance everyday living through innovative and functional kitchen designs, while its vision emphasizes long-term value creation and environmental stewardship. Nobia operates across five countries—Sweden, Norway, Denmark, Finland, and the UK—offering a diverse range of kitchen brands, including Marbodal, HTH, and Magnet, which cater to individual consumers, tradespeople, and project customers alike.  Nobia prioritizes sustainability in its operations, focusing on responsible sourcing of materials, including the use of recycled wood and ensuring that virgin wood comes from certified sustainable forests. The company aims to minimize its environmental impact in alignment with the Paris Agreement, with strategic objectives that include reducing greenhouse gas emissions and promoting a circular economy. Nobia serves a diverse clientele, including homeowners, contractors, and property developers, and collaborates with various partners, such as suppliers and academic institutions, to enhance its sustainability initiatives. With a robust distribution network and economies of scale, Nobia is well-positioned to meet the growing demand for environmentally friendly kitchen solutions while continuously improving operational efficiency and profitability. The company actively engages in initiatives that align with international ethical guidelines, ensuring compliance with human rights and environmental standards. Nobia's commitment to innovation and sustainability is reflected in its advanced production facilities and strategic initiatives aimed at strengthening its market position and driving profitable growth. Through its dedication to quality craftsmanship and customer satisfaction, Nobia Production Sweden AB aims to lead the kitchen industry in both design and sustainability.

Name: Arabesque
Company description: ARABESQUE is the largest and most diversified regional wholesale distributor of building construction and finishing materials with predominant market presence in Romania, Ukraine, Bulgaria, Serbia and Moldavia. A leading provider of integrated supply services. with annual sales (2009) of approximately €550 million euros, ARABESQUE employs more than 5,000 people, deploys over 900 trucks, maintains relationships with over 2,000 suppliers, and serves more than 75,000 customers in 5 countries. The group offers complete portfolio of building construction and finishing materials (over 30,000 items), from heavyweight (masonry blocks, metallurgical products, concrete mixers etc.), roof systems (waterproofing, metal and concrete or ceramic tiles, bituminous shingles, corrugates plates, etc.), interior decoration products (paints, grouts, binders, putties, gypsum board systems, thermal insulations, coffered roofs, wood floorings, wall panels, doors etc.), sanitary and thermal installations, electric equipments, lighting fixtures, down to furniture supplies (chipboards, ironware, table and kitchen tops, stratified wood etc.).  Local and regional customers benefit from the a broad product catalog with competitive pricing and our support-services such as  * technical counseling *  structural steel shaping and cutting *  coloring of paints and decorative plasters *  chipboard panels cutting and edging.  *  over 900 specialized trucks for on-site delivers.

Name: NEOLITH
Company description: Neolith is a pioneering company specializing in the production of sintered stone surfaces, crafted from 100% natural raw materials. As a leader in architectural surfaces, Neolith aims to redefine the standards of design and sustainability in the industry, offering versatile applications for kitchens, bathrooms, facades, flooring, and even furniture. The company's mission is to provide innovative, high-quality surfaces that combine aesthetic beauty with superior technical performance, ensuring durability and hygiene. Neolith's products are favored by architects, designers, and consumers alike, thanks to their elegant designs inspired by natural elements and their commitment to sustainability, with many models containing up to 98% recycled materials. The brand has established a strong presence in global markets, collaborating with professionals and partners across Europe, North America, Asia, and beyond, while continuously pushing the boundaries of innovation in surface design.

Name: Sklepy Komfort S.A.
Company description: Sklepy Komfort S.A. is a leading retailer in Poland specializing in home improvement and interior design products, particularly focusing on bathroom and kitchen furnishings. The company operates under the brand Senti, which offers a unique line of decorative ceramics that combine exceptional design, high quality, and functionality, catering to the needs of discerning customers. With over 160 stores across the country, Sklepy Komfort aims to provide an unparalleled shopping experience, emphasizing customer satisfaction through personalized service and a diverse product range. The company's mission is to deliver high-quality products at competitive prices, ensuring that every customer can find stylish solutions for their homes. By leveraging decades of experience and a deep understanding of customer preferences, Sklepy Komfort continues to innovate and expand its offerings, making it a trusted partner for homeowners and interior designers alike.

Name: Casa International
Company description: CASA is an international chain of contemporary interior decoration shops, with a total of more than 500 stores, subsidiaries and franchisees. Objects for interior decoration, giftware, household and bath products, textiles and small items of furniture make up  the range offered by CASA.  CASA stands for cosy living. Our CASA shops will inspire you and offer great ideas for seasonable changes in your living and kitchen corners. We invite you to visit our website "www.casashops.com" or a CASA shop in your neighbourhood for an exciting shopping and decoration experience.

Name: Hülsta-werke Hüls GmbH & Co. KG
Company description: Hülsta-werke Hüls GmbH & Co. KG is a renowned German furniture manufacturer specializing in high-quality, stylish furniture for living, sleeping, and dining spaces. With a commitment to excellence, the company emphasizes meticulous craftsmanship, timeless design, and sustainability in its products, which are well-regarded for their durability and aesthetic appeal. Hülsta's mission is to create innovative and functional furniture solutions that enhance everyday living, while its vision focuses on expanding its product range to include comprehensive home furnishing options, such as kitchens. The company caters to a diverse clientele, including individual consumers and interior designers, and collaborates with various retail partners to deliver customized solutions that meet the unique needs of its customers. Through its ongoing dedication to quality and design, Hülsta aims to inspire and elevate the living experiences of its customers.

Name: Globus ČR V.o.s.
Company description: Globus dnes Proč nás chcete... Dáváme vám to nejlepší Prodáváme jen prověřenou kvalitu – ovšem za nejnižší možnou cenu. Naší chloubou je až neuvěřitelná šíře sortimentu. Každý den si u nás můžete vybírat z 15 000 druhů potravinářského a 45 000 druhů nepotravinářského zboží. V prodejnách Baumarkt na vás čeká 50 000 výrobků pro kutily, zahrádkáře a domácnost. Čerstvost je pro nás nade vše! Proto máme své řeznictví, uzenářskou výrobu i pekárnu. Proto u nás zelenina a ovoce vypadají jako právě utržené. A v restauracích Globus vaříme každý den ta nejlepší jídla české i světové kuchyně. Každý hypermarket, kromě hypermarketu v Havířově, provozuje vlastní čerpací stanici s výhodnými cenami pohonných hmot. U nás máte záruky rychlého zaplacení, možnosti vrátit zboží, nejnižších cen, čerstvosti a nevyčerpatelné nabídky. Možná o nich ani nevíte, protože je nepotřebujete. Pokud byste je však náhodou potřebovali, nepochybně je oceníte.

Name: Happy Casa Store
Company description: Happy Casa Store is an innovative online retailer specializing in a diverse array of home goods and furnishings, including kitchen appliances, tableware, furniture, and outdoor products. The company's mission is to enhance the living experience of its customers by providing high-quality, stylish, and affordable products that improve the comfort and aesthetics of their homes. With a strong emphasis on customer satisfaction, Happy Casa Store strives to create a seamless shopping experience through its user-friendly e-commerce platform, which offers secure payment options and reliable delivery services. The target market for Happy Casa Store includes homeowners and renters, particularly families and individuals seeking practical yet elegant solutions for their living spaces. By partnering with reputable brands, such as Bestway, the company ensures a diverse selection of products that cater to various tastes and preferences. Happy Casa Store is committed to delivering exceptional value and service, making it a go-to destination for home essentials. In addition to its extensive product offerings, Happy Casa Store emphasizes customer support, providing assistance through various channels to help shoppers navigate their purchasing journey. The company also offers flexible payment options, including the ability to split payments into three interest-free installments through Scalapay, making home shopping more accessible and enjoyable. Overall, Happy Casa Store aims to be a trusted resource for those looking to furnish or decorate their homes affordably and conveniently, while prioritizing quality and style in every product.

Name: KLUDI
Company description: KLUDI is a renowned German company specializing in high-quality bathroom and kitchen fittings, combining nearly a century of engineering expertise with innovative design. The company's mission is to set industry standards through exceptional craftsmanship and forward-thinking solutions, as evidenced by numerous accolades, including the PLUS X Award for Best Brand and the German Design Award Special. KLUDI's products are designed to enhance modern living spaces, appealing to a diverse clientele that includes architects, interior designers, and homeowners seeking elegance and functionality. With a commitment to sustainability and a strong culture of innovation, KLUDI partners with a global network of premium retailers to deliver cutting-edge solutions that prioritize both aesthetics and environmental responsibility.

Name: CRISTINA Rubinetterie
Company description: CRISTINA Rubinetterie is a leading Italian manufacturer renowned for its high-quality kitchen and bathroom fixtures, including taps and accessories tailored for both residential and commercial applications. With over 70 years of experience, the company is dedicated to sustainability and innovation, focusing on energy-efficient products that minimize environmental impact. CRISTINA's mission is to enhance domestic comfort through stylish and functional designs while upholding the values of Italian craftsmanship and quality. The company serves a diverse clientele, including homeowners, architects, interior designers, and contractors, and collaborates with various partners in the construction and design sectors to promote responsible manufacturing practices. Targeting both local and international markets, CRISTINA aims to meet the evolving needs of consumers who value eco-friendly solutions. The company emphasizes optimizing water usage in its production processes, implementing systems that allow for the use of non-potable water and recovering water from cutting processes. This commitment to environmental responsibility is further reflected in its adherence to the European Green Deal and the UN 2030 Agenda. CRISTINA Rubinetterie prioritizes customer satisfaction by ensuring the health and safety of end users through the use of non-harmful materials and rigorous quality assessments. With four production units in the Novara area, CRISTINA maintains high standards of quality and efficiency, positioning itself as a key player in the global bathroom fixtures market. The company actively supports local suppliers to foster economic growth and community engagement, while also investing in the development of its workforce to ensure a skilled and motivated team. By combining innovative designs with advanced technology, CRISTINA Rubinetterie continues to lead the way in creating efficient and environmentally conscious plumbing solutions that enhance the quality of life for its customers.

Name: Ballingslöv AB
Company description: Ballingslöv AB är en av landets ledande tillverkare av inredningar för kök, badrum och förvaring.  Företaget med knappt 360 anställda är beläget i Ballingslöv, ca en mil norr om Hässleholm, i Skåne. Ballingslöv AB ingår i koncernen Ballingslöv International AB. I nästan nittio år har vi i fabriken i Ballingslöv fortsatt att bygga svenska kök efter tidens behov och önskemål. Vi har sett trender komma och gå, och vi har konsekvent hållit fast vid vår tanke att kvalitet och erfarenhet gör det möjligt att bana ny mark. Vi har behållit det vi vet fungerar, men är alltid nyfikna på nya lösningar. Vi bygger kök, bad och förvaring med samma Ballingslövsanda nu som då. Idag talar vi gärna om Var Dags Glädje. För det är just vad vi tycker att ett bra kök och en bra arbetsplats skall vara, både nu och i framtiden: en källa till vardagsglädje. Vardagsglädje.

Name: Poggenpohl
Company description: Poggenpohl is one of the oldest and most renowned kitchen brands globally, established in 1892 and recognized as a pioneer in modern kitchen design. The company specializes in creating luxurious kitchen architecture, seamlessly blending architectural thinking with innovative design, exceptional craftsmanship, and technical precision. With its headquarters and manufacturing facility located in Herford, Germany, Poggenpohl ensures the highest quality and distinctiveness in its products. The brand operates through an extensive international network of its own studios and authorized partners, distributing its kitchens in over 70 countries worldwide. Poggenpohl's mission is to transform kitchen spaces into unique, functional, and aesthetically pleasing environments, catering to discerning clients who value luxury and design excellence. The company is committed to fostering innovation and sustainability, making it a leader in the luxury kitchen market.

Name: Kvik A/S
Company description: Kvik has been delivering high quality Danish design kitchens, baths and wardrobes at surprisingly low prices since 1983. We are a franchise concept with more than 180+ franchise-owned and operated stores in 13 countries. We are part of Ballingslöv International AB, one of the leading players within kitchen, bath and wardrobe in Europe. We make Danish design kitchens with good intentions and as many high quality recycled materials as possible.

Name: FRoSTA AG
Company description: FRoSTA AG is one of Europe’s leading manufacturers of innovative, nutritious frozen food of the highest quality. What we want more than anything is that our customers are always delighted with our products. We take the utmost care to ensure that all our products are of the highest quality and always safe. More than 1,600 people work for FRoSTA AG in eight countries. We produce at three plants in Germany and one in Poland. Since 2003 we are following a unique path of transparency and sustainability: all of our  FRoSTA  products are 100% free of  food additives like taste enhancers, colorings, stabilizers, and aromas. We use only the purest, best tasting and sustainable ingredients and process them by focusing on traditional kitchen techniques and utmost transparency for the consumer. Our portfolio includes  frozen fish, vegetables, herbs and ready meals in Germany, Poland, Austria, Italy, Hungary, Romania and Czech Republic. FRoSTA products are available from supermarkets.  In April 2013, FRoSTA was the first frozen food brand to publish on the Internet the countries of origin of each batch of our ingredients. Since autumn 2015, we are printing this information directly on the product packaging. FRoSTA is the fastest growing frozen food brand  in Germany and market leader in fish in Poland. We are expanding our FRoSTA assortment in  Italy,  Austria, Switzerland, Hungary, Rumania and Czech Republic.  Find out more about  FRoSTA  on www.frosta.de and in the FRoSTA Blog (www.frostablog.de), which happens to be the first of its kind for a food brand in Germany. FRoSTA AG is also a specialist production partner in the development and production of high-quality customer brands for the European retail and wholesale sectors.

Name: ArredissimA
Company description: ArredissimA is a prominent Italian furniture company that specializes in providing tailored home furnishing solutions for various living spaces, including kitchens, living rooms, and bedrooms. The company prides itself on its commitment to quality and customer satisfaction, which is reflected in its partnership with beloved Italian television icon Gerry Scotti, who serves as a brand ambassador. ArredissimA aims to create a welcoming and engaging shopping experience, offering personalized consultations to help clients design their dream homes. With a diverse range of products that cater to both classic and modern tastes, the company targets a wide audience, from families to young professionals seeking stylish and functional furniture. Through its showrooms and online presence, ArredissimA continues to innovate and expand its offerings, ensuring that every customer finds the perfect pieces to enhance their living environment.

Name: Brico Depot Romania
Company description: Brico Dépôt România înseamnă 31 de magazine în 24 de orașe și peste 2.200 de colegi, care lucrează zi de zi pentru a oferi clienților cea mai bună experiență. Totodată, ei fac din Brico un mediu de lucru plăcut. Și tot ei sunt motivul pentru care, în 2025, suntem, pentru al treilea an consecutiv, singurul retailer din domeniul amenajării locuinței care a primit certificarea Top Employer, fiind recunoscuți, printre altele, pentru programele noastre excelente de onboarding și dezvoltare. Misiunea noastră este ca amenajarea locuinței să devină accesibilă tuturor, deoarece credem că toată lumea trebuie să aibă o locuință în care să se simtă bine. Punem la dispoziția clienților produse mai bune, la prețuri mici în magazinele noastre și online, pe bricodepot.ro, dar și servicii precum montaj, livrare rapidă sau serviciul de design 3D pentru bucătării. Le oferim sfaturi potrivite, pentru ca toate proiectele lor să devină realitate, indiferent de mărime și complexitate. Dacă vrei să îți construiești și tu o carieră alături de noi, aplică la rolurile disponibile și #HaiSaFimBricolegi.

Name: Scavolini S.p.A.
Company description: Scavolini S.p.A. is a renowned Italian company specializing in the design and manufacturing of high-quality kitchen and bathroom furniture. Established in 1961, Scavolini has built a reputation for creating innovative and stylish solutions that enhance the functionality and aesthetics of living spaces. The company's mission is to provide customers with personalized and sustainable products that reflect their unique tastes and lifestyles, ensuring that each piece is crafted with precision and care. Scavolini collaborates with a network of skilled artisans and designers, which allows it to offer a diverse range of customizable options tailored to individual preferences. Targeting both residential and commercial markets, Scavolini serves a wide clientele that includes homeowners, architects, and interior designers. The company maintains a strong presence in international markets, appealing to consumers who value quality craftsmanship and contemporary design. Scavolini's vision emphasizes leadership in design excellence and sustainability, as it continuously integrates cutting-edge technology and eco-friendly practices into its production processes. With a focus on customer satisfaction, Scavolini aims to transform everyday environments into extraordinary spaces, making it a preferred choice for those seeking elegance and practicality in their home furnishings. The brand is recognized for its commitment to quality and innovation, consistently setting trends in the furniture industry while enhancing the quality of life for its customers. Through its dedication to craftsmanship and design, Scavolini envisions a future where every home reflects the individuality and lifestyle of its inhabitants.

Name: Poliform
Company description: Poliform is a prestigious Italian company established in 1970, renowned for its high-quality furniture and interior design solutions. Located near Lake Como, the firm specializes in creating custom-made systems and furnishings that blend functionality with contemporary aesthetics, including kitchens, wardrobes, sofas, and various complementary pieces. With a strong commitment to sustainability and innovation, Poliform integrates advanced technology with artisanal craftsmanship, ensuring that each product not only meets aesthetic and functional needs but also contributes positively to the environment. The company's mission is to enhance the quality of life for its clients by providing elegant and durable furnishings while promoting a circular economy and minimizing environmental impact. Poliform operates under a "Made in Italy" philosophy, emphasizing the importance of local suppliers and sustainable materials, with 97% of its suppliers based in Italy. The company serves a diverse clientele, including individual homeowners, architects, interior designers, and large-scale contractors, and is represented in over 90 countries through a network of authorized dealers and flagship stores. Poliform's vision focuses on promoting the Made in Italy brand and enhancing community well-being through responsible business practices.  The firm actively engages in social initiatives, supporting organizations such as UNICEF and the Umberto Veronesi Foundation, and promotes wellness among its employees. With a strong international presence and collaborations with leading designers and architects, Poliform continues to redefine modern living, offering tailored solutions for both residential and commercial markets. Through its commitment to quality, innovation, and sustainability, Poliform aims to inspire and elevate the everyday living experience for its customers.

Name: Hôma
HQ Location: Portugal, Porto, Vila Nova De Gaia
Company description: Seja bem-vindo, a hôma é sua. Somos especialistas em Happy Home Living. Na hôma encontra tudo o que a sua casa precisa para ter hôma casa ao seu estilo: Decoração, Têxtil, Kids, Cozinha, Arrumação, Banho, Ar Livre.  Somos uma marca democrática, apaixonada pelo design e especialista em decoração e sorrisos.  Na hôma queremos ajudá-lo a fazer da sua casa o lugar mais feliz do mundo com propostas cheias de inspiração, funcionalidade e novidades.  Follow us, we´re going hôma!

Name: Paini SpA Rubinetterie
Company description: Dal 1954 Paini propone un’ampia gamma di rubinetteria: monocomando, arredobagno e cantiere, per ambienti da cucina, bagno e doccia. L’attuale produzione annua è di circa 4 milioni di pezzi. Il ciclo produttivo prevede l’utilizzo esclusivo di materie prime di qualità superiore, rispondenti alle rigorose norme UNI-CEE.  Since 1954. Paini offers a wide range of taps - mixers, bathroom accessorieses and ship-building industry, kitchen, bath and shower associated products. We proudly produce 4 million pieces per annum. The production cycle provides the usage of high quality raw materials only, in conformity with the strict UNI-CEE standards.

Name: ARAN World
HQ Location: Italy, Te, Atri, Zona Industriale Frazione Casoli, 64032
Company description: ARAN World is the Italian kitchen export leader, and one of the best Italian companies for design, production and distribution of kitchens, office furniture and wardrobes. Aran World è leader in Italia nelle esportazioni di cucine e tra le prime aziende italiane in progettazione, produzione e distribuzione di cucine, mobili per ufficio e armadi.

Name: Mobilya
Company description: Ceo- Dott. Cantone Luciano Il marchio registrato che da oltre 40 anni identifica una delle più grandi società operanti nel settore del mobile, e non solo. Mobilya non è solo sinonimo di mobili di qualità, ma anche di complementi d’arredo, elementi indispensabili per rendere ancora più accogliente la tua casa. Il punto di forza di Mobilya è proprio l’offerta che mette a Tua disposizione. La selezione dei migliori produttori locali e nazionali Ti assicura la possibilità di trovare la soluzione di arredamento più vantaggiosa per arredare la casa. Cucine classiche e moderne, Sale da pranzo, Camere da letto, Pareti componibili, Armadi, Credenze, Camerette, un mondo di divani, divaniletto e salotti e tante soluzioni personalizzate per gli angoli relax della Tua casa: questo è il mondo Mobilya. La missione di Mobilya è “essere il mobilificio punto di riferimento per le famiglie del Centro e Sud Italia”. L’Azienda si propone di raggiungere i suoi obiettivi attraverso una costante attenzione alle esigenze del cliente, per soddisfarlo e fornirgli il miglior servizio possibile, ed uno sguardo attento al mercato, per essere sempre al passo con i tempi. E’ per questi motivi che i valori che ispirano l’operato di Mobilya e la guidano verso il raggiungimento della mission aziendale sono capisaldi condivisi da tutta l’organizzazione: costante ricerca della qualità, dinamicità e ricerca, basate sulla conoscenza ed il rispetto di tutte le esigenze.

Name: Reform
Company description: Born in Copenhagen, we create kitchen and storage solutions that make everyday life beautifully better.   Together with some of the world’s best designers and architects, we offer collections that blend Scandinavian simplicity with global ideas. Each design is driven by curiosity and crafted to bring character and cohesion to your home.  We work with trusted materials and partners, and guide you from first sketch to final installation. So your solutions look good, work well, and wear beautifully.

Name: Bribus B.V.
Company description: Bribus B.V. is a forward-thinking kitchen solutions provider based in the Netherlands, dedicated to making kitchens affordable while prioritizing both people and the environment. The company specializes in delivering comprehensive kitchen solutions tailored to fit within clients' budgets, achieved through continuous innovation in production, assembly processes, and material usage. With a standardized range of cabinets, Bribus creates high-quality kitchens that meet the evolving needs of residents today and in the future. Operating from four locations, including its headquarters and factory in Dinxperlo, as well as service points in Diemen, Kampen, and Rotterdam, Bribus manages complete projects across the country. The company is committed to fostering partnerships and collaborations that enhance its offerings, while its team of over 350 professionals brings diverse expertise to the table, ensuring a balanced work environment and a focus on customer satisfaction.

Name: IMAB Group SpA
HQ Location: Italy, Fermignano Pesaro Urbino, 92 Via L. Falasconi, 61033
Company description: IMAB Group is a leading global manufacturing Company tightly connected to its roots made of people who share a bold dream: design and manufacture furniture, offer services and projects that makes consumers enjoy their homes and be happy (Vision). Founded in 1968 by Mr. Antonio Bruscoli to supply semi-finished product, the company will eventually develop to furniture maker thanks to the successful partnership between the manufacturing vision of son Mr.Gianfranco Bruscoli and the brilliant sales management skills of Mr. Giuseppe Rossi.  Today Imab group spa is listed on the top 10 furniture manufacturers in Italy with more than 700 workers employed thorough 10 plants and 140M in yearly sales  All wide range of production that includes bedrooms, kitchens, living room is manufactured in the famous Montefeltro furniture district for a 100% genuine “Made in Italy” label that plays an import role to support the plans of expansions to strategic foreign markets.   Very conscious to environmental issues and sensitive to balance fair decisions between employees needs and company’s priorities.   Alberto, Gianfranco son, started his career at Imab in 2001 to become Marketing Director. One of Alberto’s main contributions was “pensarecasa”; a project aimed to increase the retail value of Imab total look line-up. Beside its manufacturing role Imab group is also recognized for its social commitment with local schools, daycare, no-profit associations, hospitals and the people that everyday take part to Imab Success.

Name: Arredo3
Company description: Arredo3 is a leading company specializing in the design and production of high-quality furniture solutions, particularly for residential contract projects. With a strong focus on aesthetics, functionality, and attention to detail, Arredo3 offers a comprehensive range of products that include kitchens, living areas, bathrooms, and laundry spaces, all customizable to meet specific client needs. The company prides itself on its efficient service, from quick and clear quotations to ongoing project support, ensuring timely deliveries and high reliability, certified by its A.E.O. status. Arredo3 collaborates closely with architects, designers, and contractors, providing tailored solutions that cater to both individual and large-scale requirements. With over 600 finishes and sustainable options, the company aims to create harmonious living environments that reflect the unique tastes of its clients.

Name: Grando Keukens | Badkamers
Company description: Grando Keukens & Bad levert al sinds 1965 betaalbaar keuken- en baddesign. In de zoektocht naar een nieuwe keuken en/ of badkamer heeft iedereen zo zijn eigen wensen. Misschien vindt u de trends van nu belangrijk of het gebruik van duurzaam materiaal. Bij Grando Keukens & Bad zijn de mogelijkheden eindeloos. Elke eigenaar van een Grando-vestiging heeft jaren praktijkervaring en snapt wat er nodig is om een droomkeuken of –badkamer te realiseren. Hierdoor kunnen zij u perfect adviseren en geven zij, op basis van uw woonwensen, een eerlijk en persoonlijk advies op maat. Er wordt een realistisch 3D ontwerp van uw nieuwe keuken of badkamer gemaakt. De showrooms zijn hierbij dé inspiratiebron. Grando biedt meer dan alleen mooie, betaalbare keukens en badkamers. Grando denkt met u mee over de meest praktische oplossingen. Van demontage en afvoeren van de oude keuken of badkamer, tot technische en bouwkundige aanpassingen. Van de juiste materiaal- en apparatenkeus tot een begroting die tot in de puntjes klopt.  ‘’Dat is waar Grando voor staat: vanzelfsprekend topkwaliteit, al 50 jaar lang!’’ Bent u geïnteresseerd in uw eigen Grando vestiging? We zijn altijd op zoek naar enthousiaste en gemotiveerde ondernemers die geloven in ons concept. Kijk voor meer informatie op de website www.grando.nl/franchise

Name: Svane Køkkenet
Company description: IKKE BARE ET KØKKEN, MEN ET SVANE.  Hos Svane designer vi nytænkende køkkenarkitektur til dem, der forventer lidt mere. Af designet, funktionaliteten, holdbarheden og ikke mindst af processen. Derfor er vi omhyggelige i alt, hvad vi gør, og det gør hele forskellen. Svane Køkkenet er en del af TCM Group. Vi sælger køkkener, bad og opbevaring som hæver sig over almindeligheden i vores 28 butikker i Danmark og 10 butikker i Norge.  Se mere på svane.com

Name: Möbelmarkt Dogern KG
Company description: Auf einer riesigen Ausstellungsfläche von über 30.000qm erleben Sie im Möbelmarkt Dogern Wohnwelten der besonderen Art für gehobene Ansprüche. Wir bieten Ihrem Zuhause ein Komplettsortiment: Markenmöbel für Küche, Sofa, Sessel, Couch-Tisch, Esstisch, Stuhl, Bett, Matratze, Lampe... Unsere Auswahl an Möbel ist riesig: Vom hochwertigen Regal bis zur Landhaus Kommode, vom Designer Schrank bis zur rustikalen Eckbank und vom feinsten Edelstahl Besteck/Geschirr bis hin zu Sideboards, TV Möbel und einzigartigen Wohnwänden.  Lassen Sie Ihre Räume in neuem Licht erstrahlen. Schauen Sie doch einfach mal vorbei und lassen Sie sich inspirieren. Darüber hinaus bieten nur wenige Minuten entfernt in Waldshut unsere Partnereinrichtungshäuser Möbelarena das passende Angebot in Preiseinstiegssegment und Natura Wohndesign im Bereich gesundes, ökologisches Wohnen mit dem Fokus auf Holz und Garten.

Name: Dovy Kitchens
Company description: Dovy is een familiebedrijf waar meer dan 45 jaar vakmanschap huist. In vier decennia zijn we uitgegroeid tot een vooruitstrevende, hoogtechnologische kmo. We zagen, frezen, assembleren, lakken en bewerken elke keuken zelf en vervoeren ze dan naar klanten in het hele land. Doordat we alles zelf in de hand hebben, kunnen we garant staan voor een perfecte kwaliteit, terwijl je keuken toch betaalbaar blijft.

Name: Fissler Austria
Company description: Fissler Austria is a renowned manufacturer specializing in high-quality pressure cookers and a diverse range of premium cookware, including pots and pans. Established in 1845, the company has built a legacy of innovation and craftsmanship, embodying the philosophy that cooking is an art form that fosters passion, creativity, and appreciation for food. Fissler's mission is to inspire individuals to embrace pressure cooking, which not only preserves the nutritional value of ingredients but also significantly reduces cooking time and energy consumption. The brand is dedicated to enhancing the cooking experience by providing tools that promote healthy lifestyles through efficient cooking methods. Fissler's commitment to quality is evident in its use of durable materials and advanced technology, ensuring safety and performance in every kitchen. The company emphasizes sustainability, utilizing up to 90% recycled stainless steel in its products, and is dedicated to creating cookware that lasts for generations. Fissler primarily serves home cooks and culinary enthusiasts, targeting both professional chefs and everyday cooks who value quality, performance, and design in their kitchenware.  With a strong presence in the global market, Fissler collaborates with various retailers and distributors to reach a wide audience, ensuring that its products meet the highest standards of excellence. The brand's focus on innovation and sustainability positions it as a leader in the cookware industry, inspiring passionate cooks around the world to elevate their culinary experiences.

Name: Rutar Group
Company description: Rutar Group is a prominent player in the home furnishings and interior design sector, dedicated to transforming living spaces into personalized sanctuaries. With a mission to inspire and enhance the everyday lives of its customers, Rutar offers a diverse range of products, including stylish furniture, innovative kitchen designs, and artistic home decor. The company prides itself on its commitment to quality and authenticity, ensuring that each piece resonates with the beauty of everyday life. Rutar serves a wide clientele, from individual homeowners seeking to create their dream spaces to businesses looking for functional and aesthetic solutions. Collaborating with renowned brands like Interliving, Stressless®, and Voglauer, Rutar aims to redefine comfort and style in home living.  With over 65 years of experience, Rutar continues to be a trusted partner in realizing residential dreams, fostering a deep connection between people and their homes. The company specializes in high-quality furniture and accessories for various living spaces, offering a wide range of services, including furniture delivery, assembly, and financing options, ensuring a seamless shopping experience for its customers. Rutar's clientele includes families and individuals seeking stylish and functional home furnishings, while its partnerships with leading brands enhance its product offerings. Committed to customer satisfaction, Rutar emphasizes quality, affordability, and innovative design, making it a trusted choice for home decor enthusiasts. Through its dedication to creating inviting and personalized environments, Rutar Group transforms houses into homes that reflect individual tastes and lifestyles.

Name: Cosina
HQ Location: Denmark, Central Jutland, Århus, 18 E Hermodsvej, 8230
Company description: Cosina er Danmarks bedst ratede leverandør af storkøkkenudstyr og har showroom i Aarhus. Et unikt mix af kvalitetsmærker inden for storkøkken- og bagerimaskiner og dygtige køkken-konsulenter med mange års erfaring, sikrer at store såvel som små projekter bliver en succes. Her på LinkedIn kan du få et indblik i vores verden, og forhåbentligt kan vi skabe interessante diskussioner sammen med dig og andre restauratører.

Name: Piet Klerkx
Company description: Piet Klerkx is met zes vestigingen en bijna 90 jaar ervaring dé woonwinkel van Nederland. Naast een grote collectie meubelen en bedden, heeft Piet Klerkx in Amersfoort en Waalwijk een grote keuken en badkamer showroom. Bij Piet Klerkx vind je topmerken en stijlen op het gebied van wonen, slapen, koken en baden. Piet Klerkx heeft wooninspiratie in elke stijl en voor elk budget. De interieurarchitecten bieden graag hulp bij het maken van de juiste keuzes door het geven van kleur- en interieuradvies.  Opgericht in 1929 als meubelspecialist met een zo groot mogelijke keuze tegen de beste prijs-kwaliteit verhouding. Nationale erkenning als woonautoriteit door opening van de eerste woonboulevard in Nederland en de campagne ‘de keuze is reuze’ (zoveel m2, het is niet te tellen)

Name: SCONTO Nábytek S.r.o.
Company description: SCONTO Nábytek s.r.o. je součástí německého koncernu Höffner, který patří k největším prodejcům nábytku v Evropě. Najdete u nás kompletní sortiment bytového nábytku, který zahrnuje obývací stěny, sedací soupravy, pohovky, konferenční stolky, ložnice, matrace, rošty, dětské pokoje, kuchyně, jídelny, židle, stoly, kancelářský a koupelnový nábytek, svítidla, bytový textil a další kuchyňské i bytové doplňky.

Name: Alvic Center
Company description: Alvic Center is a specialized company that provides high-quality products and services for kitchen, bathroom, and interior design projects, catering exclusively to professionals such as carpenters, remodelers, architects, and interior designers. With a mission to ensure top-notch installation quality through expert guidance, Alvic Center offers a wide range of customizable solutions, including cabinets, doors, countertops, and modular furniture. Their extensive showrooms, featuring over 200 m² of displays, serve as inspiration hubs for clients, while their 3D budgeting tool simplifies the design process. Alvic Center collaborates with various professionals across Spain, ensuring that each project meets the highest standards of functionality and aesthetics. The company is committed to staying ahead of design trends, providing clients with innovative ideas and materials directly from the factory.

Name: WEKO Wohnen GmbH
Company description: WEKO Wohnen GmbH ist ein innovatives Unternehmen, das sich auf den Verkauf und die Beratung von hochwertigen Möbeln und Küchen spezialisiert hat. Mit dem Ziel, die Wünsche der Kunden nicht nur zu erfüllen, sondern zu übertreffen, bietet WEKO einen umfassenden Rundum-Service, der von der Küchenheimberatung bis hin zur Vermietung von WEKOCars reicht. Die Firma legt großen Wert auf nachhaltige Produkte und arbeitet eng mit renommierten Herstellern zusammen, um umweltfreundliche und qualitativ hochwertige Textilien und Möbel anzubieten. WEKO richtet sich an Privatkunden sowie an Geschäftspartner, die Wert auf exzellenten Service und individuelle Lösungen legen. Die Mission des Unternehmens ist es, langfristige Kundenbeziehungen aufzubauen und durch kontinuierliche Betreuung und innovative Dienstleistungen einen hohen Kundennutzen zu schaffen.

Name: Nobia Denmark A/S
Company description: Nobia er en af Europas ledende køkkenproducenter med en strategisk  positionering med omkring 20 stærke køkkenbrands – primært i Europa men også på verdensplan.  Nobia Denmark A/S varetager brands som HTH Køkkener, Gør Det Selv HTH, Invita Køkkener og uno form.

Name: Möbelix
Company description: Jsme Möbelix, síť prodejen nábytku a bytových doplňků. Patříme k rakouskému koncernu XXXLutz a v současné době rosteme nejrychleji ze všech obchodních sítí v Evropě. V Čechách a na Slovensku nás najdete 18x, od Karlových Varů až po Košice.  Znáte Möbelix? Zamyslete se znovu. Möbelix je na českém a slovenském trhu 11 let a  během posledních 3 let prošel radikální změnou. Z diskontních prodejen se staly reprezentativní obchodní domy, kde si přijdou na své především zákazníci, kteří chtějí moderně a prakticky bydlet. Moderní nábytek pro moderní zákazníky. To je naše vize. Sortiment vybíráme tak, abychom zákazníkům dávali nový impuls a neúnavně je inspirovali aktuálními trendy. Kromě atraktivního nábytku nabízíme perfektní servis, mimo jiné 3D plánování s tabletem na prodejně nebo digitální záměr kuchyně u zákazníka s přenosem dat. Zákazníkovi nabízíme zážitek, emoci a nikdy nezapomínáme na lidský přístup.  A to nejen  ve vztahu k zákazníkům ale především k našim zaměstnancům. Ctíme férovost a kolegialitu.

Name: Van Hoecke NV
Company description: Van Hoecke NV specializes in innovative kitchen solutions, focusing on the design and functionality of kitchen zones tailored to individual cooking habits. The company aims to enhance the cooking experience by creating efficient workspaces that streamline meal preparation through well-defined areas such as storage, washing, and cooking. Their mission is to ensure that all necessary tools and ingredients are easily accessible, thereby optimizing workflow in the kitchen. Van Hoecke NV serves a diverse clientele, including kitchen designers, architects, and homeowners, and collaborates with various partners to deliver high-quality, customizable kitchen components. The company is committed to providing practical and stylish solutions that cater to both right- and left-handed users, ensuring that every kitchen is both functional and user-friendly.

Name: REDDY Küchen
Company description: Die Marke REDDY Küchen zählt seit ihrer Gründung im Jahr 1994 und zu den großen Franchise-Ketten im Küchenfachhandel in Deutschland. Dank der hervorragenden Zahlen im wachstumsstarken mittleren Preissegment wächst REDDY Küchen europaweit. Küchenkäufer können bereits an über 80 Standorten die Vorteile und Kompetenz des inhabergeführten Küchenfachhandels mit eigener Küchenmarke erleben. Das konstante Qualitätsniveau sichert REDDY Küchen seit 2014 ohne Unterbrechung die goldene Auszeichnung als Service Champion für das exzellente Dienstleistungsangebot und die große Kundenfreundlichkeit. Wir wissen, dass die mehrfach ausgezeichnete Kundenzufriedenheit von der Qualität unserer Produkte, aber auch vom Service unserer Partner abhängt.  Wir unterstützen deshalb ambitionierte Franchise-Nehmer in ihrem unternehmerischen Alltag mit zahlreichen Leistungen auf den Gebieten Finanzen, Weiterbildung, (Online)-Marketing, Werbung und Planungssoftware. Als Franchise-Geber begleiten wir unsere Partner vom ersten Tag an in den Bereichen der operativen und strategischen Unternehmensführung. Die Beratung beginnt bereits bei der Wahl des richtigen Standorts und der Auswahl einer passenden Immobile. Auch nach der Unternehmenseröffnung können sich unsere Partner auf die Marke REDDY verlassen. Wer auf REDDY Küchen setzt, profitiert von einem erfahrenen Franchise-Geber mit unternehmerischem Weitblick. Unsere Partner zeichnen sich durch eine hohe Zufriedenheit mit REDDY Küchen aus, daher liegt die Weiterempfehlungsquote bei unseren Franchise-Nehmern bei 100%. Seit 2015 wurde die Marke REDDY Küchen daher konstant mit dem igenda.AWARD GOLD für die hervorragende Beziehung zwischen Franchise-Geber und Franchise-Nehmern ausgezeichnet.

Name: Coolshop.com
Company description: Coolshop.com is a dynamic online retail platform that specializes in a wide array of products, including toys, electronics, beauty products, home and kitchen items, and pet supplies. The company's mission is to provide customers with a diverse selection of high-quality products at competitive prices, ensuring a seamless shopping experience. With a focus on customer satisfaction, Coolshop.com offers a price guarantee and a robust customer service team to assist shoppers. The target market includes families, tech enthusiasts, and individuals seeking quality products across various categories. By partnering with top brands like Apple, Sony, and LEGO, Coolshop.com aims to cater to a broad audience while maintaining a commitment to excellence and value.

Name: Mediaprofili
HQ Location: Italy, Veneto, Mansuè, 13 Via Delle Industrie, 31040
Company description: Beyond the surface, there is our heritage and experience, an equilibrium of technology, know-how, craftmanship, passion and care. Since the foundation in 1982 we have continuously improved our production processes, developed new materials and technologies to supply our partners with the best sustainable, qualitative and cost effective manufacturing solutions. We master any polymeric or paper based foil application technology to match our customers’ needs and manufacture products able to excel in any home environment: kitchen, living, bedroom, bathroom or office.

Name: Portax S.A.
Company description: Founded in the 80's, Portax Group is an industrial reference in the European Sector of Kitchens and Wardrobes.

Name: Semeraro
Company description: Siamo italiani, amiamo l’arredamento, siamo passionali, creativi con la forza di credere nelle nostre idee e con la voglia di realizzarle. La nostra tradizione è italiana legata all’arredamento, alla moda, alla cucina, al cibo, al vino all’arte del saper vivere felicemente, qualità che ci distingue nel mondo. Sviluppiamo e proponiamo arredamenti e oggetti per la casa garantendo impegno nella ricerca dei materiali in forme e colori per rendere il tuo ambiente piacevole ed accogliente. Amiamo tutto ciò che facciamo e, ogni giorno sviluppiamo oggetti di arredamento in uno stile nel quale ci riconosciamo; il gusto che nasce dalla tradizione italiana. Il nostro sviluppo creativo è in continua evoluzione con sensibilità, cultura, condivisione e conoscenza. Il nostro obiettivo è garantire ai nostri clienti valori che corrispondono a qualità, onestà e trasparenza. Ci impegniamo per la soddisfazione dei nostri clienti. Farti vivere la tua casa con funzionalità e soddisfazione è la nostra missione. Ti promettiamo il rispetto dell’ambiente che ti circonda avendone cura al fine di avere un rapporto di trasparenza in quanto sicuri di considerarti tra i nostri nuovi messaggeri.

Name: Sijben Wooncenter B.V.
Company description: Sijben Wooncenter B.V. is a leading furniture retailer in Europe, renowned for its extensive range of furniture, sleep solutions, and kitchens. With showrooms located in Roermond, Eindhoven, and Elen, the company offers a unique collection that includes both design furniture and 'new classics', making it an appealing destination for a diverse clientele. Sijben's mission is to inspire customers by providing high-quality products and expert advice, enabling them to create their ideal living environments. The company collaborates with well-known international brands, ensuring an excellent price-quality ratio that attracts a wide audience, from design enthusiasts to families seeking functional and stylish home solutions. Sijben Wooncenter B.V. aims to deliver exceptional service and quality, positioning itself as a trusted partner for various projects, including offices, hospitality venues, and vacation homes. The company caters to a broad spectrum of clients, ranging from individual homeowners to businesses in need of comprehensive interior solutions. With years of experience and a strong portfolio of references, Sijben prides itself on its ability to stay updated with the latest trends in interior design. The company is dedicated to enhancing customer satisfaction through personalized consultations and a wide selection of brands, ensuring that every client finds the perfect fit for their space.

Name: Dille & Kamille
Company description: Dille & Kamille is a family-owned company established in 1974, dedicated to promoting simplicity and sustainability in everyday living. With a diverse range of products for home, garden, and kitchen, the company aims to inspire customers to live consciously and in harmony with nature. Dille & Kamille is proud to be B Corp certified, reflecting its commitment to social and environmental responsibility. The company actively collaborates with initiatives like 50|50 Wood, providing opportunities for individuals distanced from the labor market to gain work experience and contribute to the creation of its store furnishings. Targeting eco-conscious consumers in the Netherlands, Belgium, and Germany, Dille & Kamille fosters a strong community through its membership program, offering exclusive benefits and events to its loyal customers. The company’s mission is to continuously improve its sustainability practices while maintaining a warm, family-like atmosphere among its employees and customers.

Name: Keukenwarenhuis.nl
Company description: Keukenwarenhuis.nl is a family-owned business located in Dordrecht, specializing in affordable German kitchens, which are offered at competitive prices, often at half the cost of traditional retail. The company operates the largest kitchen showroom in the Benelux region, showcasing over 1,000 luxury kitchens in various styles, including modern, industrial, and country designs. Their mission is to provide customers with a hassle-free kitchen buying experience, offering complete kitchen deals that include appliances and installation services. Keukenwarenhuis.nl caters to both individual consumers and businesses, primarily serving clients in the Netherlands and Flanders, Belgium. With a commitment to quality and customer satisfaction, the company emphasizes transparency in pricing and a relaxed shopping environment, allowing customers to explore their options without pressure.

Name: BERLONI
HQ Location: Italy, Veneto, Riese Pio X, 71 Via Castellana, 31039
Company description: Berloni is a renowned Italian company specializing in the design and production of high-end kitchens and living spaces. Founded in 1960 by brothers Antonio and Marcello Berloni in Pesaro, the company initially focused on handcrafted furniture, later establishing itself as a leader in modular kitchen solutions. With a mission to create elegant and quality environments that reflect the unique personalities of their clients, Berloni combines aesthetics, technology, and active customer participation in its design process. The company aims to elevate the kitchen to a shared architectural space, ensuring that every detail contributes to a harmonious living experience. Today, Berloni serves a diverse clientele, including homeowners seeking personalized kitchen solutions, and collaborates with various partners to maintain its commitment to Italian craftsmanship and design excellence.

Name: PLANA - Aus Freude An Küchen
Company description: Begeisterte Kunden, die uns weiterempfehlen, sind seit mehr als 35 Jahren unser Antrieb und Ziel. Dafür sorgen wir mit Küchen von höchster Qualität und umsichtigen Services, die auf Ihren individuellen Bedarf zugeschnitten sind. Unser Versprechen an Sie: Nachhaltige Freude mit Ihrer neuen Küche. Wir begleiten Sie bei der Auswahl und Planung der perfekten Küche für Ihr Zuhause. In unseren Ausstellungen finden Sie Inspiration für jeden Geschmack und treffen Ihre persönlichen Beraterinnen und Berater.  Sie möchten sich selbstständig machen? Eröffnen Sie Ihr PLANA Küchenstudio in Ihrer Region. PLANA bietet das Erfolgsmodell, mit dem Sie jetzt in Ihre Selbständigkeit starten können. Gründen Sie Ihr Unternehmen mit dem Franchise-Pionier der Küchenbranche. https://www.plana.de/impressum/

Name: Jernia
Company description: Jernia is a prominent retail company specializing in kitchenware, home goods, and outdoor products, catering to the needs of both everyday consumers and enthusiasts. With a mission to provide high-quality products that enhance the home experience, Jernia aims to be a trusted partner for customers seeking practical and stylish solutions for their cooking, baking, and home improvement projects. The company serves a diverse clientele, including families, home cooks, and individuals preparing for special occasions, and collaborates with reputable brands to offer a wide range of products. Jernia's target market includes those looking for reliable kitchen tools, decorative items, and outdoor equipment, making it a go-to destination for anyone looking to elevate their home and lifestyle.

Name: Voortman Keukens
Company description: Voortman Keukens is een modern familiebedrijf dat al 50 jaar gespecialiseerd is in het ontwerpen en realiseren van unieke keukens, afgestemd op de persoonlijke wensen en smaken van hun klanten. Met een breed assortiment aan stijlen, waaronder modern, landelijk modern, modern classic en industrieel, biedt Voortman Keukens maatwerkoplossingen die het gezellige hart van elk huis vormen. Het bedrijf streeft naar 100% klanttevredenheid en garandeert uitstekende service en montage, waarbij ze ook de oude keuken kunnen verwijderen en leidingen aanpassen indien nodig. Voortman Keukens bedient een diverse klantenkring, van particuliere huiseigenaren tot projectontwikkelaars, en werkt samen met gerenommeerde partners zoals SieMatic om hoogwaardige keukenapparatuur en -ontwerpen te leveren. Hun missie is om de droomkeuken van elke klant tot leven te brengen, waarbij ze de nadruk leggen op kwaliteit, vakmanschap en een inspirerende klantbeleving.

Name: Molteni&C
Company description: Molteni&C is a prestigious Italian furniture company founded in 1934, celebrated for its exceptional craftsmanship and innovative design. The company specializes in creating high-quality furniture for a variety of environments, including living rooms, kitchens, and outdoor spaces. With a strong emphasis on collaboration, Molteni&C works with renowned architects and designers such as Gio Ponti and Vincent Van Duysen to produce elegant and functional pieces that meet contemporary living needs. The company's mission is to blend tradition with modernity, ensuring that each product reflects a commitment to quality and sustainability.  Molteni&C caters to a diverse clientele, including luxury residential projects, commercial spaces, and design enthusiasts worldwide. The brand has established partnerships with leading design firms and retailers, further enhancing its reputation in the international design landscape. With flagship stores in major cities such as Bangkok and Munich, Molteni&C continues to expand its global presence while celebrating its rich heritage. The company focuses on personalized design solutions, aiming to enhance contemporary living through its sophisticated and functional products. As it looks towards the future, Molteni&C remains dedicated to interpreting the evolving needs of modern lifestyles through innovative design.

Name: Dekker Zevenhuizen
Company description: Dekker Zevenhuizen B.V. is a leading family-owned company established in 1930, specializing in the production and sale of high-quality wooden and stone kitchen and worktops, along with kitchen accessories. With an annual revenue of 206 million euros and a dedicated workforce of 179 employees, the company is committed to sustainable economic growth through investments in innovation and resources, placing corporate social responsibility (CSR) at the core of its operations. Dekker Zevenhuizen serves a diverse clientele, including retail and project markets across Europe, and collaborates with various suppliers to develop products that align with the principles of the circular economy. The company's philosophy is grounded in its core values of quality, innovation, and collaboration, with a strong focus on creating a livable world for future generations. By utilizing FSC-certified wood and developing sustainable materials such as Greengridz, Dekker Zevenhuizen is dedicated to maintaining a responsible and transparent supply chain. The company has engaged FIRA Sustainability B.V. for external verification of its sustainability claims, ensuring reliability and transparency in its CSR reporting. Dekker Zevenhuizen aims to enhance its sustainability performance by addressing key areas such as labor conditions, social dialogue, waste separation, and the use of sustainable materials. Actively involving relevant stakeholders in its CSR initiatives, the company is committed to continuous improvement in its operations and supply chain management. With a strong emphasis on ethical practices and community support, Dekker Zevenhuizen strives to meet the evolving needs of its clients while making a positive contribution to society and the environment.

Name: Cash & Carry Kitchens
Company description: Cash & Carry Kitchens started in Cork over 40 years ago with a simple idea – let’s make beautiful kitchens and bedrooms affordable for families in Ireland. Since then we have grown into a network of nationwide showrooms, building a team of experts who understand what a new kitchen means to the customer, at the heart of their home. Listening to our customers has helped us become Ireland’s leading manufacturer of fitted kitchens and bedroom furniture, with an unrivalled reputation for value, quality and service.

Name: Härjedalskök
Company description: Härjedalskök är marknadsledande på köksrenovering. Med Härjedalsmetoden® förnyar företaget över 5 000 kök om året med fullt ansvar för måttbeställda produkter, egen tillverkning, montering och bortforsling. Ett hållbart alternativ som bygger på nya köksluckor, lådsystem och nya bänkskivor. Den moderna vägen till ett snyggt kök.  Härjedalskök tillhör Nordic Kitchen Group tillsammans med LIB - Luck och inredningsbolaget, Hagaköket och Canadaköket. I Norge säljs Härjedalskök av en återförsäljare undervarumärket HerjedalsKjøkken.

Name: Eigenhuis Groep
Company description: Eigenhuis Groep is een toonaangevende organisatie op het gebied van keukens. Eigenhuis Groep bestaat uit de volgende formules: Eigenhuis Keukens, SieMatic Interior Design, Satink Keukens, Gennu en Keuken Design Nijmegen . “Persoonlijk en betrokken”, zo kunt u Eigenhuis Groep het beste typeren. Deze kernwaarden worden op de voet gevolgd door ontzorging, kwaliteit, klantvriendelijkheid, transparante prijzen en service.  De visie: ‘Tevreden klanten bepalen het succes van morgen’.

Name: Ernestomeda
HQ Location: Italy, Pu, Montelabbate, 2/8 Via Dell Economia, 61025
Company description: Ernestomeda is an Italian company leader in the market of high-end design kitchens.  A COMPANY OF THE FUTURE. It all started with an ambitious aim. The aim of promoting Italianness worldwide, through innovative design, leading-edge technology, constant research and development and a passion for quality. Day by day, this concept acquired form in a company. A company aware of its mission: to observe, experiment and achieve something different. Something special. And so from the very beginning, innovation has played a key role, together with a vocation for “tailor-made” products, reflected in attention to details and solutions allowing a high degree of personalisation. All supported by the financial soundness, excellent business reputation and know-how of the Scavolini Group, of which it is a member since 1996. Its associations with prestigious designers mark out the stages in Ernestomeda’s history. Giuseppe Bavuso, Andreucci&Hoisl, Marc Sadler, Rodolfo Dordoni, Pietro Arosio, Castiglia Associati, Carlo Bartoli and Zaha Hadid, partner in the development of Z.Island, a revolutionary, futuristic kitchen.  The combination of industrial capability with atelier philosophy, in perfect keeping with the company’s strategy, led to the development of the Contract Division. THE COMPANY’S FUTURE. Ernestomeda is a company with deep roots in its home area. Over time, it has consolidated this bond, an expression of Italian manufacturing expertise and values such as ingenuity, hard work and creativity. And it is in its bond to its local district that the company’s commitment to the environment originated. This explains the genesis of the “EMvironment: Ernestomeda for the environment” project, expressing a responsible, active approach to eco-sustainable industrial development.

Name: FRAMA
Company description: Based in Copenhagen’s Nyboder neighborhood, FRAMA is a multi-disciplinary design brand that creates lifestyle objects that inspire the senses and encourage mindful living. With an emphasis on natural materials, simple geometries, and uncompromising quality, FRAMA’s work connects the imaginative with the practical, resulting in a uniquely warm and honest aesthetic.    Since the launch of its first collection in 2011, FRAMA has embraced an organic and collaborative approach to design, a practice that is equally inspired by the old and the new, and by digital technologies and analog traditions. Its naturalistic, hands-on approach to design and production has allowed the brand to create a unified aesthetic across a growing range of product collections, including furniture, scents and skincare, lighting, home objects, fabrics, books, interior architecture, and meaningful design solutions and kitchens.

Name: Rosendahl Design Group A/S | B Corp
Company description: Since Erik Rosendahl established Rosendahl A/S in 1984, we have gone through a massive development. From an agency business to one of the strongest manufacturers in Denmark of design for the home and the dining table. Our products come into existence in a close partnership with a number of leading designers and we are proud to represent a brand portfolio that embraces the much-loved classics of Danish design as well as innovative lifestyle products for the home, table and kitchen: Rosendahl, Holmegaard, Kähler, Kay Bojesen Denmark, Bjørn Wiinblad Denmark, Juna, Arne Jacobsen Clocks as well as Lyngby Porcelæn. Our design philosophy is deeply rooted in the principles of functionality, aesthetics, and responsibility. We take pride in making beautiful and durable quality products that not only tell their own story but are also part of a bigger narrative, and which respect the world around us. From the smallest details to the biggest concepts, we strive to make products that not only enrich your surroundings, but also carry the design heritage of quality design responsibly into the future. Our B Corp certification represents an important milestone for Rosendahl Design Group and demonstrates our commitment to responsible business operations and social responsibility. The B Corp certification confirms our commitment to doing business in a way that balances profit with a broader purpose. For us, our B Corp certification reflects our commitment to making positive changes with a holistic perspective, where we continuously commit to strive for and maintain high standards on a social, societal, and environmental level.

Name: ARRITAL
Company description: ARRITAL is a leading Italian company specializing in the design and manufacturing of high-quality kitchen furniture, offering innovative solutions that seamlessly blend functionality with aesthetic appeal. With a mission to create personalized living spaces, ARRITAL aims to enhance the culinary experience through stylish and practical kitchen designs that reflect the unique essence of their inhabitants. The company serves a diverse clientele, including homeowners, interior designers, and architects, and collaborates with a network of retailers and partners across Italy and internationally.  ARRITAL's commitment to customer satisfaction and design excellence is evident in its elegant showrooms, where expert guidance is provided to help customers select the perfect kitchen solutions tailored to their needs. The brand operates within a dynamic ecosystem of talented professionals and partners, united by shared values of ambition, excellence, and technical expertise. ARRITAL has a strong presence in key markets such as the UK, Germany, and various countries in the Mediterranean region, catering to a wide range of customers across Europe and beyond. In addition to its focus on design, ARRITAL is dedicated to sustainability and innovation, ensuring that each product meets the highest standards of quality while contributing to a superior living experience. The company's vision emphasizes the importance of personal expression in home design, transforming contemporary living spaces into environments that resonate with individual style. Through its commitment to excellence and customer engagement, ARRITAL has established itself as a prominent player in the global kitchen design industry.

Name: Pereda
Company description: Saneamientos Pereda Fundada en 1953 para ofrecer los mejores precios en el suministro de materiales de fontanería, con el paso de los años nos hemos convertido en la empresa líder en ventas de material de calefacción, tuberías, riego y equipamiento de baños y cocinas en la Comunidad de Madrid. Contamos con más de 12000 metros de exposición repartidos entre nuestros tres centros, que permiten a nuestros clientes elegir una amplia gama de productos de las mejores marcas. Nuestra dilatada experiencia en el sector hace de nuestro asesoramiento personalizado nuestra seña de identidad. Ofreciendo a nuestros clientes líneas sencillas, clásicas y vanguardistas, en griferías, mobiliario de baño y cocina, sanitarios, azulejos … En la sección de fontanería ofrecemos todo tipo de tubería de conducción de agua, calefacción, material de riego y jardín, productos de piscina, tratamientos de agua, placas solares y un amplio surtido de repuestos.

Name: Designa
Company description: Du kan altid forvente lidt ekstra, når du handler med Designa!  Vores køkkener er designede og producerede i Danmark med fokus på godt håndværk, finish og de små særlige detaljer. Vi brænder for at skabe en tryg oplevelse og tager dig i hånden hele vejen fra de første tanker på papiret til første ret er serveret.  For hos Designa gør vi altid en ekstra indsats.  Med mere end 30 års erfaring inden for produktion af dansk kvalitet, fremstiller vi køkken, bad, garderobe og skydedøre efter kundernes ønsker og behov. Vi lytter, mærker efter og ved derfor hvilke krav vores kunder stiller og hvad de drømmer om. Det giver en god og tryg købsoplevelse hos os. Designa er en kæde af selvstændige køkkenforhandlere med +50 butikker fordelt i Danmark, Norge og på Færøerne. Ud over salg til private, består kæden også af en lang række erhvervsafdelinger og store erhvervscentre, der leverer til det professionelle marked – fra små lokale tømrervirksomheder til store entreprenørvirksomheder – med garanti for en kort leveringstid og en høj leveringssikkerhed. Følg os på designa.dk og @designakitchen. Altid en ekstra indsats.

Name: Carlsen Fritzøe Handel AS
Company description: Carlsen Fritzøe har 25 moderne byggevarehus. Butikkene er lokalisert i åtte fylker på Sør- og Østlandet. Carlsen Fritzøe har lang tradisjon innen salg av trelast og byggevarer. H. Carlsen ble etablert i 1903 og ble drevet av tre generasjoner. I dag er Carlsen Fritzøe eid av Nord-Europas tredje største handelskonsern, Kesko, som skal sikre at vi alltid kan tilby våre kunder det beste innen produkter og tjenester til gode priser. Carlsen Fritzøe har en sterk markedsposisjon lokalt og har de siste årene ekspandert sterkt. Totalt omsetter Carlsen Fritzøe for 2 milliarder og har 500 ansatte. Hovedkontoret er lokalisert i Sandefjord. Carlsen Fritzøe er en komplett leverandør av kvalitetsprodukter innen vareområdene trelast, byggevarer, jernvarer, kjøkken og interiør. Vårt mål er å gi deg distriktets beste og hyggeligste service. Fornøyde kunder er svært viktig for oss, så derfor foretar vi jevnlige kundeundersøkelser. Vi har dyktige fagfolk som snakker samme språk som deg, som du er på fornavn med og som forstår hva du trenger for å få jobben gjort. Med Carlsen Fritzøe har du en solid samarbeidspartner du kan stole på og som anbefaler deg riktige løsninger. Vi ønsker deg velkommen til våre varehus.

Name: MOHD Mollura Home Design
Company description: MOHD Mollura Home Design is a premier destination for high-end furniture and home decor, specializing in a diverse range of products that include living room, dining, and outdoor furniture, as well as lighting and kitchen accessories. Founded in 1968, the company is dedicated to inspiring beauty and functionality in living spaces, offering tailored interior design services that reflect the unique tastes and needs of its clients. With a commitment to quality and authenticity, MOHD collaborates with top international brands such as B&B Italia, Poltrona Frau, and Flos, ensuring that every piece is 100% original and meets the highest standards of craftsmanship. The target market for MOHD includes discerning homeowners, interior designers, and architects who seek sophisticated and stylish solutions for both residential and commercial spaces. The company aims to make luxury design accessible through its extensive catalog and seasonal promotions, such as summer sales that offer significant discounts. MOHD's flagship product, the CCLight bookshelf, designed by renowned Italian designer Carlo Colombo, exemplifies the company's commitment to contemporary design, integrating innovative LED lighting to enhance versatility and elegance. MOHD Mollura Home Design's mission is to inspire beauty in everyday living, while its vision encompasses a future where design enhances the human experience in all spaces. By focusing on exceptional customer service and support, MOHD strives to create exclusive environments that blend aesthetics with functionality, catering to a diverse clientele and ensuring that each piece reflects the highest standards of quality and craftsmanship. Through its dedication to innovative design and collaboration with prestigious brands, MOHD continues to set the standard in high-end interior design and furniture solutions.

Name: Jansen Totaal Wonen B.V.
Company description: Jansen Totaal Wonen B.V. is a dynamic company specializing in the design and installation of high-quality kitchens and living spaces, with a strong focus on customization and client satisfaction. Located in the historic city center of Nijmegen, the company has successfully completed various residential projects, including the notable Achter Valburg, which features a range of stylish apartments. Jansen Totaal Wonen B.V. aims to create functional and aesthetically pleasing environments that cater to the unique needs of its clients, which include homeowners and property developers. The company collaborates with reputable partners, such as Siemens and AEG, to provide state-of-the-art appliances and materials, ensuring that every kitchen is equipped with the latest technology and design trends. With a commitment to excellence and innovation, Jansen Totaal Wonen B.V. strives to enhance the living experience of its customers through tailored solutions and exceptional service.

Name: Hansgrohe France
Company description: Hansgrohe France est une entreprise spécialisée dans la conception et la fabrication de solutions de robinetterie et de douche haut de gamme pour les salles de bains et les cuisines. Avec une philosophie axée sur la qualité exceptionnelle, la durabilité et l'innovation, Hansgrohe s'engage à offrir des produits qui allient fonctionnalité et design esthétique. La mission de l'entreprise est de promouvoir une utilisation responsable de l'eau tout en garantissant une expérience utilisateur optimale grâce à des technologies telles que EcoSmart et CoolStart, qui permettent des économies d'eau et d'énergie. Hansgrohe collabore avec des architectes, des designers d'intérieur et des professionnels du bâtiment, ciblant principalement les consommateurs soucieux de la qualité et de l'esthétique dans leurs projets de rénovation ou de construction. Grâce à une garantie de 5 ans sur ses produits, Hansgrohe France se positionne comme un leader dans le secteur de la robinetterie, offrant des solutions qui répondent aux besoins variés de sa clientèle. L'entreprise s'adresse à un marché résidentiel et commercial, incluant des propriétaires, des architectes et des designers d'intérieur, tout en établissant des partenariats avec divers détaillants et distributeurs à travers la France.
