Avec un engagement envers la satisfaction client et l'amélioration continue, Hansgrohe France vise à être un nom de confiance dans l'industrie de la plomberie et des accessoires.

Name: SieMatic
Company description: Elevating Kitchen Design Innovation. With a legacy dating back to 1929, SieMatic has been a driving force in the world of kitchen design for nearly a century. Our enduring commitment to innovation remains at the heart of our brand. We're not just in the business of crafting kitchens; we're dedicated to meticulously creating spaces that spark your creativity and seamlessly align with your lifestyle. #SieMatic #KitchenDesign #Innovation

Name: BEHOME
HQ Location: Italy, Lombardy, Corsico, 2 Via Palmiro Togliatti, 20094
Company description: BEHOME è un brand italiano di riferimento nel settore del design e dell'arredamento, con oltre 50 anni di esperienza familiare. La missione dell'azienda è quella di ridefinire gli standard dell'arredamento, offrendo prodotti di alta qualità, completamente personalizzabili e a prezzi accessibili, senza compromettere stile e funzionalità. Con l'apertura del primo flagship store nel 2020, BEHOME ha rivoluzionato il concetto di vivere la casa, creando showroom immersivi dove i clienti possono trovare soluzioni d'arredo su misura per ogni ambiente, dalla cucina al soggiorno, fino al bagno. L'azienda si impegna costantemente in ricerca e sviluppo per garantire innovazione e originalità, e ha recentemente lanciato un nuovo shop online per facilitare l'acquisto dei suoi prodotti. I clienti di BEHOME includono famiglie e individui che cercano eleganza e praticità, mentre i partner e fornitori sono selezionati per garantire la qualità Made in Italy. Con 17 showroom in tutta Italia, BEHOME continua a espandere la sua presenza, avvicinando sempre di più i clienti all'esperienza di arredare la propria casa con stile.

Name: Resopal GmbH
Company description: Resopal GmbH is a leading manufacturer specializing in high-pressure laminates (HPL) and related products, offering a diverse range of solutions for interior design and construction applications. The company is committed to delivering innovative and high-quality materials that meet the evolving needs of architects, interior designers, and contractors. With a focus on sustainability and design versatility, Resopal GmbH serves a wide array of clients, including furniture manufacturers, general contractors, and retailers in the construction and interior design sectors. Their extensive product portfolio includes compact laminates, bonded boards, and decorative surfaces, catering to various applications such as kitchens, bathrooms, and commercial spaces. Through strategic partnerships and a dedication to customer satisfaction, Resopal GmbH aims to enhance the aesthetic and functional aspects of modern living and working environments.

Name: IXINA Belgium
HQ Location: Belgium, Brussels Capital, Brussels, Boulevard Paepsem, 1070
Company description: Ixina Belgium is a leading kitchen specialist located in the vibrant heart of Brussels, specifically at Tour & Taxis. The company offers a wide range of kitchen models and interior solutions, catering to diverse styles including modern, rustic, and designer kitchens. With a mission to help clients realize their dream kitchens, Ixina provides personalized guidance and support throughout every phase of the kitchen project, from initial design to final installation. Their team of kitchen experts is available to assist customers in visualizing their projects using advanced 3D tools and offers tailored quotes based on individual budgets and preferences. Targeting homeowners and renovation enthusiasts, Ixina Belgium prides itself on delivering high-quality German furniture with a 10-year warranty, alongside a network of qualified installers and customized financing solutions.

Name: Genebre S.A
Company description: Genebre started its activity in 1981 in the market for fluid control valves, and later continued with the internationalization of subsidiaries in Europe, Asia and America. The company has maintained continuous growth over the years to become one of the world leaders in its sector. As a result of this growth, in 2008 the Genebre Group holding was created, which currently counts on Hobby Flower, their Hydro-planters brand (acquired in 2012), and Genwec Washroom Equipment & Complements (created in 2014), specialized in public bathroom equipment. These new companies complement the Genebre Group's diversified portfolio, which enables us to be present in the “Canal Contract”.   We control all of the creation processes, responding to the specific needs of each market, from the inicial concept and design of the product to the production and commercialization. Genebre products are grouped into four main lines: ·         Hydrosanitary: brass valves and accessories ·         Industrial: stainless steel valves and accessories for industrial uses ·         Taps: home taps for bathroom and kitchen ·         Public taps

Name: Burger Küchenmöbel GmbH
HQ Location: Germany, Saxony-anhalt, Burg Bei Magdeburg, 31 Martin-luther Straße, 39288
Company description: Leben ist immer das, was man daraus macht. Statistisch betrachtet erlebt eine gute Küche Hochzeiten, Taufen und nicht selten die bestandene Führerscheinprüfung. Aber vor allem – die vielen wunderbar aufregenden Tage dazwischen. Für uns ist die Planung einer neuen Küche deshalb vor allem eins: ein Stück Lebensplanung. Denn eine Küche ist mehr als eine passgenaue Zusammenstellung von Stauraum, Arbeitsflächen und Hightech. Vielmehr kann eine Küche fast so etwas sein wie ein neues Familienmitglied: voller Flair, Charakter und Persönlichkeit. Die baumann group lebt diese Philosophie seit mehr als 100 Jahren und überzeugt nicht nur mit einer großen Stil-Vielfalt, sondern auch mit der Qualität „Made in Germany“. 1917 gegründet, hat sich unser in dritter Generation geführtes Familienunternehmen zu einer international tätigen Gruppe entwickelt – die baumann group. Unsere 1.200 Mitarbeiter:innen sind die Wurzel unseres Erfolgs, der auf einer Vier-Marken-Strategie basiert: Die Küchen von BAUFORMAT und burger decken den Marktbereich vom Einsteigermodell bis zum Premium-Segment ab. BURG ist für Elektrogeräte in bester Qualität und die Marke badea als Synonym für individuelle Badmöbel bekannt. Täglich verlassen 650 Küchen und 70 Bäder unsere Werke in Löhne und Burg bei Magdeburg. Präzise. Perfekt. Wie vor 105 Jahren.

Name: STRASSER Steine GmbH
Company description: STRASSER Steine GmbH is a pioneering company in the kitchen solutions sector, renowned for its commitment to sustainability and innovative design. The company recently showcased its groundbreaking product, ALPINOVA Cubo, at the Area 30 event, which allows for the creation of kitchen fronts and islands entirely from recycled natural stone. This unique offering not only emphasizes modern aesthetics but also aligns with the growing demand for environmentally responsible materials. STRASSER Steine aims to shape the kitchens of the future by combining ecological awareness with cutting-edge design, appealing to a diverse clientele that values both style and sustainability. With a focus on expanding its product range, including exclusive glass decors for niche backsplashes, the company is well-positioned to meet the evolving needs of the kitchen industry.

Name: Doimo Cucine
Company description: Doimo Cucine is a leading manufacturer of customizable kitchen solutions, dedicated to transforming everyday spaces into extraordinary experiences. The company emphasizes "libertà progettuale," or design freedom, allowing clients to create kitchens that reflect their unique tastes and functional needs through a versatile system of modules and finishes. With a commitment to sustainability, Doimo Cucine incorporates eco-friendly materials, such as 100% recyclable aluminum, into its designs. The company collaborates closely with architects, designers, and retailers to provide tailored solutions that meet diverse client requirements, from standard modular kitchens to bespoke modifications. Targeting both residential and commercial markets, Doimo Cucine aims to enhance the culinary experience by fostering relationships and creating spaces that are not only beautiful but also practical and sustainable.

Name: JKE Design
Company description: Hos JKE bygger vi på den nordiske designtradition og forener det med nye impulser udefra. Vi er startet som snedker-virksomhed, og selvom vi i dag har både maskiner og computere til hjælp, så skræddersyer vi hvert eneste køkken på fabrikken i Nordjylland. JKE Design ligger på den samme adresse i Nordjylland som i 1970, og kærligheden til håndværket kendetegner den dag i dag JKE Design. Vi forener i dag håndværket med moderne produktion, og medarbejderne sætter en ære i at levere en god håndværksmæssig kvalitet.  JKE Design har siden 2000 været en del af den svensk-ejede Ballingslöv International koncern, der udover JKE Design tæller en række af Skandinaviens allerstærkeste køkken-, bad- og garderobeproducenter.

Name: Tvis Køkken
Company description: I 70 år har vi produceret køkkener i Tvis ved Holstebro. Det var her, virksomheden startede tilbage i 1952, da snedkermester Poul Frandsen begyndte at producere køkkenskabe. Med dygtighed og fremsynethed blev fabrikken og produktionen løbende tilpasset markedet, så Tvis Køkken kunne levere køkken, bad og garderobe af høj kvalitet til glade kunder i hele landet.  I dag fylder fabrikken over 33.000 m2, hvorfra vi producerer dit nye køkken efter de mest moderne principper – med fortsat større og større krav til kvalitet, bæredygtighed og holdbart design. Det er vigtigt for os, at et Tvis køkken læner sig ind i hjemmets sjæl, stil og historie, og at det passer til dig, der lever i det. Køkkenet skal være et langsigtet valg, der i design, kvalitet og funktion bliver en naturlig del af boligen mange år frem i tiden. På den måde sikrer vi, at du får et køkken, du bliver glad for at stå op til hver dag.

Name: Jeremias GmbH
Company description: Jeremias GmbH, a prominent member of the Jeremias Group, has established itself as a leader in the manufacturing of chimney and exhaust systems for over 50 years. The company specializes in high-quality venting solutions tailored for a variety of applications, including residential heating appliances, commercial kitchens, and industrial exhaust systems. With a mission to provide innovative and reliable products, Jeremias GmbH is dedicated to ensuring safety, efficiency, and compliance with industry standards such as NFPA and ANSI codes. The company's vision is to set industry benchmarks for quality and performance, transforming complex challenges into customized solutions through comprehensive project management. Jeremias GmbH serves a diverse clientele that includes contractors, builders, appliance manufacturers, and industrial facilities, with a strong focus on sectors such as combined heat and power (CHP), condensing technology, and industrial kitchens. The company has successfully completed over 3,500 projects worldwide, demonstrating its commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction. With numerous production sites and a global network of sales partners, Jeremias GmbH ensures location-independent availability and support for its clients. The company emphasizes sustainability and ethical principles, fostering long-term partnerships with clients and suppliers to achieve mutual success and continuous growth. By prioritizing environmental responsibility and operational excellence, Jeremias GmbH aims to meet the evolving needs of its customers while minimizing their environmental impact. Through its innovative solutions and dedicated customer service, Jeremias GmbH strives to be a trusted partner in the field of chimney technology and industrial exhaust systems, enhancing the performance and safety of venting systems across more than 60 countries.

Name: KeukenConcurrent
Company description: KeukenConcurrent is a leading kitchen retailer in the Netherlands, specializing in providing high-quality kitchens at guaranteed low prices. The company prides itself on its seven guarantees, which include the lowest price in the country, fast delivery times, and exceptional customer service. With a diverse range of kitchen collections, including budget-friendly options and custom designs, KeukenConcurrent caters to a wide array of clients, from first-time homeowners to those looking to renovate their existing spaces. The company operates nearly 50 locations across the Netherlands, ensuring accessibility for customers seeking professional advice and personalized kitchen solutions. KeukenConcurrent's mission is to empower customers to create their dream kitchens while maintaining affordability and quality, making it a trusted partner in kitchen design and installation.

Name: Valvex SA
HQ Location: Poland, Lesser Poland Voivodeship, Jordanów Woj, 2 Nad Skawą, 34-240
Company description: Valvex SA is a leading manufacturer specializing in high-quality plumbing and heating solutions, offering a comprehensive range of products including bathroom and kitchen fittings, installation systems for water, gas, and central heating. The company's mission is to provide innovative and reliable solutions that enhance the functionality and aesthetics of modern living spaces. Valvex serves a diverse clientele, including distributors, installers, designers, and investors, ensuring that their products meet the needs of both residential and commercial markets. With a commitment to quality and customer satisfaction, Valvex collaborates with various partners to deliver cutting-edge designs and technologies, positioning itself as a trusted name in the plumbing industry.

Name: DISCESUR
Company description: Desde su fundación en el año 1988, Discesur se ha convertido en un referente del mercado español en soluciones y equipamiento para cocina y baño, especializados en: - Venta y distribución de cerámica - Aparatos sanitarios - Grifería - Armarios de cocina y muebles de baño - Suelos de madera Ofrecemos un servicio distinguido y personalizado, ofreciendo nuestras soluciones a particulares y profesionales en materiales de acabado decorativo e interiorismo.

Name: Marbodal
Company description: Marbodal - Vi skapar kök du inte trodde var möjligt Marbodal, som är beläget i Tidaholm, har skapat närproducerade kök för livets alla tillfällen ända sedan 1924. Våra produkter och sortiment samt vår kunskap och erfarenhet handlar om att skapa rum med personlig atmosfär där funktionerna bjuder in till ett enklare liv, kreativ matlagning och trevliga umgängen. Vårt löfte till våra kunder är att hjälpa till att skapa kök där hela livet ska få ta plats. Det genuina hantverket, inspirerande lösningar och känsla för design gör att vi kan erbjuda våra kunder just den köksupplevelse Marbodal gjort sig känd för de senaste 90 åren. Att Marbodals kök är närproducerade innebär att vi gör allt vi kan för att bidra till ett hållbart samhälle. Inte bara i form av kortare och mer effektiva frakter. Flertalet av våra kök har dessutom Svanenmärkta stommar och köksluckor. Huvuddelen av försäljningen sker genom Marbodalbutiker, bygghandeln och husfabriker i Sverige. Marbodal är ett av flera välkända varumärken inom Nobiakoncernen, Europas ledande köksinteriörföretag.

Name: DUKA
Company description: DUKA offers a wide assortment for the Kitchen and Dining area, emphasizing on kitchenware, glassware, dinnerware, cutlery and gifts. Each product is selected for its good quality and functionality. The assortment has a contemporary expression with a Scandinavian influence. In 1920 the Swedish merchant Hjalmar Blomkvist opened a store with glass, porcelain and kitchenware in the Swedish town of Linkoping. His store proved to be successful so he continued opening more stores in other cities in Sweden. When Hjalmar retired, he sold his growing company, and with the new owner, the company continued to further expand. DUKA become a company recognised for its good design and quality all over Sweden.  Today the work continues in the spirit of the founder and DUKA Team always does its utmost to maintain the values that once created DUKA. They have guided us through the decades.  DUKA’s products are sold online and offline. DUKA currently has over 75 shops in Poland, Germany, the Netherlands, Bulgaria and the UK.

Name: Espírito Do Lar
Company description: Distribuidor de produtos de Utilidades Domésticas, essencialmente Cozinha, representando empresas internacionais de grande prestígio, tais como Snips, Pedrini, Rivadossi, Cosatto, Risoli, Silikomart. Base de actuação essencialmente ao nível de clientes de Distribuição Moderna.

Name: Virosac
Company description: Virosac è l’azienda leader in Italia nella produzione di prodotti per la casa, in particolare sacchi per i rifiuti e sacchi per la congelazione degli alimenti. Nata 50 anni fa, impiega oggi più di 100 dipendenti che lavorano in Italia, in due stabilimenti a Pederobba (TV). Qui attraverso strumentazioni d’avanguardia vengono lavorate ogni anno 8.000 tonnellate di materiale e prodotti 600 milioni di sacchetti.  Se alla nascita erano soprattutto i sacchi frigo, la produzione di Virosac si è poi notevolmente allargata arrivando a comprendere ogni tipo di sacco per i rifiuti (dal piccolo sacco in Mater-Bi per il rifiuto umido fino ai grandi sacchi ultraresistenti per il rifiuto secco del condominio) e tantissime soluzioni diverse per la cucina, il guardaroba, il giardino.  Ma la peculiarità di Virosac è la capacità di creare prodotti nuovi: è il caso ad esempio del sistema brevettato Lacciosac per la chiusura più pratica dei sacchetti, la saldatura antigoccia che evita le rotture, lo Stopsac oltre al Saccofrigo con laccetto già incorporato nel sacco.  Tema importante per Virosac è quello della tutela dell’ambiente: è stata tra le prime aziende in Italia ad ottimizzare l’utilizzo di plastiche rigenerate o materiali biodegradabili e cerca di ridurre al minimo gli imballi dei suoi prodotti.

Name: WTS SpA
HQ Location: Italy, Brescia, Flero, 120 Via Xx Settembre, 25020
Company description: WTS SpA is dedicated to providing its employees and stakeholders with the tools necessary to work effectively and safely. The company emphasizes a culture of integrity and accountability, exemplified by its whistleblowing service, which allows for the reporting of any illicit conduct to the Human Resources department. A significant part of WTS SpA's portfolio includes its ownership of Ottone Meloda, a market leader with 60 years of experience in producing high-quality taps and mixers for bathrooms and kitchens. Ottone Meloda exports its innovative and environmentally conscious products to over 50 countries, including markets in the Middle East, Africa, North America, Asia, and Europe, with plans to expand into China and India. WTS SpA's mission is to uphold excellence and innovation while ensuring a safe and supportive work environment for all its stakeholders.

Name: Fino
Company description: Established in 1935, C. Fino + Sons have continued to expand by adding more prestigious brands to its portfolio. At Fino we are able to furnish all types of rooms from kitchens to bedrooms, living rooms, dining suites and offices not just with furniture but also with furnishings such as lights, curtains and decorations. Fino represents some of the finest brands in the furniture industry, such as Veneta Cucine, Ditre Italia, Tomasella, Pedrali and a multitude of other world renowned brands. Whether it is a kitchen you are looking for, a bedroom, sofa suite, a wall unit or simply a stylish chair, Fino has it all.

Name: HAKA Küche GmbH
Company description: HAKA Küche GmbH specializes in creating custom kitchens that serve as the central hub of family life, transforming cooking spaces into personalized living areas. The company is dedicated to providing tailored solutions that address the unique challenges of kitchen design, particularly in spaces with unconventional layouts or architectural features. HAKA's mission is to harmonize aesthetics, functionality, and individual preferences, ensuring that each kitchen not only meets practical needs but also reflects the homeowner's personality. Their target market includes homeowners seeking bespoke kitchen solutions, and they collaborate closely with clients to develop innovative designs that maximize space and enhance usability. Through thoughtful planning and expert craftsmanship, HAKA Küche GmbH aims to turn every kitchen into a functional and inviting environment.

Name: Prestige Home Center
HQ Location: Belgium, Flanders, Halle, Km Autostrada Tirane Durres, 1032
Company description: PRESTIGE HOME, is the first and only center in Albania, exclusively dedicated exclusively to products and services of “HOME” lines, and “Interior Design”. Represented by the HOME and Interior Design market with the highest national and international reputation: PIERRE CARDIN HOME, DOIMO SALOTTI, ZEBRANO, VALERON, MIELE, ECOLIGHT, DORELAN, TEKA, HIGOLD, Lider Lift, DEA ARREDIM, VIVIDA, FEYDOM, VOX ELCTRONICS, SEZON DEKOR, LA FORCHETTA, DAGE PERDE, CASAL, NILLS, BICAKU STONE etc. PRESTIGE HOME is focused on providing everything for home, office and other residential or work environments. We have combined the brands that bring products and services that include decor, furniture sets, installations, lighting, furnishings, kitchen appliances, electrical appliances, insulation, wall papers, panels, other electrical accessories and environment-friendly technologies, heat, mattresses, room accessories and various spaces.

Name: Forma Cucine
HQ Location: Italy, Ve, San, 25 Via G. Di Vittorio, 30029
Company description: Forma Cucine specializes in designing and manufacturing innovative kitchen solutions, focusing on functional and stylish elements that enhance everyday cooking experiences. The company's mission is to create high-quality, practical kitchen accessories that maximize space and efficiency without compromising on aesthetics. Their flagship product, the Fly Vano sottopensile, exemplifies this commitment, offering a sleek under-shelf storage solution that is both space-saving and user-friendly. Forma Cucine caters to a diverse clientele, including homeowners, interior designers, and kitchen retailers, and collaborates with various partners to deliver tailored solutions that meet the needs of modern living. With a target market that values both design and functionality, Forma Cucine aims to transform kitchens into organized and beautiful spaces.

Name: XTONE | Porcelanosa Grupo
Company description: XTONE: Leader in large-format porcelain surfaces. Redefining design through innovation, durability, and textures.   XTONE is a global leader in large-format porcelain surfaces, created from the purest natural minerals through advanced technology and design innovation.   Available in 6, 12 and 20 mm thicknesses, XTONE delivers unmatched versatility for every application: kitchen countertops, table tops, façades, furniture, bathroom pieces, wall coverings, and flooring.   As a true trendsetter and trailblazer in texture development, XTONE sets new benchmarks in both aesthetics and performance — offering surfaces that are not only durable and functional, but also deeply expressive and refined.   More than a surface, XTONE is a material for creativity: THE TEXTURE REVOLUTION.

Name: CUBO DESIGN
Company description: Il gruppo Cubo Design è nato nel 2006 in provincia di Teramo. È specializzato nella produzione e nella commercializzazione di manufatti in legno e altri materiali destinati alla fabbricazione e all’assemblaggio di mobili. Vanta una lunghissima esperienza nel settore delle cucine componibili che risale al 1960, quando l’imprenditore Giuseppe Arangiaro dette inizio a un’avventura di grande successo. In breve tempo, Cubo Design ha conquistato il mercato italiano riuscendo a imporsi da protagonista anche in quello internazionale. Fanno parte del gruppo, guidato dal CEO Antonio Arangiaro, Miton Cucine e Binova. Il primo brand propone collezioni “democratiche” pensate per dare a tutti la possibilità di fruire di prodotti di elevatissima qualità a prezzi concorrenziali. Binova, invece, è un’azienda che dal 1958 rappresenta un punto di riferimento nel comparto delle cucine di alta gamma.  Punto di forza del gruppo è il concetto di Made…inside, ossia il passaggio dalle isole, situate in località diverse, a un metodo produttivo concentrato esclusivamente nello stabilimento aziendale. La sede di Cubo Design è Factory-One, un polo avveniristico di 25.000 mq che è stato fra i primi del settore Legno-Arredo a essere progettato secondo il concetto di Impresa 4.0. Macchinari tecnologici avanzati e intercomunicanti, sottoposti al continuo controllo di manodopera specializzata, consentono di accogliere le richieste dei clienti garantendo altissimi standard qualitativi. Grandissima l’attenzione alle tematiche della sostenibilità ambientale non solo grazie all’impegno del gruppo di realizzare prodotti a km 0 riducendo del 25% gli spostamenti logistici, ma anche tramite l’acquisizione di specifiche certificazioni (come la FSC che assicura che il legno usato nelle collezioni Cubo Design provenga da una gestione responsabile delle foreste) e l’uso di vernici all’acqua, indicate per ambienti domestici e lavorativi salubri.  .

Name: Standard Hidráulica
Company description: Standard Hidráulica nace en 1975 en Barcelona, con una filosofía basada en la calidad, el servicio, la cuidada atención al cliente, la constante investigación tecnológica y el respeto al medio ambiente. Gracias a todos estos factores Standard Hidráulica se ha convertido en el socio de referencia en el sector de la conexión y control de fluidos y grifería de cocina y baño tanto en el ámbito residencial, como no-residencial y obra civil. En 2019, se constituye el Grupo STH (Grupo industrial internacional) formado por Standard Hidráulica (Montcada i Reixac, BCN y Pinto, MAD) y STH Westco (Leigh, Manchester, UK). Y en 2021 el Grupo STH incorpora dos nuevas empresas; STH Southern Africa (Sudáfrica) con base en Johannesburgo, Port Elizabeth y Ciudad del Cabo y STH HELLAS con base en Atenas (Grecia). Con estas integraciones se contribuye enormemente a reforzar a nuestro grupo industrial con amplia experiencia en el área logística y comercial. El grupo STH cuenta en la actualidad con una plantilla de más de 219 empleados y más de 35.000 m2 de instalaciones distribuidas en procesos de producción, almacenes, oficinas técnicas y laboratorios, oficinas y showrooms. La disposición de plantas de producción propias nos permite garantizar una excelente fabricación y control de la calidad, seguridad y fiabilidad de nuestros productos y sistemas. STH además es una empresa certificada con la ISO 9001 y la ISO 14001, y con la aplicación de la Ley de Igualdad, promoviendo acciones dentro de la empresa que favorecen la igualdad de oportunidades para todo el personal de STH.

Name: REJS Group Furniture Fittings And Accesories
Company description: Bespoke solutions for the manufacture of kitchens by cabinet-makers and industrial producers.

Name: Unilin Decor
Company description: Vertically integrated supplier of melamine faced chipboard and derivative products (cut, edged, and drilled furniture components, shelving and ready-to-assemble furniture) to the furniture and kitchen industry, to the professional trade channel and to big box DIY chains

Name: Vipp
Company description: We dream of a world with fewer but better products, favouring staying power over fading trends. Whether it is developing a bin, rethinking the modular kitchen, creating a furniture line or hosting the Vipp Hotel, we measure the quality of products and concepts on their long-term ability to provide an experience out of the ordinary. It began as a love story. Sometimes winning the lottery leads to more than just temporary excitement. When Vipp founder Holger Nielsen won a car on his ticket to the local soccer stadium in 1932 it was the beginning of Vipp. He just did not know it. He sold the car, bought a metal press and few years later, when his wife Marie needed a bin for her hairdressing salon, he went to his one-man workshop and crafted what today is known as the Vipp pedal bin.  Holger could not have imagined that the pedal-controlled bin he designed in 1939 would eventually sow the seed for a full-blown design universe of accessories, furniture and kitchens. Nor that his bin would be a catalyst for a design hotel concept. Vipp is still a family-owned, independent, Danish design company run by Holger’s daughter, Jette Egelund, her two children Kasper and Sofie together with 45 employees in Copenhagen, Denmark.

Name: Thermex Scandinavia A/S
Company description: Thermex — siden 1958 Thermex designer og udvikler emhætter og emfang — og har gennem næsten 50 år leveret løsninger til både private og erhvervslivet. Vi har Danmarks største sortiment af emfang og emhætter — og har vores produkter udstillet hos flere end 900 køkken- og hårde hvidevareforhandlere over hele Danmark. Thermex har hovedsæde nord for Limfjorden i Hjørring, hvor der er hav til alle sider, højt til loftet — og masser af frisk luft. Det er inspireret af disse rammer, at vi designer og udvikler vores produkter. Foruden hovedsædet i Hjørring har Thermex afdelinger i Rødovre, Norge, Sverige og Spanien.

Name: Oresi S.r.o.
Company description: Oresi je specialista na kuchyně. Děláme jen to, co umíme nejlépe. Proto se trvale zaměřujeme výhradně na kuchyně. V každém našem produktu jsou uloženy roky zkušeností našich specializovaných konstruktérů, designérů a architektů, kteří se důsledně věnují jen neustálému rozvíjení kvality, estetických parametrů a uživatelského komfortu pro srdce každého bydlení – pro kuchyň. Díky přízni našich zákazníků jsme jedničkou na trhu. Velmi si toho vážíme a snažíme se tuto jedinečnou pozici využívat k rozvoji našich produktů a ve prospěch jeho budoucích uživatelů. Oresi je šampión v každé třídě. Naši nabídku tvoří tři značky: kuchyně střední třídy Dolti, jejich designová nadstavba Dolti Collection by Andrea Capovilla, německé prémiové kuchyně Livanza a luxusní německé kuchyně Bauformat. V každé třídě a tedy i v každé cenové kategorii vám přinášíme bezkonkurenčně nejlepší poměr výkonu a ceny. Jsme připraveni kdykoli vás o tom přesvědčit a rádi srovnáme naši nabídku s jakýmkoli prodejcem nebo výrobcem. Oresi je největší prodejce kuchyní. Od našich dodavatelů nakupujeme díky dlouhodobým vztahům a pozici největšího prodejce kuchyní ty nejlepší komponenty za mimořádně nízké ceny, využíváme jen ty nejefektivnější výrobní technologie a naši konstruktéři stále hledají nová nejchytřejší řešení. K firemní kultuře Oresi patří vždy i bohatý bonusový program a široké spektrum záruk. Nákup u Oresi se vám prostě musí vyplatit.

Name: Vanden Borre Kitchen
Company description: Vanden Borre Kitchen, c’est l’alliance de 2 experts : FBD, le spécialiste de la cuisine équipée en franchise et Vanden Borre qui apporte du choix, du service, des garanties, tout cela pour mettre le consommateur en confiance. ---------------------------------------------- Vanden Borre Kitchen, dat is een samenwerking van 2 experten: FBD, de specialist van de uitgeruste keuken franchise en Vanden Borre die keuze, diensten en garanties aanbrengt, alles om de klant vertrouwen te geven.

Name: ROCASA
HQ Location: Spain, Asturias, Avilés, 35/37 Avenida De Lugo, 33401
Company description: materiales de construcción, reformas de baños y cocinas, diseño de interiores, suministro y colocación de suelos cerámicos y de madera, suministro y colocación de accesorios de baños, mamparas, inodoros, lavabos etc...

Name: Dica
Company description: Dica cuenta con una consolidada experiencia en la fabricación de mobiliario para el hogar, siendo líder en su sector a nivel nacional. Su colección incluye mobiliario para la cocina, sistemas para el hogar, armarios, baños y muebles auxiliares. Con este completo desarrollo de producto Dica se diferencia en el mercado gracias un producto con diseños y materiales exclusivos y con una gran capacidad de fabricación a medida. Su espíritu vanguardista junto a la calidad y versatilidad del producto busca inspirar, crear enlaces y conexiones entre los espacios y el mobiliario Dica.   En constante evolución desde 1984, Dica sigue manteniendo vivo el espíritu de empresa familiar, con un equipo multidisciplinar y la tecnología como referencia.  Dica es una marca joven, con un producto consolidado y en constante evolución. Presentes en España con más de 170 tiendas, amplía sus fronteras a nivel internacional exportando a Europa y América. Dica crea ambientes inspiradores que respiran confort y bienestar. Para ello, centra sus esfuerzos en inversiones constantes y una mejora continua de los procesos productivos para ofrecer mejor producto y servicio cada día, combinando las técnicas artesanales con la tecnología más avanzada. Gracias a estas inversiones ha logrado crear un proceso de trabajo que permite poder diseñar, fabricar 100% a medida y bajo pedido cualquier proyecto.  Dica trabaja continuamente por una sostenibilidad económica, social y medioambiental. “Creamos con nuestro equipo, colaboradores y clientes relaciones duraderas basadas en el compromiso de valores compartidos.”

Name: KFA Armatura
Company description: KFA Armatura is a Polish company with over a century of tradition, established in 1922 and based in Nisko, Podkarpacie. Specializing in the production of bathroom and kitchen faucets, aluminum radiators, valves, and shower cabins, KFA Armatura is committed to innovation and environmental responsibility. The company aims to provide comfortable and ergonomic solutions, such as their universal clickclack washbasin drains, which are designed for ease of use and durability, making them ideal for both residential and public spaces. KFA Armatura serves a diverse clientele, including individual consumers and businesses, and maintains strong partnerships within the industry, focusing on expanding its presence in international markets. With a mission to blend tradition with modernity, KFA Armatura continues to prioritize sustainability and customer satisfaction while developing new, eco-friendly products.

Name: IKEA Baleares & Canarias
Company description: IKEA Baleares & Canarias is a leading retailer in the Balearic and Canary Islands, specializing in functional, affordable, and sustainable furniture and home products since 1981. The company is dedicated to improving everyday life for its customers by offering a diverse range of products, including furniture for every room, storage solutions, and home accessories, all designed with a focus on Scandinavian style and practicality. With stores located in Gran Canaria, Tenerife, and Lanzarote, as well as various IKEA points across the islands, the company serves a wide clientele, including families and individuals seeking stylish and versatile home solutions. IKEA Baleares & Canarias is committed to sustainability, implementing responsible practices in production and energy efficiency. The company actively engages with the community through initiatives such as children's contests and local projects, reflecting its dedication to social responsibility. The mission of IKEA is to create a better everyday life for the many people, a vision that is evident in their innovative product offerings and customer-centric services. In addition to its extensive product range, IKEA Baleares & Canarias specializes in modular furniture and home installations, providing professional services such as the assembly of modular wardrobes, kitchen installations, and bathroom fittings. This commitment to enhancing the home experience ensures that customers save time and receive quality service. The company also partners with local suppliers to offer fresh food options in its bistros and restaurants, enriching the overall shopping experience. Targeting homeowners in the Balearic and Canary Islands, IKEA Baleares & Canarias aims to be a one-stop solution for all home furnishing needs, combining affordability with quality and convenience. Through its dedication to customer satisfaction and sustainable practices, the company continues to play a vital role in the home furnishing market of the islands.

Name: KitchenTime
Company description: KitchenTime is an e-commerce site that offers high quality kitchenware at good prices. We strive to be the number one choice for customers shopping for kitchen utensils, bake ware, and everything in between that is connected to our lives in the kitchen.  We’re continuously expanding our already grand selection of products, with the goal to offer the widest variety of kitchenware online.  We’re always looking for new talent and ways of adding great ideas to the table; so don’t hesitate to contact us if you find our business interesting!   We believe the kitchen to be the heart of every home, and we’re fascinated of what can be accomplished there. With the help of great products you can easily add quality to the time spent in the kitchen, as well as gaining more time to enjoy the food you created. Therefore we strive to offer products helping our customers to succeed in the kitchen.

Name: Bravat Global
Company description: 150 years of award-winning design and innovation. Elevating bathrooms and living spaces with stunning design and technology.  From our innovative mixers and shower systems to our exclusive selection of ceramic sanitary ware, we are committed to designing products that combine form and function. Our philosophy is to push the boundaries of innovation and design to create exceptional bathroom and kitchen fixtures that look beautiful and function flawlessly. Our mission is to provide our customers with the highest level of satisfaction and enhance their quality of life through our products. We take pride in our dedication to design, innovation, and technology; our products are a testament to this. Our contemporary designs are crafted with pure and thin lines, creating a sleek, modern appearance that complements any style. As a global leader in bathroom solutions, we understand the importance of offering complete solutions. That's why we are excited to introduce our new collection of color and finish combinations, allowing you to personalize the aesthetics of your bathroom further. At Bravat, we are committed to providing the best possible solutions to our partners. Our focus on design, innovation, and technology ensures that our products meet the highest quality and functionality standards. We understand your success depends on access to a complete range of products and services. Therefore, we offer full bathroom and accessories solutions to meet your needs. Enjoy life with Bravat. SALES NEWTWORK: https://www.bravat.com/index.php?m=content&c=index&a=lists&catid=77

Name: TATAY S.A.
Company description: With more than 85 years in business, Plasticos Tatay is a family owned plastic producer and distributor with headquarters in Barcelona (Spain) and three subsidiaries in France, Italy and Portugal. We operate in 54 countries worldwide.  TATAY equals Quality & Design in Household, Bath and Garden products. With these values in mind, our internal design and R&D team develops innovative products with state-of-the-art materials to offer durable, user-friendly and practical solutions to our customers. Our main Product Categories are:  HOUSEHOLD: Cleaning, Organizing, Food, Take Away, Kitchen Accessories BATH: Hydrotherapy, Shower Accessories, Sanitary, Bathroom  Collections, Wall Collections, Batheroom Complements. GARDEN: Surface Irrigation (Metal & Blue line), Hoses and Garden Accessories Today, TATAY products can be found almost everywhere including mass retail, hardware and home center stores, supermarkets, department stores and specialty stores.

Name: PROSTAHL Srl
HQ Location: Italy, Trentino-alto Adige, Caldaro Sulla Strada Del Vino, 14 Località Zona Artigianale, 39052
Company description: Prostahl is the specialist in manufacture of top quality hygienic furniture in accordance with the DIN Standard in all sizes for commercial kitchens, self-service buffets and bars.

Name: Tulp Keukens
Company description: Tulp Keukens is een toonaangevende Nederlandse keukenfabrikant die zich richt op het ontwerpen en produceren van op maat gemaakte keukens. Met een sterke focus op kwaliteit en duurzaamheid, biedt het bedrijf een breed scala aan stijlen, materialen en apparatuur, waardoor elke keuken uniek is en perfect aansluit bij de wensen van de klant. Tulp Keukens heeft een eigen fabriek in Nederland, waar vakmanschap en innovatieve technieken samenkomen om hoogwaardige keukens te creëren. Het bedrijf bedient een diverse klantenkring, van gezinnen die hun droomkeuken willen realiseren tot horecaondernemers die op zoek zijn naar functionele en esthetische oplossingen. Daarnaast is Tulp Keukens actief in sponsoring, zoals de Tulp Hoofdklasse, wat hun betrokkenheid bij de gemeenschap onderstreept. Met showrooms verspreid over heel Nederland, biedt Tulp Keukens persoonlijke begeleiding en advies om klanten te helpen bij het maken van de beste keuzes voor hun keuken.

Name: METALTEX ITALIA SPA
Company description: FABBRICAZIONE DI STOVIGLIE, PENTOLAME, VASELLAME, ATTREZZI DA CUCINA E ACCESSORI CASALINGHI, ARTICOLI METALLICI PER L ARREDAMENTO DI STANZE DA BAGNO.

Name: Opti-Wohnwelt
Company description: Opti-Wohnwelt is a leading kitchen studio located in Gifhorn, specializing in providing high-quality kitchen solutions tailored to meet individual customer needs. The company is dedicated to delivering an exceptional customer experience, from the initial consultation to the final installation, ensuring that every client’s kitchen dreams are realized. With a strong focus on customer satisfaction, evidenced by over 11,500 satisfied customers, Opti-Wohnwelt offers a wide range of kitchen styles, catering to diverse tastes and budgets, including both high-end and affordable options. The company collaborates with renowned manufacturers to provide a variety of designs, ensuring that every kitchen is not only functional but also aesthetically pleasing. Opti-Wohnwelt's mission is to make the kitchen buying process simple and enjoyable, supported by comprehensive services such as virtual consultations and professional installation. Their target market includes homeowners in and around Gifhorn looking for personalized kitchen solutions, making them a trusted partner in home improvement.

Name: NEOSET S.A.
Company description: NEOSET FURNITURE COMPANY Η NEOSET δραστηριοποιείται στην ελληνική αγορά τα τελευταία 30 χρόνια, ενώ ο αριθμός των καταστημάτων της αγγίζουν τα 100 σε ολόκληρη την ελληνική επικράτεια. Τα εμπορικά σήματα της εταιρείας περιλαμβάνουν Neoset, Neoset Κουζίνα, Νεοκατοικείν, Skouropoulos και Neowood.

Name: Giostyle S.p.A.
Company description: Giostyle S.p.A. è una società industriale italiana a vocazione nazionale e internazionale che svolge la propria attività nell’ambito degli accessori per la cucina, per la casa e per il tempo libero. Tutte le persone che lavorano in Giostyle S.p.A. sono ispirate ai principi di lealtà, correttezza, professionalità, trasparenza ed efficienza, sia nei confronti del mercato che nei confronti del consumatore finale. I brand che ha in portafoglio Giostyle S.p.A. sono Gio’Style e Ordinett. Nata nel 1949, Gio’Style è leader in Italia nei contenitori in plastica per la conservazione degli alimenti, nei frigo portatili e nelle borse termiche: grazie ai suoi prodotti i consumatori possano gustarsi il piacere e la gioia del buon cibo, sia in casa che fuori casa. Gio’Style crede in un mondo dove non esistono più gli sprechi alimentari: questi hanno un nefasto impatto sulla biodiversità e sul clima, senza considerare il fatto che ogni anno in tutto il mondo viene buttata una quantità di cibo pari a 4 volte quella che servirebbe a sfamare le quasi 800 milioni di persone che sono denutrite. Ridurre lo spreco alimentare non significa quindi solo prendere coscienza dello sperpero economico ma implica una consapevolezza più forte legata al nostro futuro e alla tutela del nostro pianeta.  La nostra missione è conservare cibi e bevande preservandone al meglio le caratteristiche organolettiche: il cibo è l’elemento attraverso cui passa la convivialità, attraverso cui si scandiscono le giornate, l’elemento che unisce le persone e le famiglie e conservarlo è il valore tangibile più prezioso dei nostri tempi. Gio’Style è una storia italiana che continuiamo a scrivere con passione affinché venga prestata tutta l’attenzione e la cura necessaria perché che questi valori vengano diffusi e preservati nel tempo. Ordinett, altro brand di Giostyle S.p.A., da più di 45 anni è protagonista internazionale dell’organizzazione della casa: aiutiamo le persone ad organizzare al meglio il proprio guardaroba e gli spazi di casa con soluzioni pratiche, creative ed eco-compatibili che rispondono alle esigenze di chi oltre all’ordine non può rinunciare al gusto. Ci piace proporre ai nostri consumatori prodotti funzionali perché organizzare è sinonimo di praticità, una casa ordinata e ben organizzata è una casa efficiente, una casa fatta di persone che hanno più tempo per sé ed evitano sprechi di spazio e quindi di denaro.

Name: JOMOO Group | Europe
Company description: JOMOO Group is a highly dynamic and innovative international kitchen and bathroom group that makes a better home a reality for everyone, everywhere. Our family of brands includes leading European luxury brands as well as the best brands for the young generation in China. We offer holistic design and an innovative product and service portfolio that improves the lives of millions every day. JOMOO Group is a global company with more than 15,000 employees worldwide and distribution in more than 120 countries.

Name: REDDY Keukens Nederland
Company description: REDDY is een franchiseformule en geldt als toonaangevende keten in de Duitse keukenretailmarkt. Sinds de oprichting in 1994 heeft de onderneming een succesvolle weg afgelegd. Name: XL-BYGG Ski
Company description: Proffe folk. Proffe produkter. Vi har vært her siden 1919. Gjennom snart 100 år har vi  lært at de valgene vi gjør i forhold til sortiment er med  på å sikre et godt sluttresultat for deg som kunde. Hos oss møter du fagfolk med høy kompetanse på sine respektive områder. Du får kvalitet i alle ledd, fra den minste spikeren til den største kjøkken-innredningen. Proffene har visst det lenge. Og stadig flere av dem handler her hos oss. For de vet at vi leverer når vi skal, at vi har det de skal ha, og at vi er til å stole på. Bare kjente merkevarer. Det finnes ikke noe som heter Ski Bygg-kjøkkenet. Ikke Ski Bygg-parkett heller. Våre kjøkken heter Sigdal og Mobalpa. Parketten vi selger kommer fra Haro og Kährs. Vi holder oss til gode merkevarer av høy kvalitet, produkter som i årevis har bevist at de duger. Fordi vi mener at alt du gjør, alt du kjøper, enten det handler om nybygg eller oppussing, skal øke verdien av boligen. Vi har alt. Men ikke fra alle. Vi velger våre leverandører med omhu. Vi kvalitetssikrer dem og velger produkter hvor pris og kvalitet står i forhold til hverandre.  Og vi tør påstå at vi har alt. Alt du trenger til innredning av boligen. Alt innenfor kjøkken, innredning, benkeplater og hvitevarer. Det samme med garderobe, bad, gulv og dører. Men vi har ikke alle merker. Bare de vi mener er best. Ikke fordi vi mener andre merker enn våre er dårlige, men fordi vi heller vil være veldig gode på noen få merker enn middels gode på mange. Med vår kompetanse gir vi deg trygghet og faglig veiledning. Ski Bygg er stedet hvor profesjonelle byggere, selvbyggere og forbrukere møtes. Vårt hovedanlegg ligger i Ski. Vi har også fire proffsentere i Ås, Askim Enebakk og Fredrikstad. I tillegg har vi en egen Mobalpa butikk på Grini. Gjennom våre flotte utstillinger viser vi hvilke valgmuligheter som finnes for deg som kunde. Til sammen er vi 150 ansatte.

Name: Gruppo Cucine
Company description: Η οικογένεια Λεβεντάκη μετράει 53 χρόνια ενασχόλησης και εμπειρίας με την κατασκευή και τοποθέτηση επίπλων κουζίνας. Ο Κωνσταντίνος Λεβεντάκης το 1970 ξεκίνησε την δραστηριότητα αυτή, με κόπο και δυσκολίες, χωρίς να έχει καμία δυνατότητα να πάρει ρίσκα, αφού πίσω του είχε μια οικογένεια με τρία παιδιά που έπρεπε να στηρίξει. Πέραν όμως των προκλήσεων αυτών, τα καρκινογόνα υλικά που χρησιμοποιούνταν τότε κατά κόρων για την κατασκευή των επίπλων κουζίνας, του δημιούργησαν ένα σοβαρό αναπνευστικό πρόβλημα που τον σταμάτησε προσωρινά... Το γεγονός αυτό αποτέλεσε για τον ίδιο ένα κίνητρο, καθώς τότε ήταν που άρχισε να αναζητά εργοστάσια τα οποία να χρησιμοποιούν μόνο οικολογικά και φιλικά προς τον άνθρωπο υλικά. Το αποτέλεσμα; Οι πρώτες του συνεργασίες με επώνυμα Ιταλικά εργοστάσια που διασφάλιζαν όχι μόνο τα επιθυμητά αισθητικά αποτελέσματα αλλά κυρίως τη χρήση υλικών χωρίς κινδύνους για την ανθρώπινη υγεία. Μαζί συστρατεύτηκε άμεσα ολόκληρη η οικογένειά του με τα παιδιά, Άρη, Γιώργο και Σοφία να ξεκινούν ένα δύσκολο ταξίδι ως «Ομάδα» εξού και το όνομα: Gruppo Cucine. Η αρχή δεν έγινε από κάποιο γραφείο ή κατάστημα, αλλά από το παιδικό τους δωμάτιο έχοντας ως πυξίδα έναν απλό ηλεκτρονικό υπολογιστή, ένα δανεικό πρόγραμμα σχεδιασμού κουζίνας και μια βαλίτσα από δείγματα. Οι «εναλλακτικές λύσεις» έπαψαν να υπάρχουν ως ενδεχόμενο, ενώ η αποτυχία δεν υπήρχε ούτε ως ιδέα, ούτε ως λέξη. Χωρίς κεφάλαιο, χωρίς δάνεια ή κρατική βοήθεια, με μόνη κινητήρια δύναμη το ένστικτο, το πάθος και το όραμά τους να αλλάξουν το Status quo στον χώρο των επίπλων κουζίνας, ξεκίνησαν αυτό το όμορφο αλλά δύσκολο και απαιτητικό ταξίδι. Το ταξίδι αυτό κρατά για την «ομάδα», που πλέον αριθμεί πάνω από 100 μέλη, 21 δημιουργικά χρόνια!

KG- steht für höchste Ausführungs- und Servicequalität, kombiniert mit langjähriger Erfahrung im Einrichtungsbereich, und gilt daher als verlässlicher Partner für alle Bauherren.  Er beschäftigt sich mit dem Bau, dem Verkauf, der Verwaltung und der Vermietung von Immobilien. Name: Top Tank S.r.o.
HQ Location: Czech Republic, Praha, Prague, 1153/13 Janáčkovo Nábřeží, 150 00
Company description: Historie čerpacích stanic Free1 GAS spadá do května roku 2004, kdy byla otevřena první čerpací stanice Free1 v Pavlově Studenci. Postupně začala společnost TOP TANK s.r.o. budovat síť čerpacích stanic, a to otevřením další Free1 v Kraslicích v srpnu roku 2005. Květen roku 2006 byl pro společnost významný otevřením čerpací stanice v Aši. Na konci roku 2007 byla otevřena další čerpací stanice v Potůčkách. Rok 2008 byl pak z hlediska počtu otevření čerpacích stanic nejhojnější. V lednu roku 2008 se otevírala prozatím nejmenší čerpací stanice Pernink, v dubnu pak následoval Mníšek v Krušných horách a Rozvadov, v říjnu 2008 byla otevřena čerpací stanice Free1 v Hranicích u Aše. V září 2009 se síť rozrostla o další provozovnu v Hoře sv. Šebestiána. O rok později, v září 2010, jsme slavnostně otevírali novou provozovnu na dálničním přechu v Rozvadově, která je jako první provozovna pod značkou Free1 GAS obohacena nejen o gastronomickou nabídku teplé kuchyně pro naše zákazníky, ale i o sport bar, hernu a směnárnu. V současné době společnost Top Tank s.r.o. provozuje 30 čerpacích stanic s logem Free1 GAS. V roce 2016 společnost Top Tank s.r.o. začala s budováním jednotné koncepce čerpacích stanic a rozšiřovat jejich nabídku. Na Rozvadově vznikla první čerpací stanice s přidruženým obchodem pod značkou Global free. V roce 2017 bude dokončen projekt obchodního domu s prodejní pasáží na hraničním přechodu Folmava o celkové prodejní ploše 3 700 m2.

Name: Madebydas
Company description: Madebydas specializes in creating bespoke kitchen solutions and custom cabinetry, emphasizing quality, sustainability, and unique design. The company’s mission is to provide clients with personalized, high-quality products that reflect their individual tastes and needs, ensuring that every piece is not only functional but also a source of joy in their homes. Madebydas is committed to using sustainable materials and practices, balancing ecological, economic, and social responsibilities in their production processes. Their target market includes homeowners seeking tailored interior solutions, as well as dealers who represent their products. With a wide range of over 2,500 colors and materials, Madebydas collaborates with top suppliers to deliver exceptional craftsmanship and design, making each project a unique reflection of the client's vision.

Name: GRUPPOTURISRL
HQ Location: Italy, Apulia, Modugno, 6 Via Vigili Del Fuoco Caduti In Servizio, 70026
Company description: The company is one of the first producers of kitchens in Italy and boasts of kitchens with excellent design, available in many colors, with valuable finishes and resistant materials. In keeping with the trend to satisfy customers’ needs, a highly qualified staff is able to assist the Client in planning his own personal solutions.

Name: Wolly & Co.
Company description: We design and produce home textiles, home accessories, kitchen tools, seasonal items, and more. Our process spans from initial ideas and sketches to final delivery to each customer. We have our own design team, which approaches products with a creative and unconventional mindset. They constantly stay updated on the latest trends in Scandinavian and international design, ensuring that we always deliver collections aligned with current trends and tailored to each customer’s profile and preferences. Our passion lies in seeking inspiration for new, exquisite lifestyle products from around the globe – we create beautiful homes.

Name: Poly Pool S.p.A.
Company description: Poly Pool S.p.A. is a leader in the production and commercialization of electric material and electrical household appliances in the Italian and international large-scale retail channel. With the brands Poly Pool, Quality, Secur, Ardes and Medicura, the company is present in all the chain stores of the D.I.Y., electronics, food, hardware and household large-scale distribution, with a range of more than 5000 articles, from electric material with civil and industrial application to small domestic appliances for the house, kitchen and personal care. Poly Pool has been a reliable partner for over 35 years in the process of supplying, from the planning stages to the production, from the selection of the best suppliers worldwide to the accurate quality control of single products, in alignment with the highest international standards. The commercial network developed in Italy and other 40 foreign countries and internal logistic structure, with 40.000 m² of warehouses and productive units, allow the company to satisfy the service requests from the national and international distribution, granting daily deliveries throughout the territory, also in single stores. The company is also supply partner of “private label” products and takes care of the selection, supply and all the stages of commercialization. Poly Pool S.p.A is part of the industrial group Scame Parre S.p.A, leader in the production of electric material with civil, industrial and tertiary application. This ensure Poly Pool a supply of Made in Italy products, both for the electric material and for some electrical appliances, made in modern manufacturing plants guaranteed by the main European Quality Institutions (IMQ, VDE, UTE, KEMA-KEUR, SEMKO, NEMKO, etc.).

Name: Mepra S.p.A.
HQ Location: Italy, Lombardy, Lumezzane, 176 Via Virgilio Montini, 25065
Company description: Mepra, leading Italian manufacturer of design products for table and kitchen, is a family owned factory, founded in 1947 by the Prandelli family in Lumezzane, near the Italian Alps, where the manufacturing plant is still located. MEPRA portraits Italian tradition, culture, and style. They are proponents of the "Made in Italy" concept in which through fashion, design,  and food, is being shown worldwide what the meaning of Italian life style truly is. In able to respond everyday to the most refined customer’s needs, MEPRA has also developed a network of cooperation with some of the most famous designers (a name for all: Angelo Mangiarotti), as well as with other young talented avant-garde designers who still work for the company full-time or by  project. Creativity and design are everyday supported by the commitment for the best quality.  High quality of raw materials, high thickness, and perfect finishing are inalienable requirements for MEPRA. 100%  of the production is controlled by the quality department. Today the company is present in more than 60 countries around the world. They supply the best Sores, hotels and restaurants who have customers with a refined taste for Italian Design, Style, and Class.

Name: Glaskoch B.Koch Jr. GmbH & Co. KG
Company description: Glaskoch B.Koch Jr. GmbH & Co. KG is a dynamic company renowned for its expertise in the design and production of high-quality jewelry, glassware, and kitchen accessories. With a strong commitment to craftsmanship and innovation, Glaskoch aims to create elegant and personalized products that resonate with the individual styles of its customers. The company's diverse product range includes customizable jewelry collections, such as the popular Clip & Mix series, alongside exquisite glassware and stylish home decor items suitable for various occasions.  Glaskoch's mission is to provide unique and customizable products that cater to a wide array of tastes and occasions, making them perfect for personal use or as thoughtful gifts. The company serves a broad market, appealing to individual consumers seeking distinctive gifts as well as businesses looking for personalized promotional items. In addition to its retail offerings, Glaskoch collaborates with partners like LEONARDO to support charitable initiatives, ensuring that a portion of sales contributes to international aid projects. By targeting a market that values quality and personalization, Glaskoch is dedicated to delivering exceptional products that inspire creativity and enhance everyday living. The company’s vision encompasses not only the enhancement of its customers' lives through functional and aesthetically pleasing designs but also a commitment to social responsibility, making a positive impact in the community. Through its innovative approach and dedication to quality, Glaskoch B.Koch Jr. GmbH & Co. KG continues to elevate home experiences and foster meaningful connections with its clients and partners.

Name: Lafenice
Company description: Lafenice srl è un’azienda di distribuzione all’ingrosso del settore ITS che vanta 6 punti vendita nelle regioni Marche e Abruzzo, circa 60 tra dipendenti e collaboratori, una vasta offerta di prodotti professionali idrotermoidraulici e uno showroom di altissimo livello, pluripremiato per eleganza e qualità. L’azienda affonda le proprie radici negli anni Sessanta, quando l’attuale Presidente Tonino Forlì, insieme al Socio Eolo Di Concetto, dà vita alla Thermopicena, unica azienda di riferimento e di stimata competenza su un ampio territorio pluriprovinciale. Forte della sua prestigiosa tradizione e professionalità, nel 2011 la definizione di un nuovo Cda a direzione familiare segna una svolta storica importante per la società che adotta nuove politiche aziendali orientate allo sviluppo, all’innovazione e ad una solida cultura d’impresa fondata su valori comuni condivisi. Prendono così vita strategie di marketing inedite e di ampia risonanza sul territorio, che diventano un decisivo elemento di differenziazione e posizionamento sul mercato. Nell’ottobre del 2018 viene inauguato lo showroom di Teramo: uno dei fiori all’occhiello dell’azienda. Oltre ad essere stato concepito in un ampio contesto espositivo rivoluzionario rispetto al passato, il nuovo showroom aggiunge ulteriori articoli abitativi quali le cucine, le smart utilities ed i complementi di arredo. I due ingressi aprono rispettivamente al mondo termoidraulico ed a quello ceramico sanitario e dell’interior design, due mondi apparentemente distinti che vengono però a contatto attraverso l’open space in cui si apre la Smart Home: uno spazio innovativo ed intelligente, in cui tecnologia e bellezza trovano un felice compromesso estetico. Lo showroom di Teramo si colloca certamente tra i migliori showroom del territorio nazionale, e sarà utilizzato anche per degustazioni enogastronomiche, concerti, mostre e presentazioni di opere artistiche e letterarie.

Name: Interstudio
Company description: INTERSTUDIO er et anerkendt indretningshus med over 50 års erfaring med indretning af både private hjem og miljøer til det professionelle segment. Besøg INTERSTUDIO’s showroom i hjertet af København. Tag elevatoren direkte op til showroomet på 1. sal fra Antonigade 4. Velkommen. INTERSTUDIO HOME – Cosmopolitan Living Til dig som ønsker en bolig med præg af internationalt design. INTERSTUDIO Home byder på kvalitets designmøbler til alle hjemmets rum og kompetent indretningsrådgivning med udarbejdelse både space plan og designforslag. INTERSTUDIO BUSINESS – Smart Working Til dig der ønsker mere end bare møbler til din virksomhed. Hos INTERSTUDIO Business beskæftiger vi os med indretning af alle typer virksomheder, det sig være kontormiljøer, showrooms, hotel og restauration – hvor vi kan bidrage med løsninger til alle kategorier af rum og områder. Derudover tegner og producerer vi garderobe-og køkkenløsninger til ejendomsprojekter. Vi er vant til at rådgive og være med i de mange stadier af en indretningsopgave. Vi varetager opgaver såvel direkte med slutbrugeren som med de enkeltes rådgivere; arkitekter, bygherrer og entreprenører.  INTERSTUDIO’s designer brands Helt eksklusivt finder du hos INTERSTUDIO italienske Molteni&C, hvor vi i København har en Molteni&C Flagship Store med alt fra køkkener, garderober til møbler. Herudover er vi eksklusivforhandler på to øvrige italienske superbrands, nemlig Giorgetti og Lago Design. Desuden er vi Herman Miller’s Associate Dealer i Danmark, hvorfor vi varetager distribution og forhandling. Med Herman Miller og som en del af MillerKnoll familien repræsenterer INTERSTUDIO også det britiske miljøbevidste mærke NaughtOne. Hos INTERSTUDIO finder du endvidere eksklusivt det svenske SA Möbler med løsninger til kontormiljøer og Mikomax med flexrumsløsninger ifa. møde- & telefonbokse. Vores mangeårige relation til hhv. MDF Italia, STUA og USM Modular Furniture gør os til markedets mest indsigtsfulde på disse mærker.

Name: ELVILA
Company description: Founded in 1990, ELVILA is one of the leading brands in Romanian furniture market. 	The company specializes in manufacturing and trading home and office furniture. Elvila`s wide range of furniture includes: living room furniture, bedroom furniture, children room furniture, kitchen furniture, sofas, corner sets, armchairs and stools, beds and nightstands, bookcases, chest of drawers, kitchen corner sets, wardrobes, shelfs and dressings, hall stands, RELAXA mattresses, office furniture, hotel furniture. 	Elvila disposes of three furniture factories, ISO 9001:2000 certificated. The factories process all types of wood and manufacture a large range of home and office furniture. 	Elvila`s network currently comprises 48 stores placed in all major cities all over Romania, including 23 Elvila stores and 25 franchise and distributors stores.

Name: SCANPAN A/S
Company description: Made in Denmark   SCANPAN A/S is one of the world’s leading manufacturers of non-stick products and for more than five decades the company has produced Danish kitchenware of the highest quality and durability.   The core of the core   With deep roots in traditional craftsmanship, we create functional and timeless tools for modern kitchens, from households to professional kitchens. Our brand is constantly evolving and we can proudly say that we are always at the forefront of innovation and technology. Since SCANPAN’s inception in 1956, our hand cast aluminium products with patented ceramic titanium coating have formed the core of our business. Therefore, we cast all of our non-stick aluminium products at our own factory in Denmark.   The company   SCANPAN A/S exports to 45 countries. The export business is constantly growing and now represents more than 75% of our total turnover. SCANPAN is 100% Danish-owned, with the company’s headquarters and factory located near Aarhus, Denmark. SCANPAN A/S also has offices in Finland and subsidiaries in Norway, Singapore, China and the United States.

Our approach is as dynamic as it is agile, our team as diverse as passionate about its work. Founded in 2018, we work from offices all around Germany. Name: Jorge Fernández Grupo
Company description: Jorge Fernández Grupo is a leading company in the bathroom and kitchen equipment sector, dedicated to enhancing the quality of life through innovative and sustainable products. The company specializes in the design and distribution of high-quality bathroom fixtures and kitchen products, including ceramics, faucets, shower systems, and storage solutions. With a mission to create inspiring and functional spaces, Jorge Fernández Grupo aims to enhance both the aesthetic and practical aspects of homes through superior materials and innovative designs.  The brand is particularly renowned for its hansgrohe line, which features award-winning designs and advanced technologies such as EcoSmart, significantly reducing water consumption without compromising performance. This commitment to sustainability is central to the company's operations, as they strive to protect water resources and minimize environmental impact through responsible production practices and innovative water-saving technologies. Jorge Fernández Grupo serves a diverse clientele, including homeowners, architects, interior designers, and contractors, ensuring that their products meet the evolving needs of the market. The company collaborates with various partners in the construction and home improvement sectors to deliver cutting-edge solutions that cater to both residential and commercial markets. Their focus on user experience prioritizes comfort, functionality, and design, ensuring that every product contributes to moments of well-being for its users. Name: Valmi Finland
Company description: Imagine installing a system that satisfies all your snow and ice melting and underfloor heating needs without any problems. Valmi systems are the result of over 22 years of experience and meticulous research and development. Valmi offers the best quality floor warming systems available for your bathrooms, bedrooms, kitchens, sunrooms, basements, wherever the comfort of efficient radiant heat is desired for cold tile, slate, stone, or treated cement rooms. Our products can also be used under laminate floor, engineered wood, and carpet. Valmi offers safe, simple, and affordable electric radiant heat floor warming systems for your home or office. Valmi is proudly manufactured in the Finland and our team is dedicated to providing our customers with the best products and best service possible. Also company has a long history of making some of the most sophisticated, and energy efficient Snow Melt Controls for both residential and commercial applications. These controls include one of the most energy efficient control algorithms in the industry as well as making the motorized valves, and the solid brass slab sensors that become an integral part of your slab. Note that despite the sturdy design of our sensor which is meant to withstand the force of cars and trucks driving over it, the sensor is highly accurate, having temperature accuracy to 1 degree and moisture sensitivity that detects even traces of precipitation. Furthermore the sophisticated algorithm in the RSM control can operate a system using only the outdoor sensor in scenarios where introduction of slab sensors is not possible such as in retrofit applications. We strive to make Valmi your first choice for radiant floor heating systems and snow removal.

Name: Decodom
Company description: Sme Decodom, tradičná slovenská firma zaoberajúca sa výrobou a predajom kuchýň, obývačiek a ostatného skriňového nábytku. Náš príbeh je založený na viac ako storočnej histórii, rešpekte k tradičnému drevárskemu remeslu a úcte k našim zákazníkom. S prehľadom v aktuálnych trendoch, rozsiahlym know-how v nábytkárstve, víziou do budúcnosti a modernými technológiami patríme medzi lídrov vo výrobe a exporte nábytku na slovenskom trhu. Sme popredným a najväčším výrobcom kuchynského nábytku na Slovensku. Plánované kuchyne na mieru vyhotovíme pre každý, aj atypický, pôdorys. Zaraďujeme sa taktiež k významným výrobcom a najväčším slovenským exportérom nábytku do obývacích izieb. Pre harmonicky zladenú domácnosť sme vytvorili unikátny koncept nábytku na mieru, ktorý zariadi celý interiér v jednotnom dizajne. Okrem nábytku do kuchýň a obývačiek vyrábame aj nábytok do spální, detských a študentských izieb, predsiení a pracovní. Pri výrobe kladieme vysoký dôraz na kvalitu opracovania a výber prvotriednych vstupných materiálov. Naším poslaním je vyrábať a predávať kvalitný nábytok, ktorý dlhodobo zlepšuje a robí životy našich ctených zákazníkov krajšími a praktickejšími. Sme hrdí na to, že už roky môžeme byť pri tom, keď sa z domácností našich zákazníkov stávajú ich domovy. Ceníme si, že náš nábytok môže byť súčasťou ich jedinečných príbehov po celé generácie. Pridajte sa k najzručnejším nábytkárom aj vy a poďme spoločne tvoriť #JedinecnyPribehNabytku. Výhody práce v Decodome: - Zázemie stabilnej slovenskej spoločnosti s dlhoročnou tradíciou - Možnosť kariérneho postupu a sebarealizácie v pozíciách, ktoré sú dynamická, predstavujú každodenné výzvy, a ponúkajú vysoké kompetencie - Čiastočná práca z domova (home office) - Práca so skúsenými nadriadenými - Atraktívne finančné ohodnotenie - Zvýhodnenia na produktoch Decodom - Zamestnanecké a sociálne benefity - Špeciálne akcie a eventy pre zamestnancov

Name: Velthuizen Keukens En Badkamers

Niet echt serieus, meer een fantasie. “Totdat we beide een aantal weken onafhankelijk van elkaar toch op zoek zijn gegaan naar een locatie en de plannen verder uitgewerkt hadden. Toen wisten we; hier moeten we wat mee doen!”  Wat begon als een spontane gedachte tussen Bert en Johan, groeide al snel uit tot een serieus plan. In 2010 openden ze samen Velthuizen Keukens, gedreven door de wens om kwaliteit te leveren en betrokken te blijven bij jou als klant. Johan richtte zich op de keukentechniek en Bert op het bedrijfsmatige, met één gezamenlijk doel: altijd oprecht voor de klant staan en kwaliteit leveren op elk vlak. Door de jaren heen is Velthuizen gegroeid en realiseren we naast jouw droomkeuken, ook jouw droombadkamers. Daarnaast zijn wij gespecialiseerd in het uitvoeren van complete verbouwingen. Zo kunnen wij jou van A tot Z ontzorgen en kan jij genieten van je nieuwe thuis!

Thuesen Jensen har agentur på nogle af isenkrambranchens stærkeste brands: Pillivuyt, KitchenAid, Magimix, Peugeot, Gense, Rösle, Mauviel, Alfi, Lion Sabatier, og mange flere. Produktporteføljen er bred – alt lige fra el-maskiner, køkkenredskaber, spisestel, bestik til termokander, knive og kogegrej. Nøgleordet er kvalitet, hvilket gælder for både vores produkter og i vores arbejde til dagligt. THUESEN JENSEN A/S beskæftiger i dag mere end 60 medarbejdere i Norden.  Hovedparten af disse har base i Glostrup, Danmark. Hvor hovedkontor, varelager og det danske showroom er beliggende.

Name: LINCAR
HQ Location: Italy, Reggio Emilia, Reggiolo, 5 Via Enrico Fermi, 42046
Company description: Compagnia Riscaldamaneto Italiana L’eleganza del design, la cura dei dettagli e la scelta di materie prime di prima qualità sono sempre stati la carta vincente di Corisit. Realizziamo, prodotti per il riscaldamento domenistico di alta tecnologia, affidabili, innovativi e di elevata qualità, offrendovi un servizio accurato ed un rapporto di collaborazione e partnership. Seguiamo passo a passo la progettazione e la realizzazione delle termo stufe a pellets ed a legna, delle termo cucine sino ad arrivare ai recenti modelli termo – caldaia a pellets. Fanno parte di Corisit quattro aziende italiane, le quali lavorano nell’ambito del riscaldamento, mettendo sempre al primo posto design e sicurezza.

Name: Kitchen World
HQ Location: Ireland, Leinster, Dublin, 6 Long Mile Rd
Company description: An Irish-owned Family run company designing kitchens and wardrobes since 1977.  We provide an end-to-end solution for property developers and contractors seeking a kitchen supply and fit solution for their projects.  Designed, made and manufactured in Ireland. We plant native Irish trees for every kitchen manufactured.

Name: CF Petersen & Søn A/S
Company description: CF Petersen & Søn A/S er hovedafdelingen i CF Gruppen, der udover afdelingen i Køge består af afdelinger i Allerød Karise, Stenlille og Ringsted. I alt er vi 203 medarbejdere og vi omsætter for ca. 500 mio. kr. årligt. CF Gruppen er 100% privatejet med Michael Buhl som hovedaktionær, samt Jes Gravesen og Frank Bøgelund som minoritetsaktionærer. Vi er medlem af markedsføringskæden XL-BYG BYGGECENTER og XL-BYG PROFFCENTER.  XL-BYG BYGGECENTER henvender sig til det private marked, mens XL-BYG PROFFCENTER henvender sig til håndværkerkere, industri, landbrug og øvrige erhverv. Vi sælger et bredt udvalg af byggematerialer, såsom træ, plader, mursten, tagsten, døre, vinduer, gulve, fliser, haveartikler, maling, køkken, bad og meget mere. Vores kunder er et bredt mix af håndværkere, entreprenører, industri og GDS kunder, som vi alle arbejder målrettet for, at yde den bedste service inden for alle områder.

Name: Purus AB
Company description: Purus är en av Skandinaviens ledande tillverkare av produkter för badrum och kök vars huvudsakliga produktsegment är golvbrunnar, golvrännor, inomhusavlopp, rostfri inredning och rostfri sanitet. Purus starka ställning på den nordiska marknaden är ett resultat av pålitliga produkter, nytänkande och marknadens bästa kundsupport. Purus ingår i Vitas Group, en framstående koncern inom VVS-branschen där all tillverkning sker i egen regi i Sverige.

Name: RIVER INTERNATIONAL SA
Company description: River International S.A. es una empresa que, desde su fundación en 1982, se dedica a la distribución nacional de marcas internacionales de primer nivel en el sector de electrónica de consumo, menaje y pequeño electrodoméstico. Somos los distribuidores exclusivos de marcas de reconocido prestigio internacional como Alessi (Mesa, Cocina, Hogar), Ariete (Fun Cooking, Desayuno, Preparación de alimentos, Aspiración y Calefacción), Black&Decker (Aspiradores y Recogetodos), Beurer (Cuidado Personal y Bienestar),  Duux (Ventiladores, Purificadores, Humidificadores y Calefactores), ELBE (Electrónica de Consumo), Fissler (Menaje de cocina), KitchenAid (Cook Processor, Robots de Cocina), LucidSound (auriculares Gaming), Power A (Mandos y Accesorios Gaming), Ninja (Freidoras de aire, Ollas eléctricas, Batidoras de vaso, Heladeras, Procesadores de alimentos, etc), Russell Hobbs (Preparación de alimentos y Desayuno), Sage (Cafeteras y Preparación de Alimentos), Shark (Limpieza del hogar y cuidado del cabello) o Wahl (Cuidado del Cabello).

Name: Tupperware Italia S.p.A.
Company description: Tupperware rappresenta uno dei marchi più affidabili nel settore degli utensili da cucina da 75 anni, con l'impegno di fornire prodotti di alta qualità e rispettosi dell'ambiente, contribuendo allo sviluppo professionale di milioni di persone nel mondo, sia all'interno dell'organizzazione che nelle comunità in cui lavorano.

Name: ALVEUS Kitchen Sinks
Company description: Alveus is one of the largest and most successful European suppliers of kitchen sinks and related equipment, which boasts a 61-year tradition.  It is an international company, which has earned its enviable position in the kitchen equipment market by pursuing the highest quality stadards, keeping pace with modern design trends, and being a flexible and reliable business partner.  Due to its products, which boast not only outstanding quality but also an excellent quality/price ratio, Alveus is quickly and effectively strengthening its market positions in European countries.

Name: Jasa Company A/S
Company description: Jasa Company A/S er en handelsvirksomhed, som sælger kvalitetsprodukter til byggesektoren både i Danmark og de nordiske lande.  Varesortimentet er bredt og består blandt andet af et velassorteret program af beslag til døre, vinduer, køkken mm. Derudover fører vi et bredt sortiment til sikring af din bolig. Produkterne er låsekasser, cylindre, hængelåse, sikringsbeslag, vindueslåse mm. Vi sælger til industri, håndværkere og 'Gør-det-selv-markedet' via grossister, professionelle butikker og byggemarkeder. I samarbejde med arkitekter, ingeniører og kunder udvikler vi nye og tidssvarende produkter. Vi kan tilgodese specielle opgaver og ønsker og kan blandt andet sælge produkterne i private label. Udvikling og produktion af vore produkter foregår flere steder i verdenen, dog primært i Kina. Vi er konstant i bevægelse og vi arbejder fortsat på at optimere og se på nye udviklingsmuligheder på fremtidige produkter, som opfylder målene til tidens krav hvad angår design, enkelhed, funktionalitet, brugervenlighed og ikke mindst sikkerhed.

Name: Barazza
HQ Location: Italy, Veneto, Santa Lucia, 14 Via Risorgimento, 31025
Company description: Elettrodomestici di design in acciaio per cucine.

Name: Barebone SL
Company description: Barebone SL gestiona la marca comercial OUTLET PC. OUTLET PC nació de la necesidad de dar salida a material informático que no tenía cabida en el canal tradicional. El modelo cuajó rápidamente: productos de marca a precios increíbles, una salida a los problemas de los fabricantes y, lo mejor, sin conflictos de canal. La informática fue un sector afín con el que pudimos transmitir el valor de comprar la oportunidad a nuestros clientes. En la actualidad, el concepto de oportunidad lo ofrecemos transversalmente: informática, electrónica, cocina, pequeño electrodoméstico, juguetes, perfumes, etc.

Name: Rizzoli Cucine
HQ Location: Italy, Bz, Trodena Nel Parco Naturale, 1 Zona Artigianale, 39040
Company description: Rizzoli nasce oltre 100 anni fa nel cuore della Val di Fiemme, a ridosso degli imponenti e maestosi gruppi dolomitici ora Patrimonio dell'Unesco. Generazione dopo generazione, ispirata dall'ambiente montano che la circonda, l'azienda riesce a fare del proprio lavoro una vera passione, conseguendo risultati di altissimo livello qualitativo. Grazie all'intuito e alle capacità imprenditoriali della famiglia Rizzoli, l'azienda attua negli anni un rinnovo continuo dei suoi prodotti, creando un'intera gamma di cucine a legna atte a soddisfare i gusti dei consumatori più esigenti grazie all'impiego delle migliori tecnologie e materiali disponibili. Il risultato è ancora oggi un prodotto innovativo, funzionale, robusto e dall'ottimo design.

Name: SENESI Koupelny A Kuchyně
HQ Location: Czech Republic, Jihočeský, České Budějovice, 2646 Strakonická, 370 04
Company description: Historie společnosti SENESI sahá do roku 1993, kdy vznikla naše první prodejna v jihočeských Vodňanech. Máme více než 26 let zkušeností v oboru kompletního vybavení koupelen a kuchyní. Víme, že koupelna i kuchyně je pro naše zákazníky dlouhodobá investice a chceme jim čas věnovaný jejímu výběru zpříjemnit. Naše pobočky (showroomy) se vyznačují inspiračními zónami s plně zařízenými koupelnami a kuchyněmi. Zákazníkům pomáhají s výběrem naši grafici a návrháři.  Zakládáme si na zásadě, že prodejem to nekončí.
