Zákazníka chceme oslovit, inspirovat, pomoci s výběrem, zpracovat grafický návrh, zboží bez problémů dodat a zároveň mu zajistit realizaci, včetně záručního a pozáručního servisu. Chceme být těmi, kdo trendy v oboru zákazníkům přináší jako první. Naším cílem je neustále inovovat vzorkovny, abychom byli partnerem č. 1 pro všechny, kdo touží po nové koupelně nebo kuchyni.

Name: Dekeyzer
Company description: Dekeyzer is a premium kitchen design manufacturer dedicated to creating contemporary and modern kitchens that serve as the heart of the home. The company believes that a kitchen is more than just a cooking space; it is a gathering place where families connect and share experiences. With a mission to achieve timeless elegance, Dekeyzer focuses on harmonizing various materials and textures, blending the old with the new to create visually appealing and functional spaces. The company emphasizes the importance of thoughtful lighting to enhance the ambiance, ensuring that each kitchen reflects the unique character of the family it serves. Dekeyzer's target market includes discerning homeowners seeking high-quality, bespoke kitchen solutions that embody both style and practicality. Through partnerships with skilled artisans and a commitment to exceptional quality, Dekeyzer aims to deliver kitchens that are not only beautiful but also enduring.

Name: Wood Creations
Company description: Wij ontwerpen, maken en installeren complete interieurs voor woonhuizen en bedrijven. Van fauteuil, keuken, of vergadertafel, tot lichtplan, deuren, of kasten op maat. Hoogwaardig kwaliteitsproducten, want wij houden van kwaliteit. Van echt, eerlijk, sfeervol en betrouwbaar. Van mooie dingen bij elkaar laten passen. In hoe wij ontwerpen en produceren én in onze keuze voor duurzame materialen. Wat ons betreft maken we de wereld elke dag een stukje mooier.

Name: Quooker Deutschland GmbH
HQ Location: Germany, North Rhine-westphalia, Korschenbroich, 1 Myllendonker Straße, 41352
Company description: Quooker - das Original. Als erster Kochend-Wasserhahn überhaupt, hat es der Quooker vom kleinen Ort Ridderkerk in den Niederlanden in mittlerweile 14 weitere Länder geschafft. Der deutsche Hauptsitz liegt heute in Korschenbroich. Quooker ist ein Familienbetrieb, der sich auf Begeisterungsfähigkeit und Unternehmergeist gründet. In den 1970er Jahren hatte Quooker-Erfinder Henri Peteri die geniale Eingebung, einen revolutionären Wasserhahn zu erfinden - und zwar einen, der die damals neumoderne Instantsuppe wirklich instant machen würde. Die Idee des Kochend-Wasserhahns war geboren und heute ist er der neue Standard der hochwertigen Küche. Der Nutzen geht weit über die Instantsuppe hinaus. Der Quooker ist das meistgenutzte Küchengerät, da er zum Kochen, Blanchieren, Reinigen u.v.m. verwendet wird. Durch die Einführung des CUBEs im Jahr 2018 wurde der Kochend-Wasserhahn zum Wasserhahn, der alles kann. Denn nun ist es möglich, neben dem warmen, kalten und 100°C kochenden Wasser, auch gekühltes sprudelndes und stilles Wasser aus nur einem Hahn zu zapfen. Bei Quooker arbeiten wir mit großer Leidenschaft an unserer gemeinsamen Vision: Wir wollen so viele Küchen wie möglich auf eine clevere, energiesparende und sichere Weise mit kochendem Wasser versorgen. Quooker hat als Pionier eine komplette Produktkategorie entstehen lassen und wir sind permanent auf der Suche nach neuen Talenten, welche die Wachstumsgeschichte begleiten und positiv beeinflussen. Behaltet gerne unsere Stellenangebote hier auf LinkedIn oder unter https://www.quooker.de/stellenangebote im Auge.

Name: Grando Keukens
Company description: Grando Keukens is a leading provider of kitchen design and installation services, specializing in creating modern, functional, and aesthetically pleasing kitchens for residential projects. The company recently collaborated with Zabra Real Estate on the innovative W.e.s.t phase 1 project in Roeselare, where they designed and installed kitchens for 59 apartments, showcasing a commitment to timeless finishes and attention to detail that harmonizes with contemporary architecture and the surrounding green environment. Grando Keukens aims to be a reliable partner for developers and homeowners alike, offering tailored solutions that enhance living spaces. Their target market includes real estate developers, interior designers, and homeowners seeking high-quality kitchen solutions that combine style and practicality. With a focus on modernity and user-friendliness, Grando Keukens is dedicated to transforming spaces into functional works of art.

Name: Hello Kitchen
Company description: Jouw nieuwe keuken. Zo doen wij dat. Kijken, voelen, uitproberen en samenstellen. Een nieuwe keuken uitzoeken moet vooral leuk zijn. Daar gaan we bij Hello Kitchen voor zorgen én bij helpen. Bij Hello Kitchen heb je de keuze uit alle denkbare opstellingen, maten, kleuren en deuren. We inspireren je en laten alle mogelijkheden zien. In alle rust, want bij Hello Kitchen is het vanzelfsprekend dat jij je stijl en wensen aangeeft en wij je helpen waar kan. Je zou niet de eerste zijn bij wie we de keuken met een paar slimme tips veel beter maken. En bij iedere optie zie je meteen het prijsverschil, dat is transparant, bespaart tijd en energie.

Name: Muebles Ébano
HQ Location: Spain, Andalusia, Granada, Carretera De Huétor-vega, 18198
Company description: Fábrica de mobiliario de cocina

Name: GENTILI CUCINE S.R.L.
Company description: Gentili Cucine designs and manufactures kitchens and living rooms on the strength of a family craftsmanship tradition dating back almost two centuries.

Name: LMW Leichtmetallguss GmbH
Company description: Auch wir haben in einer Garage angefangen. Im Jahr 1963. Und seitdem ist nicht nur viel Zeit vergangen, sondern auch wir haben uns weiterentwickelt. Sind von Werdohl nach Neuenrade gezogen. Haben unsere Produktion vergrößert, unser Leistungsangebot aufgestockt und technisch viel dazugelernt. Denn nicht grundlos produzieren wir für namhafte Unternehmen im Bereich Küche- und Gastronomiegerätehersteller. Hochqualifiziert. Gut ausgebildet. Rund 50 Mitarbeiter/innen setzen täglich in mehreren Schichten alles daran, unsere Kunden zufrieden zu stellen. Eine schnelle Auftragserledigung , ein hervorragender Service und eine partnerschaftliche Zusammenarbeit sind Voraussetzung für intensive Kundenbeziehungen.

Name: CERAMICHE ORION S.R.L.
Company description: CON NOI SEI A CASA Grazie alle vostre scelte siamo diventati un punto di riferimento in Puglia per la vendita di pavimenti e rivestimenti, sanitari, rubinetteria, area wellness, arredo bagno, porte, cucine, arredo esterni e molti altri articoli importanti per la tua casa. Collaboriamo con i migliori brand del Made in Italy e per noi la qualità, l’assistenza e la cura del cliente sono al primo posto. Ti accompagniamo in tutte le fasi di acquisto, con consulenti dedicati che sapranno consigliarti al meglio in base alle tue esigenze. Visita la nostra sezione servizi per scoprire tutti gli optional a te dedicati.

Name: BulMag
Company description: „Трънчев“ ООД – търговска верига BulMag е българска компания със седалище и управление в град Шумен, която не спира да се разширява и развива от 1995 год. Основната ѝ дейност е търговията с бързооборотни стоки. Веригата има 17 магазина в градовете Шумен, Варна, Търговище и Бургас. Фирмата има почивна база в град Обзор, на разположение главно на нейните служители. Кухня и собствена транжорна в град Шумен. Общо във фирмата работят над 750 служители. Насърчаваме взаимното уважение и индивидуалността на хората, с които работим. Гордеем се с постиженията им – с растежa и с отдадеността на качеството. Всеки служител е изключително ценен за крайния успех на компанията.

Name: Waterford Stanley
HQ Location: Ireland, Dr, Unit 401-403 Waterford Industrial Estate Cork Road Waterford X91
Company description: An Irish company with a long and proud tradition, Waterford Stanley has been bringing warmth and comfort to homes for generations, stretching back to when the first range cooker was designed and built in Waterford, Ireland in 1936.  Over 600,000 homes throughout Ireland have one of our products, supported by a comprehensive network of stockists. PRODUCT PORTFOLIO Our product portfolio includes, electric, wood, multi fuel and pellet stoves and fires; built in appliances including hobs and ovens; air fryers and refrigeration. We also offer a comprehensive and stunning range of cooking appliances namely range cookers and barbeques from Rangemaster, AGA, La Cornue, Stanley, Novy, Kamado Joe, Masterbuilt, Rayburn, Falcon, and Mercury. PART OF MIDDLEBY RESIDENTIAL  Middleby Residential is a collection of premier international consumer brands dedicated to manufacturing and distributing many of the best known and loved kitchen appliances and interior furnishings in the world. Stanley, AGA, Rangemaster, Rayburn, Falcon, Mercury, La Cornue, Novy, Kamado Joe, Masterbuilt and Char-Griller are just some of the brands under the Middleby brand. Waterford Stanley distribute Middleby Residential brands on the Island of Ireland.

Name: Ornatop Srl
Company description: Nata nel 1994, Ornatop è oggi una delle aziende leader in Italia nella produzione di piani per cucine. Alla realizzazione di piani ed elementi in ceramica e in gres porcellanato, creati con lo scopo di produrre materiali per l'ambiente cucina resistenti, facilmente lavabili e non intaccabili da batteri, nel 1997 l'azienda affianca i piani con lastre in quarzo ampliando la gamma dei prodotti e diversificando l'offerta. Successivamente vengono inseriti i sassi anticati con elementi decorativi classici e i piani con listelli e con mosaico in gres con uno stile decisamente più moderno. A partire da gennaio 2011 la gamma dei prodotti viene integrata e completata con la realizzazione di piani, ante, pavimenti e rivestimenti con lastre di gres porcellanato in spessore ultrasottile (3/5/6mm). Il successo e l'evoluzione del gres porcellanato ha portato sul mercato anche lastre con uno spessore più "importante" (12/20 mm) arricchendo e ampliando la produzione di Ornatop. Oggi l'azienda può contare su un'area produttiva di circa 10000 mq., sulla tecnologia delle macchine più evolute del settore e su uno staff tecnico e produttivo in grado di gestire con la massima professionalità ogni richiesta. Ornatop si contraddistingue per essere un'azienda alla costante ricerca di innovazione sia dal punto di vista organizzativo che produttivo, per arrivare ad offrire un'altissima qualità e garantire al tempo stesso un servizio affidabile e adeguato ad ogni esigenza sempre in linea con le tendenze del mercato.

Name: Veneta Cucine France
Company description: Veneta Cucine est le plus grand fabricant de cuisines en Italie. Créée en 1967 à Biancade (Trévise), l'entreprise est aujourd'hui présente partout dans le monde avec ses cuisines modernes et design. Chez Veneta, le savoir-faire artisanal s'accompagne à la technologie et à la qualité des matériaux.  Veneta Cucine France développe l’image et l’activité de la marque sur tout le territoire français, à travers son vaste réseau de revendeurs. Nous sommes spécialisés dans la conception, la réalisation, la fabrication et la pose de cuisines sur mesure, équipées et parfaitement adaptées à n'importe quel type d'espace. Tous nos produits sont conformes aux dernières normes en termes d'hygiène, notamment avec l'innovation du système BBS® Bacteria Blocker Silverguard. Il s'agit d'un système de traitement antibactérien à base d’ions d’argent, qui permet de détruire 99,9 % des bactéries. Découvrez la qualité de tous nos modèles, qui savent s'intégrer parfaitement dans le décor d'une maison moderne et fonctionnelle. Qualité, robustesse et fabrication artisanale sont réunis dans tous nos meubles de cuisine. Visitez notre site Internet, et trouvez le revendeur le plus proche de chez vous : ➡️ http://bit.ly/venetacucinefrance

Name: CEGECO
HQ Location: Spain, Andalusia, Málaga, 68 Ctra. De La Azucarera Intelhorce, 29004
Company description: Cegeco is a spanish company specialised in the manufacturing and distribution of kitchen and tableware. In our 20 years of business we have built a solid presence in both Retail and Horeca markets providing confidence, top quality and competitive prices for our clients. We have more than 40.000 m2 of warehouse full of goods from our 2.000 product references by our own brands: Cok, Alar, Alorno, Atlantic and Emma. We are Cegeco, we are ready to deliver.

Name: Weber Woonwereld
Company description: Het begon allemaal in 1986 in Elburg met een meubelzaak van ca. 1000M2 midden in het centrum. Van daaruit is het bedrijf in een rap tempo uitgegroeid tot een begrip in Elburg en wijde omgeving. Aangezien 5 jaar na het ontstaan van Weber Meubelen de ruimte in het centrum te klein werd hebben wij besloten uit te breiden. In 1991 werd er een magazijn gebouwd met showroom op het industrieterrein Kruismaten, dit als aanvulling op de bestaande winkel in het centrum. In 1996 hebben wij nog een “lowbudget” winkel geopend op het industrieterrein Kruismaten aan de haven. Aangezien het niet eenvoudig was om 3 verschillende winkels te exploiteren binnen 1 plaats en omdat er een nieuw industriegebied werd ontwikkeld op een prachtige locatie in Elburg, hebben wij besloten hier een prachtig pand op te bouwen en ons te concentreren op 1 locatie. Dit is het huidige pand van Weber Woonwereld, met diverse woonwinkels onder 1 dak kunt u hier slagen voor de totale inrichting van uw woning. U kunt hier terecht voor uw meubels, accessoires, cadeauartikelen, slaapkamer, woonstoffering en zelfs voor uw keuken of open haard. Weber Woonwereld is in zijn lange bestaan uitgegroeid tot een Woonwereld van formaat. ″Weber Woonwereld, omdat je het verdient!”

Name: DKG Keukens
HQ Location: Netherlands, North Brabant, Bergen Op Zoom, 35 Drebbelstraat, 4622
Company description: DKG Keukens B.V. is een internationaal opererende en dynamische Nederlandse verkooporganisatie. Vanuit Bergen op Zoom ontwikkelen wij private label keukens voor zakelijke klanten waaronder inkooporganisaties, keukenspeciaalzaken en DIY's. De keukens worden geproduceerd in onze eigen keukenfabriek die tot de grootste en meest geavanceerde keukenfabrieken van Europa behoort. De keukens van DKG zijn kwalitatief hoogwaardige producten van Nederlandse bodem. Met een uitgebreid assortiment aan eigentijdse en functionele producten is een DKG keuken helemaal naar eigen wens samen te stellen. Op deze manier is er een DKG keuken voor iedereen.

Name: Giussani Group
HQ Location: Italy, Lombardy, Meda, 11 Via Silvio Pellico, 20821
Company description: Giussani Group racchiude il know-now di due aziende leader del settore mobile: Ge Giussani e Tecnogivex. Progetta, produce e installa arredo ufficio di prima qualità: pareti mobili, pavimenti sopraelevati e controsoffitti in cartongesso, ma anche arreda spazi produttivi, uffici direzionali e operativi, aree di attesa e accoglienza o di rappresentanza, così come ambienti cucina, living e fitness. Contattaci ora per un preventivo gratuito, studieremo insieme la migliore configurazione per arredare il tuo ufficio, lo spazio co-working o addirittura casa tua.

Name: Theofils
Company description: INTERIOR AND FITTINGS SINCE 1922 Theofils is a well known Scandinavian brand synonymous with high quality and long lasting furniture fittings; we take pride in constantly developing and nurturing our extensive range of products. One of our popular ranges is our customised range of handles on knobs. This range allows you to find the perfect shape and shade to blend in perfectly with your new or existing kitchens. This extensive range comes in a broad range of fittings to suit every need and budget from basic to premium; there is something for everyone – Scandinavian design at its best.

Name: Del Tongo Industrie s.p.a.
HQ Location: Italy, Tuscany, Arezzo, 163 Via Aretina Nord, 52041
Company description: Since 1954, kitchens from Tuscany to the whole world. Our origins. The Com­pa­ny, as we know it to­day, was crea­ted, step by step, thanks to the hard work and te­na­ci­ty of a fa­mi­ly of en­tre­pre­neurs, ge­ne­ra­ting weal­th and jobs. Del Ton­go has now be­co­me a ben­ch­mark for thou­sands of fa­mi­lies and for the qua­li­fied net of dea­lers Del Ton­go suc­cee­ded in crea­ting a so­lid re­la­tion­ship wi­th, th­rou­ghout ma­ny years of col­la­bo­ra­tion. We de­si­gn and ma­nu­fac­tu­re in Tu­sca­ny: our work, our sty­le, our de­si­gn phi­lo­so­phy are all ex­pres­sion of our land, whi­ch we ha­ve al­ways ex­por­ted all over the world. Production. All of Del Tongo’s products are entirely manufactured in our premises, this representing a quality assurance of all the design and production phases. Standards are constantly monitored and substantial resources are invested in research and technology, in a process of constant innovation. Our added value: the individual. Del Tongo is undoubtedly an industrial Company. Standardised production plants, processes, costs and times are all typical of an industrial structure having a strong innovative character. However, our real added value is represented by the way in which our manpower is trained and by the extreme care devoted to each production phase, a good quality/price ratio being our ultimate goal. Such approach stems from a craft tradition, but we also consider it part and parcel of our cultural heritage. Our mission. Day by day, we work in order to make design, technology and ergonomics widely accessible. We want our kitchens to look good, be smart and last long, so to contribute to improve the life of their users.

Name: Billeschou A/S
Company description: Velkommen til Billeschou A/S - En verden af sten. Fra brud til bordplade, er en fantastisk historie om den lange rejse, fra starten i et granitbrud til slut, hvor bordpladen endelig kan leveres til dig. I mere end 100 år har man brugt stenbordplader til køkkener og badeværelser. Tider og trends  skifter samtidig med mange nye anvendelsesmuligheder, design, udformning er kommet til — sten er ikke bare sten.  Billeschou A/S har været med i stenbordpladens udvikling og fulgt tidens krav og tendenser siden 1867. Hos Billeschou A/S ønsker vi konstant at have fokus på levering af det bedste produkt. Dette gør vi bl.a. ved at have konstant fokus på kvalitet, fleksibilitet, service og høj leveringssikkerhed. I samarbejde med vores forhandlere ønsker  vi at skabe en innovationskultur, som sikrer, at markedet konstant udvikles.  Billeschou A/S er underleverandør til køkkenbranchen. #billeschou #enverdenafsten

Name: BOJ
Company description: The company was founded in the province of Gipuzkoa in 1905. Back then we manufactured simple pieces of metal, but we soon expanded our range with new products and mechanical technology. Over the following years, the development of the company was accompanied by the industrial revolution of the area. Towns such as Eibar and Mondragón stood out nationally and we constantly incorporated increasingly advanced and complex technology in our products. Later in the 20th century the creative and competitive capabilities of our engineers continued to grow. We had to supply a market that was increasingly challenging and international. We needed to meet all the needs in the kitchen and, as a solution to these demands, BOJ GLOBAL emerged. Thus, the catalogue of products gradually expanded over the years. In addition to the manufacture of implements related to wine and kitchenware, we added small appliances and, a little later, a wide range of domestic appliances. In short, we provide a global service. This diversification in products has been accompanied by a diversification in markets. In what is a big step in our development, we have entered markets such as China, the Middle East, Egypt, Iran, the USA and all of Europe, including the Baltic countries. All of this growth is the result of the work and effort of our great team of people. These professionals, with more than 20 years of experience both nationally and internationally, are the reason why BOJ GLOBAL is a consolidated and recognised brand across half of the world. It is a brand that always looks forward from the strength of a history spanning more than 100 years.

Name: HANDCRAFTED INTERIOR
HQ Location: Denmark, Capital Region, Hellerup, 2 Gammel Vartov Vej, 2900
Company description: Handcrafted Interior er et ungt og innovativt køkkenfirma med fokus på smukt design i træ og den kvalitetsprægede forarbejdning i detaljen. Hos os er alle køkkener og møbler unikke, og alt skræddersyes efter vores kunders drømme, behov og ønsker. Selv om vi i dag er vokset til over 60 medarbejdere fordelt over tre forskellige lande, stræber vi nu som før efter en mestring af det sublime snedkerhåndværk. Som kunde mærker du denne stræben ved, at det er de samme dygtige håndværkere som hele vejen igennem – til det punkt hvor f.eks. et køkken er leveret – har ansvaret og stoltheden over samme møbel. Handcrafted Interior er et familiedrevet foretagende, hvor to familier i Danmark og i Letland har arbejdet hårdt for at gøre en drøm om skræddersyede køkkener og møbler mulig. Som navnet Handcrafted Interior indikerer, tilbyder vi andre snedkererede løsninger såsom indbyggede skabe, walk-in closets, reoler, børnemøbler, badeværelsesmøbler m.m. Handcrafted Interior har showroom i København, Aarhus og Malmø derudover værksted i Letland, hvor knap 50 snedkere, tegnere og andre håndværkere er beskæftiget. Vores værksted i Letland sikrer, at vi kan tilbyde yderst attraktive priser og hurtig leveringstid. Den enkelte snedker producerer alle vores køkkener og møbler fra bunden til færdigt produkt. Derefter kommer vedkommende til Danmark og monterer sit håndværk. Det skaber et helstøbt og unikt produkt. Handcrafted Interiors passion er at skabe smukt og innovativt design, som ikke bare ser lækkert ud, men som også er funktionelt i alle henseender. Vi ser det som vores fornemmeste opgave at være i stand til at levere køkkener og andre håndlavede møbler i fantastisk kvalitet, hvor kærligheden til designet og håndværket skinner tydeligt igennem.

Name: Remember KF Design
Company description: REMEMBER bringt Farbe in die Welt Seit der Gründung im Jahr 1996 steht für REMEMBER die Inspiration durch Farben und Formen im Vordergrund – und das ist bis heute so geblieben. Im Laufe der Jahre entstand ein ständig wachsendes Sortiment individueller Design-, Lifestyle und Geschenkartikel. Egal ob Spiele, modische Accessoires, Kalender, Wohn-, Küchen- oder Büroartikel – eines eint alle Produkte: jeder Artikel wird mit großer Leidenschaft ausschließlich im eigenen Haus entwickelt und gestaltet.  Viele Gegenstände des täglichen Lebens werden durch einen unverkennbaren Gestaltungsstil zu etwas Neuem gemacht. Das Resultat ist ein außergewöhnliches, sehr originelles Sortiment.  REMEMBER-Produkte wurden aufgrund der hohen Qualität bei Gestaltung und Verarbeitung bereits vielfach mit renommierten Design-Preisen ausgezeichnet.  REMEMBER verkauft sein Sortiment sehr erfolgreich im Direktvertrieb sowie seit 15 Jahren auch an den deutschen und internationalen Handel. REMEMBER-Produkte finden sich in Design-, Geschenk- und Dekorationsgeschäften, in hochwertigen Kaufhäusern und Spielwarengeschäften, im Papeteriehandel, in Museums-Shops, als beliebte Non-Book Artikel im Buchhandel, sowie im Fachhandel für Tisch, Küche und Wohnaccessoires.  Nachdem REMEMBER im Heimatmarkt bereits etabliert ist, sind die Produkte heute zunehmend auch weltweit zu finden. Neben dem Guggenheim-Museumshop in Bilbao und Venedig oder dem MoMA in New York und San Francisco sorgen internationale Partner für Distribution u.a. in Japan, Australien, Neuseeland und Kanada.

Name: Hansgrohe AG
Company description: Hansgrohe AG is a leading manufacturer of high-quality bathroom and kitchen fixtures, specializing in innovative solutions such as wall-mounted faucets and shower systems. The company's mission is to consistently deliver exceptional quality to its customers, underpinned by a commitment to sustainability and environmental responsibility. With a diverse product range that includes various installation systems and accessories, Hansgrohe caters to both residential and commercial markets, serving clients such as architects, builders, and homeowners. The company partners with specialized retailers to ensure that its products are accessible to a wide audience, reinforcing its reputation for excellence in design and functionality. Hansgrohe AG aims to enhance the user experience in everyday water usage, making it both enjoyable and efficient.

Name: Laminam Germany
HQ Location: Germany, Hesse, Frankfurt Am Main, 1-3 Brüsseler Straße
Company description: Laminam steht für hochwertige Keramikbeläge im Großformat, die aufgrund ihrer besonderen Eigenschaften für Wohngebäude, öffentliche Räume und Industrie eingesetzt werden. Die Oberflächen des italienischen Unternehmens mit Sitz in Fiorano Modenese in der Region Emilia Romagna sind bekannt für ihr zeitloses Design und eine raffinierte, sinnliche Ästhetik. Diese schöpft ihre Ausdruckskraft aus der reichhaltigen Landschaft Italiens als Ursprungsort aller gestalterischer Inspiration. Besondere Rohstoffe, handwerkliche Fertigungstradition und hochtechnologische Verarbeitung lassen ein leistungsstarkes Produktportfolio entstehen, das seine Ausdruckskraft aus dem besonderen Spannungsfeld zwischen Natur und Innovation bezieht: In unterschiedlichen Größen und Stärken können die Beläge für Küche, Bad, Böden und Wände, Treppen, Terrassen und Fassaden verwendet werden. Die einzigartige Verbindung von ästhetischer und technischer Präzision überzeugt Architekten, Designer und Planer weltweit.  Neben höchsten Anforderungen an Hygiene, ästhetischer Haltbarkeit und Langlebigkeit weisen die Keramikplatten zahlreiche funktionale Eigenschaften wie Trittsicherheit, Feuchtigkeitsresistenz und Wärmeleitfähigkeit auf, welche Laminam zu einem innovativen und qualitätsstarken Partner in der Ausstattung und Gestaltung von öffentlichen und Wohngebäuden sowie dem Objektbereich macht. Mit dem innovativen Ausbau der Produktionsstätten trägt Laminam seinem Anspruch an eine energie- und ressourcenschonende, umweltfreundliche Produktion Rechnung. Hier übersetzen Menschen mit Passion und technischem Know-How die jahrhundertalte Keramiktradition Italiens zu einem innovativen High-Tech Produkt für gehobene Ansprüche in Architektur und Interior Design.

Name: Marchi Cucine
Company description: Progettare e realizzare cucine eccellenti, che esprimano valori superiori alla ricerca costante della massima qualità e della assoluta bellezza.  Marchi Cucine si distingue da sempre per la ricerca della perfezione estetica e strutturale di cucine fortemente evocative, dai tratti stilistici inconfondibili, che attingono ai valori della tradizione per offrire un risultato di assoluta eccellenza, fuori dalle mode e dal tempo.  La nostra mission è quella di progettare e realizzare cucine eccellenti, che esprimano i valori in cui crediamo da sempre, per chi è alla ricerca di un ambiente esclusivo e carico di significati, un ambiente che coniughi eleganza e solidità, calore ed equilibrio, tradizione e contemporaneità.

Name: Aerre Srl
Company description: Nata da un’idea e dalle indubbie capacità di Raffaele Anastasio, la “AERRE CUCINE srl” viene inaugurata nel 1994 ad Arzano, in provincia di Napoli. Oggi è un’azienda giovane e dinamica che, sorretta dal forte entusiasmo e dalla elevata professionalità di quanti vi operano, si propone con notevole successo sul mercato delle cucine componibili, attuando soluzioni innovative capaci di soddisfare pienamente ogni esigenza di arredamento e funzionalità, riservando particolare cura al design, unito a caratteristiche di elevata robustezza. Il suo obiettivo è ambizioso: conquistarsi un posto da leader tra i produttori nazionali di cucine, potendosi già porre con pieno merito nella prestigiosa storia dell’imprenditoria campana.

Name: Löwik Wonen & Slapen
Company description: Bij Löwik Wonen & Slapen begint inrichten met een dagje genieten. De enorme woonboulevard is gevestigd in één grote winkel vol woonideeën. Van de kleinste woonwens tot de grootste dromen: ze zijn levendig verbeeld. Vele prachtige ingerichte woonkamers, smaakvolle en gezellige keukens en warme sfeervolle slaapkamers inspireren bezoekers tot een nieuwe kijk op het leven in huis. Löwik Meubelen, gevestigd in Vriezenveen, is de grootste woonboulevard van Oost-Nederland. U vindt hier de grootste collectie banken, eetkamerstoelen en fauteuils. Naast wonen is Löwik ook gespecialiseerd in slapen. We hebben de grootste collectie matrassen, comfortbedden, ledikanten, boxsprings, juniorkamers en bedtextiel. De persoonlijke aandacht en het kopje koffie zijn nooit verdwenen. U bent van harte welkom in het knusse restaurant en de koffiehoek: De Fabrik. De droom van oud-directeur Löwik is realiteit geworden; winkelen bij Löwik Wonen & Slapen is een heerlijk dagje uit. Ook op het gebied van koken biedt Löwik wonen en slapen een zeer grote collectie keukens. De super geprijsde keukens bij Superkeukens en de prachte luxe design keukens bij Designkeukens.

Name: Jan Van Sundert
Company description: Een woning kopen en inrichten doet u niet elke dag. Geen wonder dat u niet over één nacht ijs wilt gaan. Zeker wanneer het gaat over keukens, badkamers en tegels hebben we het al snel over behoorlijke bedragen. En dan moet het natuurlijk gewoon goed zijn!  Al sinds 1969 is Jan van Sundert keukens, badkamers en tegels gevestigd te Etten-Leur. Van oorsprong een echt familiebedrijf, waarvan de leiding inmiddels van de vader, Jan van Sundert, is overgegaan naar de zonen. Het bedrijf is nog steeds volledig onafhankelijk. Vader van Sundert legde het fundament voor een gezond bedrijf waar men het leveren van kwaliteit voor een betaalbare prijs nog steeds "heel gewoon" vindt. In onze sfeervol ingerichte showroom, treft u ruim 300 keuken- en badkamer-opstellingen aan en tal van fraaie tegelcollecties geschikt voor woonkamer, keuken, bijkeuken of badkamer. Het grootste tegelassortiment in West-Brabant. Op deze website krijgt u een ruime impressie van onze showroom, de koffiecorner, de kinderhoek, receptie en een selectie keukens en badkamers...

Name: GASTRO PRODUCTION S. R. O.
HQ Location: Czech Republic, Kamenný Újezd South Bohemian Region, 500 Zemědělská, 373 81
Company description: We specialize in the manufacturing, sales, and service of stainless steel gastronomic equipment (cooling showcases, tubs, tables, plates or heating plates, tubs and much more). For over 30 years, we have been providing our services to customers across Europe. Our goal is to create a positive impact on the ecosystem, deliver high-quality solutions, and turn your visions into reality—from fully equipping hotels, kitchens, and canteens to custom-made interior designs, primarily from stainless steel, but also wood and stone. With a focus on digitalization, premium services, and customer comfort, we ensure that every project meets the highest standards.

Name: Zwilling J.A. Henckels Iberia S.A.
HQ Location: Spain, Catalonia, Cornellà De Llobregat, 11 Ctra. De L'hospitalet, 08940
Company description: ZWILLING J.A. HENCKELS es una de las marcas más antiguas de Europa. Fundada en 1731, es hoy dia un referente mundial en el campo de la cuchillería y el menaje de cocina, así como en accesorios de belleza, manicura y pedicura.

Name: FerreHogar
Company description: Somos una empresa especializada en cocinas portatiles, gran variedad en mosquiteras, hamacas y accesorios para el camping, caravanas y acampadas. Disponémos de Tienda Online y también suministramos a Mayoristas. Si está interesado en conocer más sobre nosotros visite nuestras páginas web o tiendas online.  Si Usted esta interesado en vender nuestros productos. Por favor, escribanos a : ferrehogar@ferrehogar.es y dejenos todos sus datos y actividad. Nos contactaremos a la mayor brevedad posible! También puede hacerlo por teléfono al (0034)  610 798 533 o 968 296 654   de Lunes a Viernes , de 10 a 13 hs.

Name: Arklam Super Size
HQ Location: Spain, Valencia, Castelló De La Plana, Km. 7,5 Carretera Alcora, 12130
Company description: Large format sintered mass for flooring and cladding, kitchen countertops, ventilated façades... 100% Made in Spain Masa sinterizada de gran formato para pavimentos y revestimientos, encimeras de cocina, fachadas ventiladas... 100% Hecho en España

Name: Synferri
Company description: ΓΙΑ ΤΟ ΣΠΙΤΙ ΣΟΥ, Ο,ΤΙ ΣΕ SYNΦΕΡΕΙ!  Είμαστε η αλυσίδα καταστημάτων με τις πιο δυναμικές και ολοκληρωμένες λύσεις για τη διακόσμηση του σπιτιού και το νοικοκυριό στην πόλη της Πάτρας!  Επισκεφθείτε μας και βρείτε ό,τι χρειάζεστε σε: - Διακόσμηση  - Καθαριότητα - Κουζίνα - Μπάνιο - Λευκά είδη - Κήπος - Ομορφιά - Κατοικίδια Από την Πάτρα για την Πάτρα, στα 3 καταστήματά μας και στο Synferri.gr!

Name: Intermat B.V.
Company description: In 1977 opent Intermat haar deuren in Mijdrecht. Sindsdien is er veel gebeurd. Het kleine familiebedrijf is uitgegroeid tot een partner in keukens, tegels en badkamers. Particulieren en professionals komen bij Intermat voor inspiratie, advies en service. In de 2.000 vierkante meter showroom zijn de toonaangevende keuken-, tegel- en badkamermerken vertegenwoordigd. Intermat biedt in deze showroom een uniek totaalconcept voor zowel de particulier, aannemer en projektontwikkelaar waarbij de beheersing van het koopproces centraal wordt gesteld.

Name: Concordia Keuken & Bad
Company description: Concordia Keuken & Bad  is een totaalleverancier voor keukens, sanitair, wand- en vloertegels. In onze gecombineerde showrooms van 3000 m2 staan legio voorbeelden voor u opgesteld, in Meppel èn Heerenveen. Concordia Keuken & Bad  is een specialist in maatwerkkeukens met daarnaast het design merk NEXT 125. Wilt u liever een meer standaard uitgevoerde keuken, dan kunt u ook prima bij ons terecht. Wij staan graag voor u klaar met advies! Onze tien punten waar we trots op zijn: geen aanbetaling, totaal leverancier, scherpe netto prijsopgave, eigen montagedienst, afvoer van het verpakkingsmateriaal, bezorging in eigen beheer, voor elk budget, hofleverancier, afspraak is afspraak, tevreden klant is onze garantie.  Wij zijn het adres voor: Keukens, sanitair, tegels, vloeren, kasten, natuursteen, keukenzaak, keukenshowroom, designkeukens, landelijke keukens, moderne keukens, maatwerkkeukens, keukenmontage, showroomkeuken, showroomaanbiedingen, showroom opruimingskeukens, inbouwapparatuur, keukenwerkblad, werkblad graniet / composiet, Whirlpool, Bauknecht, Smeg / siemens, AEG, Zanussi, Pelgrim, spoelbak, keukenkraan, badkamer, badkamerrenovatie, sanitair-showroom, radiator, stoomcabine, sauna, whirlpool, douchewand, badkamertegels, vloertegels, wandtegels, vloerverwarming, schuifwanden, tegelmontage, houten vloer, vloeren, parketvloer, parket, laminaat, laminaatvloer, pvc vloer en nog veel meer.

Name: Euromebel
Company description: COMPANY HISTORY Euromebel was founded in 1994 in Sofia, Bulgaria and is currently one of the leading manufacturers of high-end furniture. Our comprehensive production range includes furniture systems for the whole house, bookcases, wardrobes, beds, kitchens, sofas and tables. Working closely with leading architects we also dedicate our productive resources to bespoke furniture concepts for large commercial and residential projects. CORE VALUES We strive to impress with our work. We believe design is everything and design is everywhere. We strive to advance our craft all the time. We believe everyone of us is the source of change and innovation that we seek. We love what we do and we care deeply for each and every detail. You can view the catalogue with our most recent projects here: http://issuu.com/euromebel/docs/press_1a

Name: VIKA
Company description: For over 60 years, Vika has been a trusted family-owned B2B partner in designing and manufacturing kitchens, bathrooms, and tailor-made interiors. What started as a passion for craftsmanship has grown into a team of 120+ professionals committed to quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction. Our mission is to create beautiful, functional interiors and long-term partnerships built on trust and craftsmanship — a vision we carry into our new, future-ready headquarters.

Name: D. Lechner GmbH
HQ Location: Germany, Bavaria, Rothenburg Ob Der Tauber
Company description: Die Lechner Holding AG ist führender Hersteller von maßgefertigten Arbeitsplatten und Rückwänden für Küchen- und Wohndesign. Über 740 Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter arbeiten international in den Produktionsstätten Deutschland, Schweden und Ungarn. Seit 1991 produziert die D. Lechner GmbH in Deutschland auf einer Produktionsfläche von 90.000 m². Der hochmoderne Maschinenpark und die flexible Fertigung garantieren höchste Qualität und kurze Lieferzeiten. Durch das innovative Produktportfolio bietet Lechner die größte Vielfalt an außergewöhnlichen Materialien wie beispielsweise Keramik, Glas, Naturstein und C+S, unserer Laminat-Kollektion mit hochwertigen Dekoren, die sich durch eine besondere Oberfläche oder ein ausgesuchtes Design auszeichnen.

Name: Bulthaup Italia
Company description: Fondata nel 1949, bulthaup è oggi leader mondiale nel settore delle cucine premium. L'azienda a conduzione familiare indipendente, alla sua terza generazione, è ora guidata dal CEO Marc O' Eckert. La dedizione di bulthaup alla qualità, alla funzionalità e al design, unita a passione e talento per l'innovazione, hanno reso il brand una forza trainante sul mercato.   bulthaup Italia si avvale di un'esclusiva rete distributiva di 28 Partners selezionati, operanti sia con clienti finali privati che nel contract.

Name: Accademia Mugnano
HQ Location: Italy, Sparanise Caserta, Km 189,200 Ss 7 Appia, 81056
Company description: 🇮🇹 Accademia Mugnano, dal 1945, è impegnata nella produzione di pentole in alluminio con rivestimento antiaderente.  La nostra missione è ricerca e sviluppo costante di soluzioni innovative per semplificare e arricchire l'esperienza culinaria. Fondiamo la nostra pratica su valori come tradizione, qualità, design, sicurezza e durabilità.  Applicando rigorosi standard internazionali, utilizzando materiali di alta qualità e adottando rivestimenti antiaderenti, crediamo che ogni cucina nel mondo possa preparare con successo anche le ricette più complesse.  Il nostro impegno va oltre il profitto, ponendo al centro dei nostri processi decisionali i consumatori e l'ambiente. Cucina sano, cucina italiano con Accademia Mugnano 🇬🇧 Accademia Mugnano, since 1945, has been dedicated to the production of aluminum cookware with non-stick coating. Our mission involves continuous research and development of innovative solutions to simplify and enhance the culinary experience. We base our practices on values such as tradition, quality, design, safety, and durability. By adhering to rigorous international standards, utilizing high-quality materials, and incorporating non-stick coatings, we believe that kitchens worldwide can successfully prepare even the most complex recipes. Our commitment extends beyond profit, placing consumers and the environment at the center of our decision-making processes. Cook healthy, cook Italian with Accademia Mugnano.

Name: THUIS - De Showroom
Company description: U maakt het kopers graag zo makkelijk mogelijk. Met een fijne woning die gewoon in orde is. Waarin alles klopt en het direct comfortabel wonen is. Het team van THUIS begrijpt het belang daarvan als geen ander. Daarom hebben wij een uniek concept voor ontwikkelaars en beleggers ontwikkeld. De belangrijkste voordelen van dit concept zijn: Alles onder één dak U vindt bij ons alles onder één dak: keukens, badkamers, wanden en vloeren, bouwkundige upgrades, raamdecoratie en maatkasten. Breed assortiment Er is een breed assortiment van hoogwaardige en duurzame producten, passend bij de stijl van uw project. Comfortabel en compleet U biedt uw koper of huurder een comfortabele en complete woning; de bewoner hoeft er alleen zijn meubels nog in te zetten. Zorgeloos kiezen Wij denken mee over het beste ontwerp en zorgen voor een waardevolle woning. THUIS - de Showroom is een onderdeel van Dura Vermeer.

Name: Siloma Srl
HQ Location: Italy, Tv, Barbisano, 71 Via Toti Dal Monte, 31050
Company description: Siloma nasce nel 1968 nel settore delle camerette ma oggi offre una gamma estremamente vasta di proposte giorno, cucine, camere e camerette caratterizzate da modularità, flessibilità, cura dei materiali e del design.  È un’azienda moderna che propone soluzioni giovani e flessibili per soddisfare le richieste più vicine agli stili di vita del momento, dove tecnologia funzionale e creatività si coniugano in una continua evoluzione.  Siloma srl è oggi una realtà italiana che opera nel settore dell’arredamento e in questi anni ha potuto maturare un ampio patrimonio di conoscenze e competenze. La sua realtà industriale ricopre oggi 42.000 mq, e sebbene operi anche su un piano internazionale è riuscita a mantenere un forte legame con il territorio d’origine, quello veneto, conservando i propri valori e le proprie tradizioni che stanno alla base del successo dell’azienda.

Name: Asko Nábytek Spol. S R.o.
Company description: ASKO – NÁBYTEK patří mezi největší tuzemské prodejce nábytku s tradicí již od roku 1991, kdy byla otevřena první prodejna v Praze. V současné době nabízí ve 13 obchodech po celé České republice široký sortiment nábytku jak v moderním designu, tak v klasickém provedení, ale i bytové doplňky a kuchyně na míru. Na každé prodejně naleznete také kompletní nabídku souvisejících služeb: doprava nábytku, odborná montáž, možnost splátkového nákupu, záruční i zákaznický servis a v neposlední řadě i garance nejnižší ceny. Od roku 2009 je sortiment ASKO – NÁBYTEK k dostání i on-line na e-shopu společnosti s doručením po celé ČR. Během března 2019 byla také spuštěna nová služba Click & Collect, která umožňuje pohodlný nákup on-line a následné osobní vyzvednutí včetně platby na kterékoli prodejně. Společnost klade zásadní důraz na vaši spokojenost, a proto neustále zlepšuje své služby na základě vašich podnětů a upravuje prodejny podle nejnovějších trendů. V roce 2018 byl zavedený nový moderní koncept prodejen otevřením pilotní prodejny Teplice. Vzhled změní postupně všechny pobočky tak, aby zákazníci mohli nakupovat v moderních, prostorných, vzdušných a vzhledově velmi příjemných prodejnách, jejichž průměrná plocha je 6000 m2. Do dalších let plánuje společnost rozšiřování své obchodní sítě. Chce tím přispět jak ke zvyšování vaší spokojenosti, tak i ke zvyšování zaměstnanosti v naší zemi prostřednictvím nabídky nových pracovních míst v prodejnách ASKO – NÁBYTEK. Společnost ASKO – NÁBYTEK patří od roku 2011 k podnikové skupině PORTA se sídlem v Německu. Jednatelem společnosti pro CZ a SK trh je Michal Moureček. V prodejnách ASKO – NÁBYTEK si ze širokého sortimentu vybere jak náročný zákazník, tak ten, který zařizuje své první bydlení. Jednoduše každý, kdo hledá kvalitu i výborný servis.

Name: Jealser
HQ Location: Spain, Navarre, Elcarte, Km 8,5 Ctra Guipúzcoa, 31195
Company description: Jealser S.A. es una gran empresa afincada en Elcarte (Navarra) especializada en el tratamiento del aluminio. Su capacidad para producir cualquier tipo de piezas de Aluminio combinada con la experiencia y profesionalidad de su personal, hacen que el nombre de esta empresa sea sinónimo de calidad y buen hacer. La empresa fue fundada en 1970 por su actual presidente, Jesús Alonso, de ahí que el nombre inicial de la misma fuera "Accesorios Alonso". La expansión de la empresa hizo que en 1986 naciera como tal Jealser S.A. En los primeros años de vida, esta empresa se dedicaba fundamentalmente a la fabricación de accesorios para la carpintería de aluminio. Con el paso del tiempo, ha ampliado su campo hacia sectores tan diversos como los accesorios de cocina, el curvado de perfiles, el mecanizado de piezas o los perfiles y accesorios para armarios. En la actualidad opera regularmente en Europa, América y África.

Name: Vitrum
HQ Location: Latvia, Bergi, Jaunā Līgo Street 31, lv-1024
Company description: Elevating hospitality & retail spaces. Designed for performance. Built to last. At Vitrum, we design and manufacture tailored solutions for the restaurant, bar, and retail industries—handling everything from design and manufacturing to installation and ongoing service. Our approach is built on precision, craftsmanship, and efficiency—ensuring that your space isn’t just visually striking but also works seamlessly behind the scenes. For over 30 years, we’ve partnered with leading restaurants, hotels, bars, retailers and distributors across Europe, Scandinavia, and the UAE, delivering comprehensive solutions that optimize workflow, enhance guest experiences, and maximize operational success. Our expertise: 🔹 Restaurant Solutions – From back-of-house efficiency to front-of-house impact. 🔹 Bar solutions – Modular, high-performance bar setups built for speed & style. 🔹 Professional kitchens  – Standard and custom high performance equipment for small and large food service projects (restaurants, hotels, schools, airports and more). 🔹 Retail spaces – Custom environments designed to keep customers engaged. 🔹 Manufacturing & Powder Coating – In-house production for total quality control. 🔹 Windows & Doors – Precision glazing solutions that merge durability with design. Why choose Vitrum? ✔️ End-to-end project management – From concept to execution. ✔️ Innovative design & engineering – Built around your space, vision, and workflow. ✔️ Scalable solutions – Whether it’s a single restaurant or a multi-location rollout. ✔️ 3,000+ projects delivered – Across 20+ countries, with 15,000 sq. meters of in-house production. Let’s build something exceptional. Whether you’re opening a new space or upgrading an existing one, Vitrum is your full-service partner in creating hospitality and retail environments that perform. 📍 Visit us at: www.vitrum.lv

Name: JEE-O International
Company description: JEE-O Unique Bathrooms weds beautiful design to functionality in bathroom concepts. Extending beyond the bathroom, the designs by JEE-O also fit beautifully in the rest of the house, including the kitchen or sauna, by the swimming pool or on the beach. JEE-O has a minimalistic, innovative style with a cosmopolitan character. Bold and distinctive, yet refined: JEE-O creates concepts providing sufficient space for body and mind, always seeking an atmosphere of functional luxury. 2004 marks the birth of JEE-O, a creative concept by Lammert Moerman. The brand has grown immensely since that time; its selection of separate showers and baths, mixers and wash basins is currently available all across the globe. The JEE-O soho 01 shower won a Red Dot award and a German Design Award.

Name: Officine Gullo
Company description: Officine Gullo is a distinguished manufacturer specializing in high-end kitchenware, particularly renowned for its exquisite hammered copper cookware sets. The company combines traditional craftsmanship with innovative design to deliver exceptional culinary performance, ensuring even heat distribution and durability through its unique materials, which include solid copper and stainless steel. Officine Gullo's mission is to elevate the cooking experience by providing elegant and functional kitchen tools that not only perform well but also enhance the aesthetic of any kitchen. The brand caters to a diverse clientele, including private customers, architects, interior designers, and retailers, positioning itself in the luxury market for culinary enthusiasts and professionals alike. With a commitment to quality and sophistication, Officine Gullo aims to be a leader in the premium kitchenware sector, appealing to those who appreciate both artistry and functionality in their cooking tools.

Name: DSM KEUKENS
Company description: DSM Keukens staat aan de top van de Belgische keukenmarkt. Wij zijn een familiebedrijf met 100 jaar ervaring. Wegens onze sterke groei en uitbreiding zijn wij steeds op zoek naar gemotiveerde medewerkers. Bezoek onze website voor de openstaande vacatures: http://www.dsmkeukens.be/vacatures/ Momenteel zijn er al 18 toonzalen: Sint-Martens-Latem, Roeselare, Sint-Niklaas, Erembodegem, Olen, Aartselaar, Beveren-Leie, Oostende, Kampenhout, Oudenaarde, Genk, Namen, Drogenbos, Schoten, Gosselies & Zaventem.

Name: Tescoma S.p.A.
HQ Location: Italy, Lombardy, Cazzago San Martino, 3 Via Caduti Del Lavoro, 25046
Company description: Tescoma è un'azienda leader mondiale nel mercato degli utensili da cucina e dei prodotti per la casa,  presente in Italia dal 1996. Le sue attività comprendono ricerca, sviluppo, progettazione, produzione e commercializzazione di prodotti per la cucina e per altri ambienti di casa a marchio proprio.  A partire dalla sua fondazione, questi sono stati i principi guida dell'azienda:  1. Offrire un'ampia gamma di prodotti di qualità a prezzi convenienti  2. Progettare, sviluppare e produrre utensili dal design originale  3. Promuovere nel mondo il brand Tescoma.  L'assortimento comprende oltre 2.500 prodotti, sia per uso domestico che professionale: utensili per la preparazione, la cottura e la presentazione dei cibi, oggetti per la pulizia e l'ordine in casa, profumi per gli ambienti.  Tescoma è supportata da diversi centri produttivi e logistici anche all'estero e i prodotti possono essere acquistati in oltre 100 Paesi nel mondo.  La presenza del brand sui mercati internazionali è dovuta principalmente ad un efficace lavoro di ricerca e sviluppo, ad un design originale dei prodotti, materiali di alta qualità, cura nella produzione ed ampiezza di gamma.

Name: TESCOMA España
HQ Location: Spain, Valencia, Mutxamel, Parcela E4 Pol.ind. Riodel Calle Moli Nou, 03110
Company description: Tescoma: la mayor gama de utensilios de cocina Tescoma se posiciona internacionalmente como una referencia ineludible en el sector de la fabricación y distribución de utensilios de cocina gracias a su presencia en más de 100 países y sus más de 40 espacios operativos. En España, la matriz lleva operando más de una década con un óptimo rendimiento. Tescoma España opera respaldada por la sede central de la firma ubicada en Zlín (República Checa) que cuenta con una superficie de 50.000 m2 y desde donde salen cada día cientos de miles de productos hacia sus diferentes filiales en el extranjero. Esta gran estructura logística y de personal permite que Tescoma pueda ofrecer un extensísimo catálogo con más de 2.500 referencias para cocina doméstica y uso profesional y diferenciarse de su competencia más directa gracias a su variedad, originalidad y la calidad de toda su oferta.

Name: Teunissen & Becking
Company description: Teunissen & Becking BV is uw specialist in tegels, keukens en badkamers. Met ruim vijftig jaar ervaring durft Teunissen & Becking BV zich met recht specialist in hun vakgebied te noemen.  Dankzij ons ruime assortiment zijn er veel mogelijkheden om een keuken, badkamer en/of het tegelwerk geheel naar uw eigen wensen samen te stellen.  Ervaring, kwaliteit, en scherpe prijzen worden bij ons gecompleteerd door ouderwets vertrouwen.Wilt u persoonlijk advies of bent u opzoek naar de juiste keuken, badkamer en/of wand- en vloertegels dan willen wij u graag uitnodigen voor een bezoek aan onze showroom. U wordt vrijblijvend geadviseerd door een van onze adviseurs.  Voor meer informatie kunt u kijken op onze website.

Name: Intratuin Arnhem Presikhaaf
Company description: Intratuin Arnhem Presikhaaf betovert & inspireert. Groot assortiment voor tuin, huis en balkon. Als meest inclusieve Intratuin van Nederland  hebben we aandacht voor onze omgeving en organiseren we allerlei activiteiten om  deze nog groener en gezelliger te maken.  Of je nu komt voor een workshop, uniek cadeautje of plantenadvies; onze  behulpzame medewerkers zorgen ervoor dat je altijd met de juiste producten én een goed gevoel naar huis gaat. Intratuin Arnhem is onderdeel van Scalabor, Scalabor is hèt sociaal ontwikkelbedrijf voor Midden-Gelderland. We helpen mensen die ondersteuning nodig hebben bij het krijgen en behouden van een plek op de arbeidsmarkt.  De PROEFTUIN is het restaurant in Intratuin Arnhem. Ons verhaal gaat over vers, natuurlijk, biologisch, biodivers, inclusief, participatie, sociaal en maatschappelijk. In onze keuken bieden wij mensen met een afstand tot de arbeidsmarkt een werkplek en mensen die het horeca vak willen leren een opleidingsplek.  In onze BELEVINGSTUIN hebben wij een eigen moestuin waaruit de kok dagelijks zijn verse producten haalt die worden gebruikt voor de bereiding van onze gerechten. Daardoor smaken onze gerechten in ons restaurant nog veel beter!

Name: Bulthaup
Company description: bulthaup kitchens and living spaces are places where people come together to connect, relax and feel at home.  To create such places, people, and their needs and customs, must be at the heart of all our considerations. This is how bulthaup thinks and acts. Every day, we are wondering whether our concept of “the kitchen” is enough to meet people’s wants and needs, now and in future. We continually investigate this question as we manufacture our products with a passion for detail and a love of authentic materials, to create kitchen and living space systems that enrich lives now and tomorrow. People are able to create things that even the most sophisticated technology cannot: Material authenticity that can be experienced with all of the senses.

Name: TPC Cocinas
Company description: TPC Cocinas is a leading company specializing in the design and manufacturing of high-quality kitchen products, including kitchen doors, furniture, countertops, and accessories. With a commitment to innovation and sustainability, TPC Cocinas aims to create functional and aesthetically pleasing kitchen solutions that cater to the diverse needs of its clients. The company serves a wide range of customers, from individual homeowners to interior designers and contractors, providing tailored solutions that enhance the culinary experience. TPC Cocinas also emphasizes environmental responsibility in its production processes, ensuring that its products are not only stylish but also eco-friendly. Through strategic partnerships and a robust online presence, TPC Cocinas continues to expand its reach in the competitive kitchen design market.

Name: Tischlerei Krumböck
Company description: Tischlerei Krumböck is a traditional furniture carpentry company that has been dedicated to honest craftsmanship since 1896. Specializing in custom furniture solutions, the company offers a wide range of services including the design and installation of kitchens, living rooms, bathrooms, and complete home furnishings. With a mission to create high-quality, tailored wooden products, Tischlerei Krumböck aims to enhance the living spaces of its clients through innovative design and meticulous attention to detail. The company primarily serves private homeowners, collaborating closely with them to realize their visions for interior spaces. By focusing on personalized service and craftsmanship, Tischlerei Krumböck has established itself as a trusted partner in the home improvement sector.

Name: AXIS Group Sp. Z O.o.
Company description: Axis Group Sp. z o. o. is a Polish company that produces granite kitchen and bathroom sinks made in "cold casting" technology.  Our modern manufacturing plant focuses on stylish, elegant, excellent-quality products, clean technology, and a low carbon footprint.  As a result, we have been one of the top Polish producers of granite kitchen and bath products for over ten years. We owe our success to a team of experienced, skilled, dedicated employees who use technologically advanced, modern machinery exceeding all environmental safety standards. All the suppliers of our production components and materials meet strict requirements and source their products within the European Union. We are a manufacturer for both the AXIS brand and numerous OEM brands of our long-term customers. Our products sell successfully in all European countries, North Africa and Asia. We have just started our expansion into the USA and Canadian territories. Our products have been awarded a full range of required certificates and approvals, including ISO 2009 issued by the German company TUV and IAPMO. We currently produce over 150 models of sinks of all types and sizes in 12 colors.   We provide our customers with a full range of services, from transforming an idea into a project through the production of models and then molds - the primary production tool, guaranteeing proper surface quality and all aesthetic details, to the launch of serial production. "Well done is better than well said."   These words by Benjamin Franklin are the principle that guides us every day.

Name: Pando
Company description: After 40 years on the market, the launch of a new product catalogue still remains a challenge for us proving that we are able to do even better and surprise our customers once more. This is a way of expressing our illusions and work to improve the quality of life of the people who count on Pando to equip their kitchens. We strive each day to be better and to produce the most effective kitchen hoods in terms of extraction levels, noise, smoke treatment and energy consumption. We integrate the best ECO motors on the market and LED lighting systems into virtually all of the hoods that we make to remain leaders in QUALITY. We look forward to continuing working with you, which is what gives us most satisfaction of all

Name: SPEKVA
Company description: In the south of Denmark you will find a very special workshop; a workshop, where the most skilled and passionate craftsmen and -women create unique and extraordinary bespoke wooden solutions for beautiful kitchens around the world.  Only the finest wood is allowed into the SPEKVA workshop, where every single stave of wood is handpicked and combined with an experienced eye for color, texture and the characteristics of the different wood types. It’s an art and every countertop leaving the workshop is a handcrafted masterpiece. When you choose a customized solution from SPEKVA, you feel the craftsmanship, quality, and love in the wood. Each piece of wood has its individual expression, and the wooden staves are processed and combined by experienced hands, giving the finished countertop the most beautiful play and a clear Nordic design identity.  SPEKVA - Handcrafted in Denmark.

Name: Ciar SpA
HQ Location: Italy, The Marches, Pesaro, 3 Via Molaroni, 61122
Company description: Ciar is the most innovative producer of motorized movements for the Motion Furniture industry. Since 1987 Ciar design and supply integrated solutions for chairs/sofa with a combination of linear actuator kits, recliner mechanisms and massage frames.  Over the years Ciar pursued new applications of linear actuators kits in other industry segments: Fitness, Kitchen Fans, Hairdresser wash units, Recreational vehicls (RV), special Products. Please check our website www.ciar.it or  for more details write to: info@ciar.it

Name: Jøni A/S
HQ Location: Denmark, South Denmark, Odense, 28 C.f. Tietgens Boulevard, 5220
Company description: We Know What’s Cooking. Ja, det gør vi nemlig. For siden 1973 har vi udviklet og produceret storkøkkenudstyr, solgt til både Danmark og mange andre steder i verden.  Vi laver både kipstegere, kogeborde, koge-, køle- og stege-gryder. Vi nørder ned i hver eneste detalje og skaber storkøkkenudstyr, der fungerer i det virkelige køkken og løser virkelige udfordringer. Derfor er vores produkter også konstrueret med særligt fokus på let og ergonomisk betjening, energiforbrug, driftsikkerhed og en lang levetid. Og med over tre millioner forskellige kombinationsmuligheder har vi den kipsteger, det kogebord og den stegegryde, der passer perfekt til dit køkken.  Al vores udvikling og produktion foregår på vores fabrik i Odense i Danmark, hvor vi er 50 medarbejdere. Vi er et stærkt team, der udvikler, planlægger og producerer maskinerne ud fra lige præcis dine valg. Men ingen Jøni uden alle vores gode samarbejdspartnere og forhandlere i hele verden, som sælger vores produkter og giver en uvurderlig høj service til alle dem, der bruger vores storkøkkenudstyr.

Name: DMP Electronics Srl
HQ Location: Italy, Teramo, Canzano, 1 Via Maestri Del Lavoro, 64020
Company description: Since more than 45 years, DMP designs and manufactures electronic taps, integrated solutions, washrooms and kitchens furnishings , with certified and eco-friendly materials and processes. Its most reference sectors are: contract, community, catering and home.

Name: TM Italia Cucine
HQ Location: Italy, The Marches, Ascoli Piceno, 24 Via Enrico Mattei, 63100
Company description: To create an industrial system capable of processing unique pieces, to meet the needs of every customer, by transferring on every project the technological content of the research programs developed within the TM Italia LAB: this is the evolved craftsmanship model successfully followed by TM Italia, exporting the Italian manufacturing excellence around the world. Know-how, development and engineering skills, a range of over 350 selected and certified materials, support and international coverage to create unique strictly tailored kitchen projects, turnkey furniture, retail and hospitality. A system of solutions and integrated services to supporting your project. Discover more on www.tmitalia.com

Name: L'ANGOLO DELLA CASA
Company description: Un delizioso angolo nel centro di Sesto San Giovanni e tanto buon gusto sono gli elementi che fanno de L'Angolo della casa lo spazio da visitare per dar spunto alle idee. Strutturato su un unico piano, L'Angolo della casa è molto più di uno show room consacrato alle forme innovative, raffinate e trendy delle collezioni tavola firmate da prestigiose case europee, a una selezione di accessori d'arredo in stile contemporaneo nonchè alle pentole e agli utensili da cucina più funzionali e a tante-tante idee regalo. Lo store nasce per essere un punto d'incontro, uno spazio da vivere e da esplorare dove gli aspetti della creatività, della consulenza e del servizio al cliente hanno la preminenza, dove ci si reca con piacere per soddisfare una curiosità o per conoscere i tanti dettagli che rendono piacevole la tavola e ogni angolo della casa. L'atmosfera nel nuovo L'Angolo della casa è infatti elegante e raccolta ma, allo stesso tempo, calda e mai formale. I "padroni di casa" sono sempre a disposizione del pubblico per spiegare come un particolare design possa essere esteticamente seducente, e allo stesso tempo, perfettamente funzionale. Affidarsi all'esperienza e al prestigio di L'Angolo della casa significa poter scegliere l'allestimento della tavola e i complementi d'arredo tra collezioni che spaziano dallo stile classico e romantico al minimalismo del design contemporaneo. Uniche per completezza e varietà di decori, tutte le collezioni sono accumunate da un altissimo livello qualitativo e da un valore destinato a conservarsi nel tempo.

Name: Bouwcenter Concordia
Company description: Concordia is dé leverancier van alle hout- en bouwmaterialen, voor zowel de professionele verwerker als de particulier.  Sinds decennia zijn wij het vertrouwde adres voor aannemers, grotere professionele bouwondernemingen en zzp-ers. Het verheugt ons dat óók de particulier steeds vaker zijn weg vindt naar onze prachtige winkels en magazijnen. Bouwcenter Concordia biedt een bijzonder breed pakket aan materialen voor verbouw, nieuwbouw of renovatie, van bouwmaterialen, sierbestrating, gevelbekleding, wand- en vloertegels, natuursteen, keukens en badkamers tot garage-, binnen- en buitendeuren. Daarnaast bieden wij een pakket aan ondersteunend materiaal, zoals elektrische of handgereedschappen, bevestigingsmaterialen, klimmaterieel, stukadoorsproducten, werk- en veiligheidskleding en installatiematerialen. Onze voorraden zijn dusdanig groot dat een klant nooit misgrijpt en bestellingen binnen 24 uur geleverd krijgt.  Bouwprojecten vergen vakmanschap. Bouwcenter Concordia begrijpt dat als geen ander. Ons doel is onze klanten optimaal te ondersteunen met kennis, professionaliteit en kwaliteit. Daarnaast staan wij bekend om onze snelheid en accuratesse. Bouwcenter Concordia onderneemt bovendien met oog voor de omgeving. Samen met onze klanten zetten wij in op duurzaam bouwen en renoveren. Wij streven naar energiezuinigheid en het gebruik van materialen die het milieu zo min mogelijk belasten en die een lange levensduur hebben.  Concordia heeft vestigingen in Meppel, Hoogeveen, Dedemsvaart, Dieverbrug, Steenwijk, Heerenveen, Roden, Genemuiden, Grijpskerk, Dronten, Urk en Elburg. Er is er dus altijd eentje dichtbij. De koffie staat klaar!

Name: Kiebitzberg Gruppe
Company description: Manufacturer of all kinds of furniture, high-quality kitchens, floating and mobile buildings as well as solid surface material design. The Kiebitzberg Group (shipyard, furniture workshops, planning offices, art hotel) was founded in 1985 by Andreas Lewerken and is still fully family-owned today. The shipyard itself has a 300-year history. Today the group includes 100 skilled workers with 5 locations in Germany from Hamburg to Leipzig. Sustainability and constant optimization of climate goals, as well as consistent investment in the machinery, give our customers an environmentally conscious feeling and investment protection in the products.

Name: E90 Srl
Company description: E90 has been providing natural stone design solutions for twenty-eight years with personalized service to its clients: from project analysis, marble or stone selection, design, processing, finishing, to on-site management and installation of projects that span the globe. Some of our best works can be seen at Hotel Cafè Royal (London - UK), Hotel Lutetia (Paris - France), W Hotel (Tel - Aviv), Gum stores and historical bathrooms (Moscow) and many more. Great experience in supply and installation of materials for Luxury Homes, Kitchen & Bath Design, Boutique Hotels, Wall Décor, Flooring, Architectural Design, Interior Design. Our principal forces are: •	Some materials are unique in their sector •	Quick production and response time •	The flexibility of custom-made colors, patterns, design, and finishing Our company is based in central Italy and it is fully equipped for processing and installation of materials like Marble, Granite, Terrazzo Stone, Quartz compounds, Stone resin, and cement.

Name: Bouwcenter Van Hoppe | Centen
Company description: Bouwcenter Van Hoppe in Eersel en Bouwcenter Centen in Wanroij zijn regionale leveranciers van bouwmaterialen en aangesloten bij de Veris Bouwmaterialengroep.  Met in totaal 95 vestigingen in Nederland is Veris Bouwmaterialengroep een samenwerkingsverband van 31 zelfstandige handelaren in keukens, sanitair, tegels, hout en bouwmaterialen. De Veris Bouwmaterialengroep BV fungeert als backoffice voor de bij Veris aangesloten bedrijven die de formule Bouwcenter hanteren. De kernwaarden van de backoffice zijn inkoop, logistiek, informatisering en automatisering. Een van de belangrijkste taken is de inkoop van bouwmaterialen, hout en plaatmateriaal, gereedschappen en ijzerwaren, keukens, tegels en sanitair.  Bouwcenter Van Hoppe | Centen werkt in totaal met een team van 50 deskundige en enthousiaste medewerkers, die klanten adviseren over de toepassing en verwerking van bouwmaterialen. Het producten pakket bestaat uit een breed assortiment bouwmaterialen, gereedschappen, hout & plaat, parket & laminaat, deuren,  keukens en tegels.  Het onderscheidend vermogen ligt in de kennis van producten & materialen en de klantbenadering: hulpvaardig, vindingrijk en servicegericht. Bouwcenter Van Hoppe | Centen biedt dus alles wat nodig is voor bouw of verbouw, zowel binnens- als buitenshuis. En dat allemaal onder één dak!

Name: Tre P Ceramiche Srl
HQ Location: Italy, Latium, Roma, 127 Via Della Maglianella, 00100
Company description: Cinquanta anni di esperienza, cinquanta anni di innovazioni, ampliamenti della sala espositiva e del deposito esterno per i materiali pronti, cinquanta anni di lavoro serio. Questo e i migliori marchi al mondo trattati, garantiscono il massimo per chiunque ha intenzione di affidarsi alla Tre P Ceramiche. Vaste sale completamente dedicate all'arredamento del bagno, dai saitari alla rubinetteria, dalle mattonelle agli accessori. Due showroom dove sono esposti i migliori pavimenti, da esterno ed interno, per rivestire il salone, la cucina in muratura e le camere e sale Hi-teck, dove presentiamo le novità della fiera, i mosaici, i lavabi in cristallo integrato, mobili in wengè, idromassaggio, i marmi e le porte Scrigno. Siamo in continua evoluzione.   seguici anche su Facebook e instagram per avere tutti gli aggiornamenti e le offerte Tre P Ceramiche ShowRoom MAGLIANELLA Via della Maglianella N° 127/131 - Roma Tre P Ceramiche ShowRoom APPIA Via Appia Nuova 1240 b - Roma (di fronte Ippodromo Capannelle)

Name: Sigdal Kjøkken - Nobia Norway AS
Company description: Sigdal Kjøkken - Nobia Norway AS has been a prominent player in the Norwegian kitchen market since its establishment in 1950, focusing on high-quality craftsmanship, innovative technology, and timeless design. With a mission to provide beautiful and modern kitchens for every home, the company has successfully produced around 7,000 complete kitchens annually, making its products a staple in thousands of households across Norway. Sigdal's design philosophy emphasizes the kitchen as a multifunctional space that fosters social interaction and creativity, offering tailored solutions to meet individual customer needs. The company has recently launched the RE:New concept, promoting sustainability by allowing customers to refresh their existing kitchens with new components, thereby extending their lifespan. Collaborating with renowned designer Lotta Agaton, Sigdal has introduced the "Warm Minimalism" kitchen concept, which blends simplicity with warmth and creativity. Targeting homeowners seeking both functionality and aesthetic appeal, Sigdal Kjøkken continues to strengthen its reputation as one of Norway's most respected kitchen brands.

Name: Dorsch
Company description: When DORSCH first came to life in 2013, we strove to stand up in a crowded market. With lots of enthusiasm, well-planning, ingenious designs, and quality control, DORSCH is now one of the leading brands in the industry.  DORSCH has a wide range of products that are made of the finest materials that comply with the German Safety Standards and we use Premium German coating “GREBLON” as well.  All DORCSH products comply with the “TUV” Safety Standards.  In designing our products, we made studies to understand the actual need of the market for an easy, healthy, and stress-free cooking and a better life. Our insight has led us to design an easy handling yet durable products, and our slogan, “your kitchen partner,” demonstrates our interest in our customers’ well being.  Our long term vision is to be present in most of the countries of the world. Our head office is located in Copenhagen, Denmark and is responsible for business development, product distribution and customer service for the European countries while DORSCH Regional Office in Istanbul, Turkey is responsible for managing the distribution business for the MENA region. DORSCH, Enjoy Cooking!

Name: Gruppo Cascella Mobili
Company description: Cascella Mobili offre un'alta personalizzazione degli arredamenti di ogni tipo, dalla cucina classica e moderna alle camerette, dalla camera da letto al soggiorno. L'alta qualità del piccolo negozio sotto casa. La convenienza di un grande Gruppo.

Name: Kolektor Liv d.o.o.
Company description: Liv brand offers sanitary installation  and flushing systems, as well as electronic flushing and urinal controls, traps and syphons for the residential,  commercial and public construction industry. Products: WC water cisterns (built-in, dry mounting and visible), sanitary and kitchen syphons. Blagovna znamka Liv ima pomembno vlogo v segmentu ponudnikov izdelkov sanitarne tehnike (podometni in nadometni wc splakovalniki, oprema za javne sanitarne prostore, suhomontažni elementi, sifoni, wc deske). Načrtno delovanje, predana in izkušena ekipa ter posluh za potrebe kupca nam omogočajo, da vedno ponudimo kakovostne izdelke, zasnovane na najsodobnejši tehnologiji in oblikovane z najnovejšimi trendi.

Name: Grena A.s.
HQ Location: Czech Republic, Veselí Nad Lužnicí, 541 Třída Čs. Armády, 391 81
Company description: Grena, a.s. je tradiční český výrobce vermikulitových protipožárních, nehořlavých, žáruvzdorných a izolačních materiálů Grenamat, kuchyňských a nábytkových dvířek Grena DD a desek s vysokým leskem či hlubokým matem Grenagloss. Hlavní oblastí výroby jsou protipožární, nehořlavé, žáruvzdorné a izolační vermikulitové desky a tvarové dílce. Tyto produkty mají široké využití ve stavebnictví, lodním průmyslu, při stavbě krbů a kamen, výrobě dveří a v řadě dalších odvětví. Grena má s touto výrobou zkušenosti přes 20 let a svůj sortiment dováží do více než 30 zemí světa. Druhá divize se orientuje na povrchové úpravy materiálů (lamino, dýha, kašírování, CPL, HPL, akryláty) a výrobu nábytkových dvířek.  Grena, a.s. is a building materials company. We are the traditional Czech manufacturer of vermiculite fire-resistant, non-combustible, refractory and insulating materials Grenamat, kitchen and furniture doors Grena DD and high-gloss or deep matt panels Grenagloss. The main areas of production are fire-resistant, non-combustible, refractory and insulating vermiculite boards and shapes. These products are widely used in construction, shipbuilding, fireplace and stove construction, door manufacturing and many other industries. Grena has over 20 years of experience with this production and imports its range to more than 30 countries. The second division focuses on surface treatment of materials and the production of furniture doors.

Name: Sanimex
HQ Location: Belgium, Brussels Capital, Brussels, 669 Chaussée De Mons, 1070
Company description: SANIMEX est une société forte d'une expérience de plus de 20 ans dans le domaine du carrelage, sanitaire et des cuisines équipées. SANIMEX c'est deux points de vente avec plus de 1000 et 1500m² de show-room avec parking. SANIMEX est connu pour la qualité et le large choix de ses produits, ainsi que pour ses meilleures conditions. Une équipe de professionnels est mise à votre disposition pour vous aider dans votre choix et ce selon votre budget. SANIMEX, c'est la rénovation de votre intérieur à des prix attractifs. N'hésitez pas à nous rendre visite ou nous contacter par message privé ou au 02/527.37.60

HQ Location: Ireland, Fakaofo, Roscommon, Racecourse Road, xd45
Company description: MLK (Mark Lohan Kitchens) are an award winning Irish kitchen manufacturer with over 20 years experience and expertise designing, crafting and professionally installing bespoke kitchens, and home cabinetry for clients across Ireland and the UK. Commercial clients benefit from working with a company who have the capabilities and capacity to manufacturer for large scale projects both in Ireland and the UK.

HQ Location: Spain, Las Palmas, Parcela, C/ Ciprés, 35118
