Company description: Diepeveen keukens & badkamers is een familiebedrijf, waar Aris & Gijsbert Diepeveen dagelijks met veel enthousiasme werken aan dat verschil voor jou. Zodra je de showroom van Diepeveen keukens en badkamers binnenloopt, ervaar je de heerlijk ruime opzet van onze keukens en badkamers, onze creatieve instelling en onze persoonlijke benadering. Wij maken graag het verschil, en dat zal je zeker merken.

Name: GRUNKEL
HQ Location: Spain, Andalusia, Dos Hermanas, 15 Calle Torre De Los Herberos, 41703
Company description: GRUNKEL es una marca familiar fundada en 1985 en la provincia de Sevilla (España), y dedicada a la venta de electrodomésticos de toda índole. Desde GRUNKEL nos hace felices poder compartir momentos contigo, desde pequeñas utilidades para tu cocina hasta grandes televisores para tu salón con la última tecnología Smart TV. En GRUNKEL intentamos mantener esa esencia de pequeña gran familia que tanto nos caracteriza, fomentando el trabajo en equipo para hacer de la empresa un hogar para nuestros trabajadores. Para nosotros es muy importante fomentar el compañerismo y el buen ambiente de trabajo dado que, si queremos trabajar al servicio de las familias es importante empezar por la nuestra. Además, focalizamos nuestra actividad en intentar siempre atender a las necesidades de nuestros clientes, luchando siempre por mejorar la calidad de nuestros productos y por reinventarnos continuamente para responder a las novedades en tendencias del hogar.

Name: Alaia Home
Company description: Una nueva forma de renovar tu casa. Te acompañamos en cada paso del camino, con asesoramiento desde el primer momento y desde tu propia casa. Creamos espacios aportando tu carácter, marcando una impronta que aporta elegancia, originalidad y que te invitan a vivirlos. Visita nuestra web y te ayudamos a configurar tu espacio online, podrás visualizar desde la comodidad de tu sofá como quedará tu nueva cocina, o tu nuevo baño, o el espacio que te has imaginado. Te lo ponemos fácil, olvídate de tener que desplazarte y visitar un estudio, elegir materiales, complementos,..., te enviamos a un diseñador a tu casa que te guiará, acompañará y resolverá tus dudas durante todo el proceso. Simplemente tienes que imaginar lo que quieres hacer, nosotros nos encargamos de todo lo demás.

Name: Second Life Kitchen S.r.l.
Company description: Fondato a Pesaro nel 2010, Second Life Kitchen è un progetto innovativo sviluppato dall'esperienza di un team di esperti del settore dell'arredamento.  L’idea Second Life Kitchen anticipa il futuro: rinnovare la cucina – e non solo (armadi, archivi, mobili, etc.) – mantenendo la struttura di base e sostituendo ante, cerniere, accessori e tutte le parti parzialmente o completamente rovinate dall’invecchiamento o superate da un punto di vista tecnologico ed estetico. Il concetto del “donare una seconda vita” è, per Second Life Kitchen, la spinta più grande per la ricerca dell’eccellenza: immaginare modi nuovi di rendere uno spazio più splendido e vivibile, recuperando le importantissime risorse ambientali di cui sono fatte le cucine e i mobili, è il concetto chiave della filosofia aziendale.  Alla base del successo dell’attività, vi è la fusione tra l’esperienza dei migliori partner nella produzione di componenti della cucina ed elettrodomestici e la professionalità dei consulenti scelti: una perfetta unione che ha portato al consolidamento del marchio Second Life Kitchen a livello nazionale.

Name: Riccardo Barthel
HQ Location: Italy, Tuscany, Florence, 234r Via Dei Serragli, 50124
Company description: Riccardo Barthel dal 1976 non rappresenta un tradizionale showroom ma uno stile preciso, unico ed inconfondibile: lo stile Barthel. Negli anni l'Azienda si è evoluta per rispondere puntualmente alle richieste sempre più esigenti dei propri Clienti in Italia e nel Mondo.  Oggi la passione di due generazioni a confronto, unita alla maestria ed alle capacità di architetti ed esperti artigiani, muove l'Azienda alla ricerca dell'eccellenza e della perfezione. La mission Riccardo Barthel è continuare a produrre ed arredare con il proprio stile inconfondibile ville e dimore, gli yacht e qualsiasi tipologia di ambiente nel rispetto dei valori e della tradizione dell'artigianalità fiorentina, divenendone così dalla Toscana e da Firenze “Ambasciatore nel mondo”. Il Made in Italy viene così proposto ed esaltato per qualsiasi esigenza di ristrutturazione e arredamento: materiali di pregio e soluzioni professionali per la cucina ma anche per l'arredamento di hotel e qualsivoglia esigenza specifica, come ad esempio per il rivestimento di mattonelle che ha reso celebre Riccardo Barthel in questi anni. tessuti, sanitari o tappezzeria per proposte di arredamento e di decorazione di classe e in stile Casa Barthel.

Name: Prima Cucine S.r.l
Company description: Cucine di design, dalla personalità forte, studiate per differenti esigenze. È dal 2017 che proponiamo al nostro mercato cucine dalle personalità decise, studiate nel dettaglio per poter soddisfare le esigenze più diverse. Noi di Prima Cucine siamo un gruppo di esperti cucinieri veneti che dedica il proprio lavoro ad un cliente sensibile alle nuove tendenze in termini estetici, compositivi e di materiali scelti. Proponiamo così una gamma collezioni che, sfruttando l’alta modularità e componibilità, sono in grado di creare soluzioni ad hoc e su misura, in risposta a specifiche esigenze e bisogni.  Mettere al centro i nostri clienti ci ha aiutato a proporre le nostre collezioni ad un prezzo conveniente quanto basta per poter garantire la solidità e durabilità di un prodotto che solo il Made in Italy può promettere.  Scegliere Prima Cucine significa scegliere un brand funzionale anche per i propri living, che possono essere costruiti in linea con design ed estetica della propria cucina.  Un brand italiano, con produzione e logistica presso la sede operativa di Trebaseleghe (PD).  Un brand presente su tutto il territorio italiano con una rete di rivenditori che garantisce una distribuzione capillare. Scopri tutte le collezioni proposte da Prima Cucine.

Name: Aurora Cucine Scrl
HQ Location: Italy, Tuscany, Poggibonsi, Via Dei Pioppi Loc. Bellavista, 53036
Company description: Aurora born in Poggibonsi (Siena) in 1947 as a family business specialized in the production of iron furniture. In the early 1960s, it entered the world of kitchens with modular models and then evolved over time, adapting products and services to the needs of the modern customer. Today, the range of Aurora products has typical "Styled & Made in Italy" connotations with great attention to ecological issues, specializing in two stylistic areas: Modern Design and Modern Country.

Name: Dibiesse Cucine
HQ Location: Italy, Treviso, Miane, 28 Via G. Rossini, 31050
Company description: Dal 1973 ci impegniamo per progettare e produrre cucine di qualità: belle, fatte bene, che durano nel tempo.  From 1973 we are specialized in the production of quality kitchens: beautiful, functional and that will last a lifetime.

Name: Pedrini PPL spa
HQ Location: Italy, Brescia, Roncadelle, 16 Via Enzo Ferrari, 25030
Company description: The origins of the company. 80 years of history, where tradition meets innovation and aesthetic research meets functionality: this is the Pedrini identity in a nutshell. The company came into being in Lumezzane thanks tothe entrepreneurial tenacity of its founder Giuseppe Pedrini, in an industrial area which was the home of metal working in Italy. It is a company that has been able to rapidly evolve from a small business to an industrial firm thanks to original ideas, cutting edge solutions and a real passion for quality.  This is shown by its achievements such as the launch of the first two lever corkscrew, the success of lines that have become synonymous with Italian design in the kitchen, such as “Lillo”, and the creations developed in collaboration with famous designers.  The brand values. Pedrini interprets characterizing brand values, which are at the basis of its success on increasingly demanding and competitive markets. For everyone who is attentive to the quality, design, functionality and duration of products, Pedrini offers solutions that combine great experience in production with cutting-edge constructive decisions and materials, in line with today’s lifestyle: modern, dynamic, attracted by design but without giving up convenience and where the kitchen is the heart of the home.

Name: FIR Villadossola
Company description: La nostra missione è progettare, vendere, installare ed assistere come se fosse per la nostra casa. Da oltre 50 anni, assistiamo il cliente nella ricerca delle migliori soluzioni d'arredo: arredobagno, wellness, rivestimenti, pavimenti, stufe, camini, cucine.  Tanti prodotti, un unico stile: il tuo.

Name: Mobitaly - Italian Furniture Craft And Design
HQ Location: Italy, An, Camerano, 39/41 Via Direttissima Del Conero, 60021
Company description: MobItaly was born in 2011 from the initiative of young artisans and professionals, to produce custom-made italian furniture.  The cooperative has a corporate structure of 24 people, all former employees of important companies operating in the furniture sector. Mobitaly, therefore, can count on strong technical/production expertise and know-how deriving from years of experience in the design and construction of modular kitchens. The specific capabilities of the components allow the company to operate not only in the kitchen sector, but also in the living and bathroom sectors as well as in the contract sector. A single interlocutor to manage the complexity of large projects such as residential complexes, luxury hotels, public spaces, commercial chains or buildings in large cities. Mobitaly’s management is reliable and professional, ensuring planning with clear time frames, custom solutions and high quality processing, guaranteed delivery and precision of execution. In the turnkey industry, we are operative in the five continents: starting from New York, the great apple that never stops, where we provided turnkey solutions for the residential sector, passing through Miami with work on a luxurious resort and ending in Africa, the new continent that hired our company for custom solutions in large cities. And let’s not forget our country: in Rome we worked in precious palaces that became unique and luxurious residences. To affirm our taste and pursuit of quality. We are a reliable partner and the experience of our technicians is guaranteed by the series of important references in the sector.

Name: Officine Fanesi
HQ Location: Italy, Metauro, 3 Via Leonardo Da Vinci, 61036
Company description: The kitchen tailored to your space. In the Officine Fanesi workshop, we take care of each project in detail, following all the phases of production. The particularity of our product is the ability to cover the needs of those who are looking for a customised and unique product.

Name: Ciac Cosmopolitan Home
HQ Location: Italy, Tuscany, Ponsacco, Via Valdera P., 56038
Company description: CIAC Cosmopolitan Home was established in 1977 with the aim of creating a group of Italian furniture manufacturers located in Tuscany region, drawn together by an innovative businessman who wanted to join forces with furniture factories operating at the highest level of quality. His aim was to export their products around the world, at the time a very ambitious project, considering the tendency for young Italian companies in that era to focus solely on the domestic market, with the international export market dominated by a small group of industrial scale mass producers. Since then, CIAC Cosmopolitan Home has pursued its goal with remarkable results, exporting to over 60 countries worldwide with a constant yearly growth. Today CIAC Cosmopolitan Home globally represents and promotes a select group of Italian high-end companies producing both fine classical cabinetwork and contemporary design, from children’s bedrooms to kitchens. Each of these companies has the same goal: Growth and Quality orientation! With 40 years of experience in the luxury sector, CIAC Cosmopolitan Home is a profitable and reliable partner, able to meet the needs of an international market. Our strength is our network: our team consists of 30 people, a highly trained technical group of experts dedicated to custom-made design. Our commercial network has been expanded to include several countries in Africa, as well as China and several other nations in the Far East. Our main priority has always been to build a direct link between our factories and customers, to ensure that, together, we make the most of the best opportunities as they present themselves, now and in the future.

Name: Arredamenti Riuniti Lombardia Srl

Company description: Arredamenti Riuniti nella sede unica di Calcinate (Bergamo) è un’azienda nata dall’unione di un pool di imprenditori con un’esperienza più che ventennale nell’arredamento. Oltre a possedere una conoscenza approfondita dell’intero settore, quest’impresa vanta rapporti consolidati, diretti e senza intermediazioni quali rappresentanze, grossisti o distributori monomarca. Gli elevatissimi volumi d’acquisto fanno di Arredamenti Riuniti uno dei primi negozi d’Italia nella vendita di arredamenti di qualità. Questa assenza di costi intermedi unitamente ai favorevoli rapporti d’acquisto ci consente di offrirvi le migliori novità del settore ad un prezzo accessibile, con una gamma di centinaia di proposte: dalle cucine alle camere, armadi, soggiorni, divani, camerette.

Name: Mobili Badini

Company description: Il Mobilificio Badini si trova a Cerveteri, dove è in attività dal 1967 nel settore della vendita di mobili ed arredi. Il mobilificio offre servizi di progettazione degli ambienti e di architettura d'interni, proponendo un'ampia gamma di arredamenti sia per la casa che per l'ufficio. Nello show-room di 3000 mq potrete prendere visione delle tante soluzioni di arredo proposte e toccare con mano la qualità dei mobili Badini, scegliendo tra cucine componibili, mobili per la zona giorno e la zona notte, mobili classici e moderni, arredo bagno, tavoli e sedie, divani, pareti attrezzate e librerie, ma anche letti, armadi, complementi di arredo, mobili per ragazzi e mobili da giardino, tutti realizzati anche su misura.

Name: Icon Design Solution

Our mission is to give shape to customers' ideas by providing a complete service and customized solutions. Each project is executed with dedication by proposing a vision of functional and practical beauty, suitable for all environments, following distinct styles and satisfying different needs. In our showroom in the heart of Trieste, customers have the opportunity to touch the quality of the rich assortment of renowned brands and meet the furniture professionals in ad hoc spaces that expertly cut into the exhibition concept. Our team of architects and interior designers takes care of analyzing the needs and desires of each client and follows them step by step in the enhancement and realization of their ideas, recommending the most suitable products for their style and needs. Our customers can do every project also from the comfort of their homes. Our staff will help furnish and personalize any room online, choosing from a wide range of products.  Browsing our e-shop means designing your dream home from start to finish. Discover classic and contemporary kitchens and explore modular combinations and design furnishings to create tailor-made living areas. Choose beds and mattresses, wardrobes and bedside tables to create a welcoming and comfortable atmosphere in the sleeping area. There are also solutions for the dream bathroom, a perfect synthesis of functionality and aesthetics, and the ideal lighting to create the overall harmony that enhances every furniture detail. The best furniture and design brands, an interior design team with architects to design environments without leaving anything to chance, and an ad hoc installation service: We are Icon Design Solution, a Triestine company that operates worldwide.

Name: Pittori 1931
HQ Location: Italy, Matelica Marche, 5 Via San Giacomo Della Marca, 62024
Company description: La “Pittori 1931” , forte della pluridecennale esperienza nella produzione di cucine  è lieta di proporsi a tutti quei clienti, professionisti e non, che, condividendo con noi la passione per l’eccellenza e la bellezza, siano alla ricerca di un partner assolutamente affidabile e di grande esperienza. Ogni cucina Pittori è frutto di un attenta ricerca di materiali e un accurato studio delle esigenze di ogni singolo cliente, con un attenzione particolare rivolta alla assoluta personalizzazione del prodotto e alla maniacale ricerca del perfetto connubio tra passato e futuro. Tradizione, tecnologia, qualita’ ed eccellenza trovano una nuova dimensione dove ogni desiderio è possibile. La produzione, completamente realizzata nel nostro stabilimento, coniuga le migliori tecnologie per la lavorazione del legno alla sapiente mano dell’uomo, dando vita a qualsivoglia progetto di arredo.  Venite e scoprite un mondo dove passione e creativitá danno vita ad un nuovo modo di fare arredamento. The “Pittori Cucine“, thanks to the decades of experience in the production of the highest quality  kitchens, is pleased to offer its service to all the customers, professionals and not, who share our passion for the excellence and beauty, and are looking for a reliable and highly experienced partner.  The kitchens “Pittori” are the result of a careful selection of materials and of attent study of the needs of each individual customer, with particular attention paid to complete customization of the product and to obsessive search for the perfect blend of past and future. Tradition, technology, quality and excellence meet in a new dimension where every wish cancome true.  The production, made entirely in our factory, combines the best technologies of wood processing with the handcraft of experienced artisan, giving life to any décor project.  Come and discover a world where passion unites with creativity in a new way of making furniture.

Name: Sanasi Cucine

Il legno è il materiale che dà forza e resistenza alle cucine Sanasi, insieme ai metalli e alle superfici che ne definiscono le rifiniture e i dettagli.

Projects are delivered by a team of over 130 experienced specialists, including lighting and kitchen architects, furniture, decoration and plumbing experts, textile designers, project managers and logistics specialists, ensuring successful implementation of complex individual orders, regardless of the location – be it London, Maiami, Dubai, Zürich, Monaco, Cyprus, Majorca or Lerici.

Name: Kemner Home Company
Company description: Wir zählen zu einem der außergewöhnlichsten Möbelhäuser Deutschlands mit Sitz in der Region Geestland. Unsere Philosophie – Möbel Dein Leben auf! Name: Senso Ambiente Ltd

Name: Centroservice S.r.l.

Name: Meson's
HQ Location: Italy, Pn, Pasiano Di Pordenone, 1 Via Gradisca, 33087
Company description: Le collezioni del catalogo Meson’s sono disegnate per incontrare le diverse esigenze di un pubblico eterogeneo ma caratterizzato dalla comune passione per l'eccellenza. Nel progettare le nostre collezioni, prestiamo attenzione a dettagli apparentemente secondari, poiché siamo convinti che “far bene” non basti. Testiamo e collaudiamo continuamente i nostri prodotti sin dalla fase di prototipazione, per garantire la soddisfazione di chi ha scelto di investire in una cucina Meson's. Name: STILCURVI Srl
HQ Location: Italy, Veneto, Meduna Di Livenza, 27 Via Corella, 31040
Company description: The company was founded in 1986 and is based in Meduna di Livenza (North East of Italy, 60 km far from Venice airport).  Its roots are firmly embedded in its knowledge and expertise of raw materials which are modelled and turned into shapes that are difficult to tame. In fact, the name Stilcurvi is a reference to these "curves" and the starting point of the company’s long history which has brought it to where it is today, with 170 employees and indoor production facilities covering around 70.000 square meters. In the Nineties the company expanded, supplying to its customers finished furnitures as well as wood accessories for the furniture industry. Thanks to the past 20 years' investments, today Stilcurvi's offer includes curved items for kitchens, bathrooms and bedrooms of any type, shape and finish (lacquered with polyurethanic lacquer, wrapped with PET/PVC foil or veneered), gloss/matt UV-painted panels and melamine faced chipboard/mdf frontals with(/without) integrated handle. Cutting-edge technologies combined with a strong workmanship enable Stilcurvi to deliver products of the highest standards, ensuring to its customers a thorough control over its manufacturing process as well as competitive prices. L'azienda è stata fondata nel 1986 e si trova a Meduna di Livenza (Tv): conta 170 dipendenti e si sviluppa su circa 70.000 mq di superficie coperta. Grazie agli investimenti degli ultimi 20 anni, oggi l'offerta di Stilcurvi comprende articoli curvi per cucine, bagni e camere di ogni tipo, forma e finitura (laccati con vernice poliuretanica, avvolti con foglie polimeriche o impiallacciati), pannelli verniciati lucido/opaco UV e pannelli in truciolare/mdf nobilitato anche con maniglia integrata. Tecnologie all'avanguardia combinate ad una spiccata abilità artigianale consentono a Stilcurvi di offrire prodotti di altissimo livello, garantendo ai propri clienti un controllo a 360° sul proprio processo produttivo ed allo stesso tempo prezzi competitivi.

Name: Telese
Company description: Whether it is about creating a functional and welcoming kitchen for a private residence or designing tailored solutions for large contract projects, Telese has always been committed to exceeding customer expectations through impeccable craftsmanship, the quality of materials, and the attention to detail that characterize every project undertaken. Telese was founded over 60 years ago as a large joinery. Acquired by its founder Angelo Telese, it has deep roots in traditional craftsmanship. The experience gained over the years is the solid foundation upon which we build our kitchens and furniture items, adding artisanal care and industrial innovation to create environments that reflect the nature and desires of those who will inhabit them. The company now has a well-established tradition in the field of custom furniture, with decades of experience in the industry. Constantly evolving over the years, it is now a reference point in the sector both in Italy and internationally. Our distinctive approach is completely bespoke production, characterized by true tailoring in the design and realization of furniture. Each piece is created with artisanal care and attention to detail, ensuring not only perfect adaptability to spaces but also high aesthetic and functional quality. The work phases follow strict quality standards, from design to realization, ensuring excellent and customized results for every client.

Name: Fabryka Mebli STOLKAR
Company description: Od ponad 35 lat produkujemy 𝗺𝗲𝗯𝗹𝗲 𝗸𝘂𝗰𝗵𝗲𝗻𝗻𝗲, które zdobywają serca i zaufanie indywidualnych oraz biznesowych odbiorców. Meble STOLKAR to idealny sposób na aranżację każdego wnętrza w stylu klasycznym, eleganckim, nowoczesnym czy minimalistycznym. Nasze meble do kuchni to synonim niebanalnego designu oraz wysokiej jakości. Tradycyjne nurty połączone z najnowszymi trendami, szeroka paleta kolorów i struktur, personalizacja na miarę własnych potrzeb – meble STOLKAR odmienią każdą przestrzeń.   For over 35 years, we have been producing kitchen furniture products that win the hearts and trust of individual and business recipients. STOLKAR furniture is the perfect way to arrange any interior in a classic, elegant, modern or minimalist style. Our kitchen furniture is synonymous with original design and high quality. Traditional trends combined with the latest trends, a wide range of colors and structures, customization to suit your needs - STOLKAR furniture will transform any space.

Name: Næstved Flisecenter
Company description: Sjællands største udvalg i fliser, klinker, mosaik, granit, marmor, skifer og kompositsten. Egne Projektkonsulenter, der kan rådgive både Arkitekter, Entreprenører og andre beslutningstagere i projektmarkedet. Uanset om det er til køkken, bad, gulve eller til udendørs brug, kan Næstved Flisecenter hjælpe med at finde den løsning, som både er egnet til opgaven og som passer til din personlige smag, behov og økonomi. Med over 80.000 m2 fliser, klinker, mosaik og natursten på lager fordelt på op mod 1000 forskellige slags, har Næstved Flisecenter intet mindre end Sjællands største udvalg, som vises frem både i vor udstilling med opbyggede miljøer og på store og mindre plancher. Mere end 30 års erfaring med skæring/forarbejdning af natursten giver kunderne sikkerhed for stor ekspertise på dette felt. CNC-styret produktion af bordplader til køkken, badeværelser, trapper, vinduesplader og sålbænke, både individuelt tilskåret og i standardmål, og såvel til indendørs brug som til udendørs belægning med de bedst egnede overflader.

Name: INDUMAG
Company description: A INDUMAG - Indústria de Mármore e Granitos Ornamentais, Lda. é uma empresa que se dedica à transformação de todo o tipo de calcários, brechas, mármores e granitos. A empresa fundada em 1992, situa-se na zona industrial de Viadores, freguesia da Pampilhosa concelho da Mealhada, distrito de Aveiro. Sendo uma empresa com uma vasta experiência na transformação de pedra, a INDUMAG trabalha com matérias-primas nacionais e estrangeiras. Com grande flexibilidade produtiva, a INDUMAG desenvolve uma ampla gama de produtos: •Todo o tipo de componente para contrução civil; •Pavimentos e revestimentos standard ou à medida nas mais variadas hipóteses de acabamento superficial; •Tampos para móveis de casa de banho, cozinha e mobiliário clássico; •Mobiliário decorativo e peças especiais; •Fogões de sala; Dispõe de um gabinete técnico composto por uma equipa especializada dedicada à elaboração de projectos (sejam projectos de raiz, seja a adopção de estereotonomia definida pela arquitectura às medidas reais da obra) e de soluções decorativas, como sejam os espaços banho, jantar e estar, fachadas, etc... Com boa capacidade de resposta e zelando pela qualidade dos seus produtos e pelo cumprimento de prazos de entrega, a INDUMAG oferece aos seus clientes condições que têm permitido uma rápida preparação e execução de obra. Este é sem dúvida uma das razões pela qual a empresa tem merecido a confiança de muitos clientes nomeadamente da área da hotelaria e restauração.

Wenn Sie aus ganzem Herzen sagen können: Das ist meine Küche, dann sind wir erfolgreich. Denn die Küche ist endlich wieder der Mittelpunkt häuslichen Lebens. Company description: Înfiinţată în 1994, TEMAD este una din cele mai importante companii de distribuţie din România, recunoscută pe piaţa materialelor auxiliare pentru construcţii, renovari, industrie, casa si gradina, auto si pet food. Compania are un portofoliu vast de produse de calitate superioară ce acoperă o arie foarte largă de aplicaţii şi utilizări: adezivi, etanşeizanţi, spume poliuretanice, vopsele spray auto, decorative şi speciale, spray-uri tehnice, echipamente de protecţie, sisteme de fixare, abrazive şi scule aşchietoare, profile din aluminiu şi PVC, accesorii pentru zugrăvit, accesorii pentru termoizolaţii şi pentru gips-caton, benzi adezive şi de etanşare, tencuieli decorative, accesorii pentru baie şi bucătărie, produse de curăţat, răşini, scule de măsurare şi de grădinărit, vopsele lavabile, vopsele pentru lemn, vopsele pentru suprafete din beton. Grupul de firme TEMAD În contextul economic actual, crearea propriilor centre de producţie reprezintă o prioritate în strategia de dezvoltare a companiei TEMAD, atât prin implicare în dezvoltarea regională cât şi pentru optimizarea costurilor operaţionale. Astfel că, în anul 2013 s-a luat decizia înfiinţării a unei noi companii: TEMAD ENERGIE, care detine o centrală fotovoltaică la Râșnov - Brașov.

Name: TWIST
Company description: TWIST is a compact, convenient easy vend solution tailor-made to provide Snacks and Beverages to the European water cooler industry.  The Twist machine fits neatly into any corner, table or counter-top in the office space. End users won’t need a large canteen or kitchen area to securely vend snacks to its employees. Twist distributors simply install a TWIST dispenser with a selection of their existing water cooler clients, insert a mix of the market’s best selling snacks, and watch revenues soar! Clients can purchase snacks and other consumables at any time, with no need for staff help. Anything that fits, you can vend. Snacks, Soft Drinks, Cookies, Chewing Gum, Vitamin Rich Cereal Bars, Dried Fruit or other products can be sold 24 hours a day, when and where your customer needs them most. Fiesta Group, the holding company behind Twist is one of the pioneers of the European Bottled Water cooler industry and is constantly in search of ways and means to improve the range of services it offers to its clients (thereby increasing revenues per point of sale). Fiesta's businesses in Spain and Portugal, today manage a park of 80,000 coolers under the Group’s flagship companies Acqua Jet and Fonte Viva. The TWIST concept has enabled these businesses, to substantially improve their revenues per client and to offer a much improved range of services to their increasingly demanding client base.

Name: Menicacci Sas

Vendiamo materiali per la costruzione e ristrutturazione della casa: pavimenti, rivestimenti, parquet, sanitari, arredo bagno, box e cabine doccia, vasche da bagno, minipiscine idromassaggio, rubinetteria, cucine componibili, accessori bagno in pronta consegna… La lunga storia che abbiamo alle spalle ci ha permesso di maturare una grande esperienza nel settore e di avere un’approfondita conoscenza dei materiali, delle linee, dei fornitori ma soprattutto dei desideri delle persone. Da grandi appassionati del nostro settore stiamo sempre dietro alle evoluzioni tecnologiche e alle ultime tendenze del design, e nel tempo abbiamo fatto un’accurata selezione dei fornitori, arrivando a lavorare con le migliori aziende italiane e potendo così offrire prodotti di elevata qualità tecnica ed estetica.

Name: 2aKüchen

Name: Hartkorn Gewürzmühle GmbH

Als inhabergeführtes Familienunternehmen in vierter Generation entwickeln, mahlen und veredeln wir täglich neue Gewürzmischungen, um die kulinarischen Kreationen unserer Kund:innen zu bereichern.  Unser Sortiment mit über 600 Produkten reicht von unverzichtbaren Basics über ein nachhaltiges Bio-Sortiment, die wichtigsten Gewürze für die nächste Grillparty, moderne Gewürzmischungen für die junge Küche bis hin zu ausgefallenen Gourmetgewürzen. Unsere Produkte bieten den perfekten Genuss für nahezu jedes erdenkliche Gericht – ganz ohne Geschmacksverstärker, Laktose oder Hefeextrakte.  Aber wir sind mehr als nur Gewürzexperten. Jede:r Mitarbeiter:in ist auch ein:e Held:in des Arbeitsalltags. Und unsere Hartkorn Heroes sorgen mit ihren Superkräften für Frieden und Ordnung in der Gewürzwelt und stellen sicher, dass unsere Gewürze jederzeit sicher zu dir nach Hause kommen. Auch wenn sie nicht gegen Superschurken wie Thanos kämpfen, so brennen sie doch für das, was sie tun, genauso wie jeder Marvel-Held.  Fühlst du dich inspiriert von unserer Leidenschaft für Gewürze und unserer Vision, das kulinarische Erlebnis unserer Kund:innen zu bereichern? Möchtest du mehr über unsere Unternehmensphilosophie, unser Marketing und deine mögliche Karriere bei uns erfahren? Dann begleite uns auf unserer Reise und folge uns hier auf LinkedIn! 🌶️🚀  https://hartkorn-gewuerze.de/de/content/impressum.html https://hartkorn-gewuerze.de/de/content/datenschutzerklaerung.html

Name: Eggersmann Küchen GmbH & Co. KG

Polylak is uitgegroeid tot een serieuze speler op de interieurmarkt die probleemloos ook grote projecten tot een goed einde brengt. From our headquarters in Meulebeke, Belgium, we strive to be a true "Home of Creativity" for all our customers, employees and suppliers. Contact us and we will find out what we can do for you !

Name: UNIDOOR BV
Company description: Unidoor heeft een unieke kijk op design, functionaliteit, maatwerk en massaproductie. Houtbewerker, keukenbouwer of interieurinrichter? Wij zijn er voor u. Onze meubelfabriek is uitgerust om zowel snel geautomatiseerd maatwerk te produceren, als grote aantallen.  Of het nu gaat om keukenkastdeuren, keukenonderdelen, werkbladen of (massieve) meubels, al onze realisaties zijn het resultaat van de symbiose tussen vakmanschap en technologische innovatie. Wij maken uw ontwerpen volgens de regels der kunst en met de kwaliteitsgarantie “made by Unidoor”. Wij bieden zowel de sporadische klanten als onze vaste partners een zelfde efficiënte en snelle uitvoering van hun opdrachten. En dit steeds op een manier die volledig aan de verwachtingen voldoet. In onze lakkerij werken wij onze keuken- en kastdeuren, meubels en meubelonderdelen af naar uw wens en volgens uw technische voorschriften. Veel collega houtbewerkers vertrouwen hun panelen en meubels aan onze zorg toe. Ze kunnen rekenen op een perfecte afwerking en snelle levering. Wij hebben een traditie van innovatie. In onze hallen en in ons atelier treft u de modernste machines op de markt aan. Zulke investeringen zorgen ervoor dat bij ons kwaliteit en stukwerk samen gaan en dit tegen scherpe prijzen.  Bij Unidoor heerst een cultuur van openheid, respect, teamspirit en vertrouwen waarin initiatief, creativiteit en passie voor hout bijzonder goed gedijen. Authenticiteit en betrokkenheid typeren onze managementstijl. Als familiebedrijf willen we in al wat we ondernemen een lange-termijn perspectief hanteren. We voelen ons betrokken bij het welzijn van onze klanten, leveranciers, onze medewerkers en de lokale gemeenschap.

Name: Himlekök
Company description: Himlekök tillverkar kök, badrum och annan skåpsbaserad inredning.  Allt tillverkas för hand av våra duktiga möbelsnickare på våra fabriker i Träslövsläge och Falkenberg. På Himlekök arbetar det möbelsnickare samt designers som tillsammans med våra kunder designar, tillverkar och säljer skräddarsydda inredningar av högsta kvalitet.   Genom att inte ha några återförsäljare håller vi nere kostnaderna och kan arbeta nära våra kunder genom varje steg av design, tillverkning och montage.

Name: Seipp Wohnen GmbH
Company description: Seipp Wohnen ist eines der führenden Einrichtungshäuser in Deutschland. Seit über 115 Jahren bieten wir unseren Kunden individuelle Einrichtungsberatung, mittlerweile an drei Standorten: Neben dem Haus Waldshut im historischen Stadtzentrum und dem Einrichtungshaus im Park nahe der Tiengener Innenstadt, finden Sie in Konstanz unser Küchenstudio bulthaup am See. Drei Häuser – ein Gedanke: Wohnen ganz persönlich! Ob Wohnen, Schlafen, Küche, Garten, Textilien, Leuchten, Arbeiten und Büro – gelungene Einrichtungsprojekte fangen bei uns mit einer ausführlichen Beratung an. Lieferung, Montage und Service sind im Detail aufeinander abgestimmt. Wir liefern maßgeschneiderte Einrichtungslösungen und sind langjähriger Ansprechpartner für Planungsprojekte. Neben der professionellen und kompetenten Beratung sind der umfassende Service und ein für diese Region einmaliges Sortiment wichtige Bausteine unserer Unternehmensphilosophie. Als erster EMAS zertifiziertes Einrichtungshaus in Deutschland versuchen wir stetig unseren ökologischen Fußabdruck zu verringern. So generiert Seipp Wohnen jedes Jahr rund 141.000 KWh Strom durch die eigene Photovoltaikanlage und liefert die hochwertigen Möbel bereits mit einigen Hybridfahrzeugen aus. E-Tankstellen und Jobrad-Leasingangebote für Mitarbeiter gehören zum ökologischen Selbstverständnis.  In schwierigen Zeiten zählt ein sicherer, familiärer Arbeitsplatz in angenehmer Atmosphäre. Wir können trotz wirtschaftlicher Unbeständigkeit ein stetiges Wachstum verzeichnen. Deshalb sind wir auf der Suche nach kreativen Innenarchitekten/-innen (m/w/i), Interior Designern (m/w/i) oder Einrichtungsberatern (m/w/i). Lassen Sie sich vom Seipp-Spirit anstecken. Eben Seipp like, seit 1902.  Weitere Informationen finden Sie unter seipp.com/jobs.

Our passion for engineering, our ongoing motivation and the satisfaction of our customers are the driving force behind our work and also its foundation. We want to win you over with our experience, our quality, our flexibility and our sensitivity.

Name: Mk Cucine

Name: Craftly
Company description: Craftly produces kits to get you creative in your own kitchen. Our team consists of creators, who love to experiment and produce their own food, drinks, and herbal products. The idea came to Vincent, one of the founding brothers, that we could package up a box that could inspire and get anyone ready to start creating in their own homes. We hope that the kits inspire customers to start making more at home and shopping less for finished products in the stores.  We value the environment and wellbeing of our planet and as so our kits are made with 100% recyclable and compostable materials - not a single unecessary plastic component. The original "Do Your GIn" kit comes with 12 exotic botanicals that allows you to make compound gin in your own home.  The Do Your Gin kit has been a breakthrough hit in USA and German markets, where it was the top selling cocktail kit in Germany during the 2019 Holiday Season. As a follow-up to the success of the gin kit, our next product is "Do Your Whisky", allowing people to make their own whisky at home.  Wholesale Inquiries: sales@doyourgin.com

At the factory we have our own drying ovens, therefore we control the process from the first rough cuts of the wood down to the final process details. Production is made from oak, cherry, beech and lime woods but also from a combination of solid wood and natural veneered MDF. The materials we use: varnish, glue have quality certificates from the “European Union” and are ecologically pure.  The furniture is built with the most modern techniques incorporating the principles of tradition and craftsmanship. The company is manufacturing – bedroom and dining room furniture, kitchens – tables, chairs, beds, cabinets, small solid wood furniture and many more. The wide range of products – more than 500 different models, allows the company to fully upholster hotels, restaurants or private accommodations. We consider this as our main competitive advantage on the furniture market. “EVRICA” produces a custom made furniture – as long as pictures and drawings are supplied we can reproduce almost every wooden furniture model. Name: Monolith Srl
Company description: Monolith è il marchio leader nella realizzazione di rubinetti per cucine industriali, rubinetterie per grandi impianti e attrezzature per comunità. Prodotti di elevata qualità, in grado di offrire l'affidabilità della lunga durata e la funzionalità di un Richiedi un preventivo gratuito online, i professionisti di Monolith Srl saranno lieti di offrirti l'assistenza specializzata necessaria a rinnovare il tuo ambiente di lavoro con i rubinetti industriali più adatti alle tue esigenze.

Name: Alco Srl
HQ Location: Italy, Emilia-romagna, Ferrara, 14 Via Majocchi Plattis, 44124
Company description: Da più di quarant' anni la Alco si occupa della progettazione e realizzazione di locali pubblici. Predispone forniture di attrezzature e arredamenti per ristoranti, bar, pub, pasticcerie, birrerie, panifici, gastronomie, pizzerie, alberghi, agriturismi, grandi comunità e altro. Preventivi gratuiti per qualsiasi tipo di fornitura, realizzazione di disegni per arredamenti e cucine con assistenza su ogni tipo di lavoro. Ampia gamma di attrezzature per la cottura, lavaggio, refrigerazione, aspirazione, preparazione; arredi per la sala quali tavoli e sedie per interno ed esterno; attrezzature complementari quali pentole in acciaio, alluminio e rame, piatti in porcellana e vetro, bicchieri in vetro e cristallo, posateria e coltelleria professionale.

Name: Vertommen NV
Company description: De firma Vertommen biedt een ruime keuze aan badkamers, keukens, verwarmingsinstallaties, ventilatie systemen, airco en wellness. Als groothandel in sanitair en verwarming werkt de firma nauw samen met installateurs, bouwpromotoren, aannemers en architecten. Sinds enkele jaren kent de keukenafdeling een enorme groei.  Zowel voor particulieren als voor projecten, worden de keukens door onze eigen schrijnwerkers geplaatst en tot de laatste puntjes opgevolgd. Onze badkamer- keuken- en verwarmingsspecialisten zorgen voor 3D-plannen voor badkamer en/of keuken, warmte-verlies berekening van de installatie en het nodige professionele advies betreffende energiezuinige toepassingen. Zonnepanelen, zonneboilers, vloerverwarming, ventilatiesystemen met warmterecuperatie, en andere energiebesparende toepassingen zijn de laatste jaren niet meer weg te denken in de moderne woning. Vertommen staat voor SERVICE & KWALITEIT

Name: Newcastle Design
HQ Location: Ireland, Co. Wicklow, Rathnew, Charvey Way
Company description: Newcastle Design is Ireland’s premier kitchen design and interiors experts. We work with you from initial design to create your vision and build the perfect kitchen, living room, bathroom or bedroom. In addition to dealing directly with our design studio you can be assured that our materials are locally sourced in Ireland from high quality suppliers. We offer innovative range of products to suit all tastes and lifestyles. We aim to enhance our customers experience through a knowledgeable, friendly service and an environment of trust, that delivers a product that fits their requirements making their dreams a reality.

Name: Maes Inox
Company description: - YOUR KITCHEN, YOUR CANVAS - Koken is creëren. Experimenteren en perfectioneren. Met een ongebreidelde passie ontwerpt de Chef zijn signatuurgerecht. Exclusief, kunstzinnig en een tikkeltje rebels. Koken is kunst scheppen. Dat kan alleen in een state-of-the-art keuken, volledig op maat van de Chef en zijn team.  - BEN MARTIN -  Met een Ben Martin fornuis plant je een krachtig, multifunctioneel en hightech inductiefornuis neer in je keuken. Maes Inox ontwikkelde dit fornuis in nauwe samenwerking met de beste chef-koks. Daarom bevat het de meest innovatieve technieken. Daarom ook getuigt het design van pure klasse. En uiteraard wordt elke Ben Martin op maat gemaakt in duurzaam RVS-inox. - REFERENTIES - Hof van Cleve *** / BE The Jane ** / BE Pure C ** / NL La Grenouillere  ** / FR Noma ** / DK Vrijmoed	** / BE Boury ** / BE Seagrill ** / BE t Zilte ** / BE Nuance ** / BE Air Republic * / NL Berto * / BE La Villa Lorraine * / BE Sofitel / NL Hotel 27/ NL Door 73 / BE Metro Antwerpen / BE Mesa / BE	 Hotel August / BE Maste / BE Kasteelhoeve de Victorie / BE Blueness / NL De Brabohoeve / BE De Singel	/ BE Victor Bozar Cafe / BE Le Coq aux Champs / BE La Barrière de Transinne	/ BE L'autre Vie / BE	 Pulpo / BE Balthazar	/ BE Frites Atelier / BE

Name: RBH Roermond
Company description: RBH Roermond is in ruim een halve eeuw uitgegroeid tot een begrip in Limburg. Voor professional en particulier hebben wij een uitgebreid en professioneel assortiment aan bouwmaterialen, hout en gereedschappen.  Van droomkeukens en stijlvolle badkamers tot dakpannen en gevelstenen. Onze showroom van 2.000 m2 herbergt een ruim assortiment producten van topkwaliteit. Particulieren kunnen bij ons terecht om samen met onze adviseurs hun nieuwe keuken of badkamer samen te stellen.

Name: Construct Furniture Company Ltd.
Company description: Construct Furniture Co. Ltd is a well-established and trusted furniture and doors manufacturer with over 35 years of experience, proudly delivering quality craftsmanship across Europe, the UK, and the MENA region. Our extensive portfolio features custom-designed kitchens, bedrooms, home and office furniture, internal doors, security and fire-rated doors, as well as full-scale project solutions. We collaborate closely with clients to furnish commercial offices, retail outlets, hotels, and large-scale developments with tailored, functional, and stylish solutions. All our products are developed in-house by a dedicated team of designers and manufactured to internationally recognised benchmarks, proudly certified to ISO 9001:2015 standards for quality management. Whether you're envisioning a bespoke space or need support on a major development, we’re here to bring your project to life. Let’s create something exceptional—get in touch with us today.

Name: Coox GmbH
Company description: Under the name coox, we develop smart and innovative products for the kitchen, which are designed to make every day cooking easier. The “WUNDERFORM” (miracle pan) was the starting point, which is best known from the German TV show “Das Ding des Jahres” (The Thing of the Year”). In 2019, founders Marc Elsen and Ralf Scheel wowed the jury and the public with their groundbreaking invention. This positive response encouraged and motivated us to develop other problemsolving products. So, be inspired by our products and get in touch with us. We look forward to hearing from you!

Name: SmartDesign Keukenstudio
Company description: Slim in smaakvol ontwerp Wij vinden het belangrijk dat u weloverwogen een keuze kunt maken voor uw keuken. Daarom bent u bij ons van harte welkom om rustig te kijken en vragen te stellen zodat u zeker weet dat u de juiste keuze maakt. We zetten onze creativiteit in om lastige vraagstukken, eenvoudig op te lossen en daarbij tegelijkertijd het design te verbeteren. Waardoor u meer keuken krijgt voor minder geld. Dat is SmartDesign. Slim en smaakvol. Graag tot ziens in het SmartDesign center in Maassluis.

Name: Goergen Keukens
Company description: Goergen Keukens staat al meer dan 90 jaar voor eerlijkheid en transparantie op alle fronten. Graag bieden wij u een persoonlijk advies en kijken we graag mee naar slimme – en financieel aantrekkelijke – oplossingen. Samen met u achterhalen wij uw specifieke wensen en inventariseren we de leefsituatie bij u thuis. Ontzorgen staat altijd centraal, van het maken van het 3D-ontwerp tot en met het realisatieproces. Bij ons is alles mogelijk. Wij worden graag uitgedaagd!

Name: Bokmerk BV
HQ Location: Netherlands, South Holland, Alphen Aan Den Rijn
Company description: Bokmerk is in 2010 opgericht door Marcel Bok. Mede door zijn achtergrond in staal- en aluminium coating kwam hij op het idee om de traditionele industriële toepassingen uit te breiden naar mogelijkheden voor particulieren. Het duurzame aluminium, mits voorzien van een beschermende coating, leent zich uitstekend voor gebruik in omgevingen waar vocht voorkomt, zoals keukens en badkamers. Daarbij kan de coating in elke denkbare kleur worden aangebracht. Zo past een achterwand van Bokmerk in elk interieur. Het succes van een Bokmerk achterwand is niet onopgemerkt gebleven. Zo zijn onze achterwanden nu exclusief verkrijgbaar in meer dan 700 keukenspeciaalzaken in heel Nederland, België en ver daarbuiten.

Name: DB Adee Keukens
Company description: Wanneer je een keuken koopt bij Adee Keukens in Rijssen, dan vallen een paar dingen op. De zorgvuldigheid en aandacht waarmee de medewerkers met hun klanten omgaan. En de grote betrokkenheid van de personeelsleden bij hun werk. En dat moet ook wel, want elke keuken is persoonlijk. Tot in de details bekijken we tijdens het verkooptraject waar uw wensen liggen. En dat proberen we zo goed mogelijk ten uitvoer te brengen. Gemiddeld genomen duurt de aankoop van een keuken bij Adee Keukens misschien net iets langer. Maar dan weet u wel, dat u voor uw persoonlijke situatie de beste van de beste keus hebt! Tenslotte koop je een keuken hoogstens een paar keer in je leven. Bij Adee Keukens begrijpen we dat. Daarom nemen we uitgebreid de tijd om u perfect en persoonlijk te begeleiden. Dat klanten onze werkwijze waarderen blijkt wel uit de hoge klantcijfers die zij geven.

Name: Image Keukens
HQ Location: Netherlands, South Holland, Oud-beijerland, 4 Willem Beukelszstraat, 3261
Company description: Welcome to Image Keukens, the region's leading kitchen supplier for 28 years. And just a little over a year ago, we opened our second location in Bussum! Our experienced specialists are familiar with all the ins and outs of kitchens. You'll find kitchens in all shapes, styles, and sizes. Whether you prefer a rustic, traditional, authentic, or sleek, modern kitchen... We offer something for everyone. Our extensive collection includes kitchens for budget-conscious buyers and exclusive, custom-made kitchens. We take the time to understand your personal needs and are happy to advise you on purchasing your dream kitchen. Our fitters will then ensure professional installation. You can also contact us for the renovation of your existing kitchen. Come visit us and be inspired by the world of Image Keukens

Name: Tinello Keuken & Interieur
Company description: Tinello is een toonaangevende specialist op het gebied van landelijke maatwerk-keukens. Onze ontwerpen vallen op door eigentijds design met de warmte van natuurlijke materialen. Landelijke, moderne, klassieke keukens maken we van de eerste schets tot de laatste kwaststreek helemaal naar uw wens. Zo creëren wij samen met u een persoonlijke keuken die het hart van uw huis is. Wij zien u graag in onze showroom waar u persoonlijk de Tinello-sfeer en gastvrijheid beleeft.

Name: Dengo Keukens
Company description: Dengo ontwerpt, fabriceert en installeert keukens, kasten en interieurs voor klanten uit de institutionele en zakelijke markt. Grote aantallen, bijzondere afwerkingen, afwijkende maatvoeringen, speciale eisen aan ergonomie: in maatwerk zit onze expertise.  Onze platte organisatie en het geautomatiseerde productieproces zorgen voor flexibiliteit en korte levertijden. Doordat keukens in eigen huis worden geproduceerd bieden wij volledig vrije ontwerpkeuze. Uiteraard kunnen de particuliere klanten ook bij ons terecht. Kijk op www.dengo.nl voor meer informatie!

Name: Fred Constant
Company description: FRED CONSTANT: DESIGN DAT LEEFT Fred Constant maakt unieke designs met een eigen persoonlijkheid. Bijzondere keukens, complete interieurs en markante woonproducten, zoals meubels. We werken met robuuste, massieve en natuurlijke materialen, en streven naar een tijdloos resultaat dat blijvend waarde toevoegt aan uw leven. U bent van harte welkom voor een bezoek aan Assendelft, waar al onze designs met de hand worden vervaardigd. Met een hecht team werkt Fred Constant aan bijzonder design voor u. We doen dit vanuit een karakteristiek oud-industrieel pand in Assendelft. Hier vindt u onze showroom, onze werkplaats en onze roots: we zijn hier gevestigd sinds 2000. Wanneer u Fred Constant vraagt om u te helpen met uw keuken of interieur, of voor het ontwerp van bijvoorbeeld een tafel, dan komt u in aanraking met onze geheel eigen aanpak. Onderdeel daarvan is dat we loyaal zijn richting onze opdrachtgevers. We werken met u samen. Geen stunts, maar eerlijke offertes en goede afspraken. Clubgevoel Diezelfde eerlijkheid vindt u terug in onze werkplaats. Hier werken onze vaklieden met oog voor detail en liefde voor hun ambacht. En ons pand mag er dan uit zien als een fabriek, wij zien het liever als een club, waar iedereen samenwerkt aan steeds betere prestaties, steeds mooiere resultaten.

Name: Lightstyle Kitchen
Company description: Our Lightstyle team strives to provide the highest level of design services, product selection, and meticulous attention to the details of your project. We tailor our services to meet your needs. We feature state-of-the-art showrooms in the cities of Prague, České Budějovice, Bratislava, and Miami. Regardless of your budget or needs, Lightstyle carefully listens to you and collaborates with you in shaping ideas for a new and improved space. Whether you already have specific details firmly in mind, or need our design expertise to help you create an overall concept, our team will walk you through the entire process. Every project is important to us at Lightstyle, and we look forward to sharing our enthusiasm with you as we help you design a new kitchen, living room, or any space where our furniture will make your life easier. We believe that building relationships is one of the things we do best. It’s a great foundation for the rest of the process. Lightstyle will design and create a home for you that is not only beautiful and functional but also fulfills our promise of value.

Name: HL-TopMix
Company description: At HL-TopMix, we mix more than just feed – we mix expertise, innovation, and care. As a Bulgarian-German company, we craft high-quality animal nutrition products and raw materials for farms of all sizes. Whether you run your own feed kitchen or need a ready-made solution, we're here to help you grow healthy animals and a successful business.

Name: INKO
Company description: At INKO, we have been manufacturing high-quality kitchens since 1999, combining innovation, sustainability, and functionality to offer unique solutions for every home. Our 12,000 m² factory in Coín, Málaga, produces approximately 7,000 kitchens annually, designed with the latest technology and the precision of traditional craftsmanship. We have a team of 140 professionals committed to excellence and a network of over 200 distributors in 11 countries, consolidating our presence in both national and international markets. Sustainability is a fundamental pillar at INKO. All our kitchens are made from 100% recyclable raw materials and components, and 25% of the energy used in our production comes from photovoltaic sources, reducing our environmental impact and contributing to a more responsible future. With more than 25 years of experience, we continue to move forward with the same passion, helping to transform spaces into places where life and inspiration meet. INKO, creating spaces, transforming lives.

Name: Grupo Acb
Company description: Empresa fabricante de puertas, modulos y complementos para mobiliario de cocina. todo tipo de diseños y modelos de puertas con un amplio abanico en la variedad de colores. Sitio Web                                                              Sociedad de financiazion privada www.grupoacb.com                                          Numero de empleados entre 25-50   Redes sociales en: Facebook y Linkedin

Name: BIRGIT MÜLLER COCINA Y VIDA
Company description: Die Küche ist das Herz des Hauses. Deshalb sollten Sie besonderen Wert auf die Auswahl Ihrer Küche legen. Unsere exklusiven Küchenwelten stehen für unterschiedliche Einrichtungsstile, aber einen gemeinsamen hohen Anspruch. Das Know-how und die Erfahrung aus drei Generationen innovativer Küchengestaltung garantieren dafür, dass wir für Sie in unseren Küchenstudios - in Palma und Port d’Andratx auf Mallorca - die optimale Küche entwickeln.

Name: Iturria Industrial S.l
HQ Location: Spain, Basque Country, Irun/irún, Ezurriki Kalea, 20303
Company description: ITURRIA es una empresa familiar creada en 1929 dedicada al suministro al por mayor de materiales de construcción , cerámica , cocinas , baños , jardin, madera y ferretería . Hoy en día ITURRIA se encuentra con una 4º generación trabajando bajo su techo, para mantener a la empresa, día a día en la cultura de la innovación y la renovación interna, la misma cultura que le ha mantenido viva durante 89 años. ITURRIA cuenta hoy con unas instalaciones de 20.000m2 y su gama de productos, muy lejos de verse limitada a la venta de materiales de construcción , se encuentra en un imparable proceso de crecimiento, ofreciendo prácticamente todos los productos relacionados el acondicionamiento del hogar.

Name: Nordic Tech
Company description: På Nordic Tech brinner vi för att lyfta kökets samlingsplats med högkvalitativa lösningar. Vi erbjuder ett brett utbud av rostfria diskbänkar, diskhoar, blandare och andra kökstillbehör – designade för att hålla i generationer. Våra produkter kombinerar tidlös estetik med robust funktionalitet och tillverkas med stor omsorg för detaljer.  Vi samarbetar med återförsäljare över hela Sverige, såsom köksbutiker, bygghandlare, designers och bänktillverkare, för att ge dig det bästa inom köksdesign. Oavsett om du söker en klassisk eller modern stil kan du hitta måttanpassade lösningar som passar just ditt hem.  Med ett starkt fokus på innovation och kvalitet vill vi inspirera och hjälpa dig att skapa ett personligt kök där varje detalj räknas.   Välkommen till Nordic Tech – där design och hållbarhet möts!

Name: Moebelplus Deutschland GmbH & Co KG
Company description: moebelplus Deutschland GmbH & Co KG agiert in einer zukunftssicheren Branche: Der Onlinehandel ist ein stetig wachsender Markt mit ausgezeichneten Perspektiven. Wir sind ein modernes, schnell wachsendes Unternehmen mit zahlreichen Möglichkeiten zur persönlichen Entfaltung und Entwicklung. Hochwertige Elektro-Geräte im Küchen- und Haushaltsbereich sind unser Kerngeschäft und alles rund um’s Thema Küche ist unsere Leidenschaft. Das hauseigene SieMatic-Küchenstudio und angeschlossene Lager bieten zudem Spielräume zur kreativen und tatkräftigen Entfaltung.

Name: KH System Möbel GmbH
HQ Location: Germany, Lower Saxony, Melle, 46-48 Spenger Straße, 49328
Company description: KH SYSTEM MÖBEL is located in Melle-Bruchmühlen, Lower Saxony, the centre of the German kitchen furniture industry. As a family business, we have a keen sense of responsibility and commitment to our tradition, and stand for reliability, ensuring lasting success because we think of the future today.

Name: Rubinetteria Bugnatese Srl
HQ Location: Italy, Novara, Gozzano, 111 Via Carlo Rolando, 28024
Company description: Ogni rubinetto è in grado di raccontare una storia fatta di passione, competenza e design. Soluzioni innovative per ogni tuo ambiente di casa: dal bagno alla cucina. Rubinetteria Bugnatese, dal 1950, produce soluzioni innovative per i tuoi spazi.

Name: Copatlife
HQ Location: Italy, Pordenone, Fontanafredda, 11/a Via E. Chiaradia, 33074
Company description: Copatlife è un brand italiano specializzato nella realizzazione di cucine di design che rivolge le sue attenzioni principalmente al mondo del progetto. Copatlife è tra i brand più giovani ad affacciarsi nel mondo cucina italiano: dal 2014 ha saputo esprimere un’identità forte e riconoscibile nel mondo del design. I plus di Copatlife sono un’ampia offerta, riconoscibile ed identitaria, racchiusa in un unico grande sistema cucina, che consente una grande adattabilità del progetto in un’ottica smart.

Name: Report Srl
HQ Location: Italy, Veneto, Gaiarine, 6 Viale Delle Industrie, 31018
Company description: Siamo a fianco di designer e aziende del mondo dell’arredamento per la progettazione, produzione e fornitura just in time di piani, antine e altri elementi d’arredo per mobili cucina e bagno.

Name: Cova Cucine
HQ Location: Italy, Trento, Denno, 43 Via Alcide De Gasperi, 38010
Company description: Italian brand of kitchens. Designing and producing kitchen since 1821. 1821 was our birth-year, 2021 is the beginning of a new adventure. 200 years as a starting point, where tradition and know-how are combined and shown by 5th and 6th generation of Cova. We are solid, in ideas and materials we use. We are born in Non Valley and here we do what we have always been doing: we create kitchens. We decided to stay in this amazing valley and produce everything inside our factory: our strength. We coordinate 100% of the production of kitchens in Denno (Non Valley), where our factory was born and is growing with us. We are Industry and Craftmanship. We are like Stone, which is not ruined by aging. So did we. Since 1821 our factory went through the wise hands of our ancestors till ours, ready for the future.

Name: Flex Service Srl
Company description: Flex Service, specializzata nella produzione di elementi per mobili just-in-time dritti e sagomati, vanta l'esperienza e la potenzialità di creare arredi con ogni tipo di curvatura e con una vasta gamma di colori. La nostra forza principale è la lavorazione just-in-time sia dritta che sagomata, consegnando un prodotto finito ed imballato, che permette ai nostri clienti di eliminare costi di magazzino e di avere solo ciò che hanno venduto. Tutte le fasi di lavorazione del prodotto sono curate nei dettagli garantendo qualità e precisione. Con il nostro servizio ci rivolgiamo ad aziende che producono camere, uffici, bagni, cucine e designer, cercando di soddisfare pienamente tutte le esigenze dei nostri clienti. La nostra azienda, in collaborazione con la ditta Ecma Mobili Srl, è specializzata anche nel servizio di contract per hotel, residence, negozi, ristoranti, bar e per qualsiasi altro spazio che lo richieda.

Name: Kosmo Srl
Company description: Experts of the cooking universe: we are partners not just suppliers Every idea is an invaluable resource, a potentiality to be implemented. For this reason KOSMO likes to evaluate in depth all the possibilities and to realize them into new products, in which Italian design is combined with the research for the most advanced technologies to create modern hobs, customizable in every detail. Continually exploring new solutions that make the kitchen more elegant and functional, the company has been able to effectively respond to a specific requirement of the Market: food cooking by using high-performance appliances equipped with functional safety programmes and able to optimize consumption, by making the most of the natural energy power. Reinterpreting the culinary art with originality, KOSMO has given life to refined and innovative products. In more than twenty years of activity, it has launched on the Italian and international market numerous lines of gas, electric, glass-ceramic and induction hobs with high technological performances and an unmistakable style. KOSMO's partners are important manufacturers of home appliances and major dealers, looking for Made in Italy quality and extreme flexibility in production.

Name: Engel Küchenmontagen GmbH
Company description: Wir, die Engel Küchenmontagen GmbH, sind ein spezialisiertes Handwerksunternehmen mit über 22 Jahren Erfahrung in der Montage von Markenküchen namhafter Hersteller wie Nobilia, Nolte, Häcker, LEICHT, next125, TEAM 7 und Schüller. Gemeinsam mit unserem Team aus 72 Küchenmontage-Spezialisten unterstützen wir deutschlandweit mehr als 120 Küchenstudios bei der fachgerechten Montage von hochwertigen Küchen.

Name: Möbel Schulenburg GmbH & Co. KG
Company description: Möbel Schulenburg wurde 1921 von Rudolf Schulenburg in Hamburg-Wilhelmsburg gegründet und feiert in Kürze sein 100-jähriges Jubiläum. Möbel Schulenburg ist eines der größten Möbel-Einzelhandelsunternehmen in Norddeutschland und bietet mit seinen sechs Standorten ein Shopping-Konzept der Extraklasse, das den Einkauf für die ganze Familie zu einem besonderen Erlebnis werden lässt.  Mit seiner Riesenauswahl für jeden Geschmack, abwechslungsreichen Events und mit Qualität zu günstigen Preisen sowie exzellenten Serviceleistungen hat sich der Name Schulenburg im Bereich der Einrichtungszentren zu einer im Norden weithin bekannten und beliebten Marke entwickelt. Wir haben nahezu alles da, was die Welt der Einrichtungen bietet ­– von Möbeln für den kleinen Geldbeutel bis hin zu großen Marken. Wer zu uns kommt, wird schnell merken, dass er hier den Schulenburg-Slogan verwirklichen kann. Und der lautet: Wohn’ Dich glücklich!“ Bei uns finden Sie den Job, der zu Ihnen passt, ob als Einrichtungsberater im Bereich Möbel oder Küchen, in der Dekoration, als Möbel-oder Küchenmonteur, Mitarbeiter im Kundendienst, in der Verwaltung oder an der Kasse. Unser Jobangebot ist vielfältig und bietet auch Quereinsteigern viele Chancen. In unseren Möbelhäusern sorgt die wohnliche Atmosphäre für die richtige Wohlfühl-Umgebung, in der sich Mitarbeiter und Kunden gleichermaßen gerne aufhalten. Attraktive Verdienstmöglichkeiten durch leistungsorientierte Vergütung und viele Sozialleistungen sind für uns selbstverständlich. So macht das Arbeiten Spaß.

Name: Línea 3 Cocinas
HQ Location: Spain, Madrid, Ciempozuelos, 11 Avenida Del Instituto, 28002
Company description: En Línea 3 Cocinas estamos especializados en el diseño y reforma de cocinas, pero sobre todo, en ofrecer la mejor experiencia al cliente. Contamos dos showrooms, uno en el centro de Madrid y otro en la zona sur. Somos una empresa referente en el sector, con proyectos de innovación digital como nuestro canal de Youtube. Hemos ganando varios premios de diseño (en 2013, 2014, 2017 y 2019) en el evento de interiorismo más prestigioso de nuestro país - Casa Decor.

Name: Noriliving Digitaldruck GmbH
Company description: NORILIVING-pepeprint ist Ihr Experte für individuelle Wohn- und Interieur-Elemente im Premium-Segment. Über unseren Online-Handel bieten wir eine umfangreiche Auswahl an stilvollen Einrichtungselementen, wie Duschrückwände, Küchen-Spiegel, Wohn- und Schlafzimmer-Wanddesigns, die perfekt auf die Bedürfnisse stylischer Haushalte zugeschnitten sind.  Dabei beweist unsere Vielfalt an modernen, trendigen Designs unsere Kernkompetenz in Sachen optisch-hochwertiger Innenarchitektur und das für jeden Geschmack und jede Geldbörse. Von minimalistisch-monochromer Farbgebung, über farbenfrohe Fotos zu den verschiedensten Motiven bis hin zu opulenten Naturstein-Designs wie Schiefer, Granit- oder Marmor ist alles zu finden.  Unsere hochwertige Produktpalette zeichnet sich durch ihre schnelle Installation, Langlebigkeit, Schmutz-Resistenz wie auch einfache Reinigung aus.  Unser Fokus liegt dabei auf höchster Qualität und den besten Kundenservice! Im nationalen Vergleich bewegen wir uns unter den Top 3 der Marktführer, in bester Gesellschaft. Unsere Usability ist dabei ausschlaggebend, da wir den Individualismus unserer Kunden, durch unseren eigens hierfür entwickelten Konfigurator / Designer, optimal unterstützen möchten. Seit unserer Unternehmensgründung im Jahre 1968 ist unsere Unternehmensgruppe Partner des Handels. Mit der NORILIVING-pepeprint waren wir relevanter Partner von mehr als  20.000 privaten Renovierungen und vielen professionellen Wohnungsprojekten; deutschlandweit.  Designs nach Kunden-Geschmack, Innovationsführerschaft in der Gestaltung unserer Produktpalette, höchste Druckqualität und eine optimale Produktions-, Liefer- und Service-Geschwindigkeit.  NORILIVING-pepeprint ist Ihr Partner bei Renovierung oder Neubau. Unsere Partner sind Projektentwickler im Bereich: Hotels, sozialer Wohnungsbau, Wohnraum-Entwickler, Messebau u.v.m.

Name: LIEBLINGSGLAS
Company description: Lieblingsglas steht für hochwertige Gläser in deinem Alltag. Ob du Ordnung in deine Küche bringen und Vorräte luftdicht verstauen möchtest, in der Woche Zeit sparen dich aber trotzdem gesund ernähren willst oder du endlich planst dein eigenes Gemüse zu fermentieren und Sauerteig Brot zu backen. Alle Gläser sind multifunktional einsetzbar und dadurch ein Wegbegleiter fürs Leben, der sich an deine Bedürfnisse anpasst.  Lieblingsglas revolutioniert deinen Alltag, indem es dich mit langlebigen, multifunktionalen Gläsern und inspirierendem Content rund um Rezepte, Ordnungstipps und Ernährungswissen unterstützt. So wird deine Küche schöner, ordentlicher und effizienter gestaltet – für ein bewusstes Leben. Wir bei Lieblingsglas stehen nie still, haben immer neue Ideen und möchten, dass in jedem deutschen Haushalt mindestens ein Lieblingsglas im Schrank steht. Du möchtest uns bei dieser Reise begleiten? Das erwartet dich bei Lieblingsglas: 🌟 ZUSAMMEN STARK - Bei Lieblingsglas ermutigen wir aktiv jedes Teammitglied, mutige Entscheidungen zu treffen, und vertrauen darauf, dass ihre einzigartigen Fähigkeiten unsere gemeinsame Vision stärken. 🌟 KREATIVES DENKEN IM FOKUS - Unsere Kultur bei Lieblingsglas ermutigt dazu, aus der gewohnten Denkweise auszubrechen. Wir sind mutig, neugierig und begegnen unseren Projekten mit kreativen und innovativen Ansätzen. 🌟 NACHHALTIGKEIT  - Unsere langfristige Vision für eine nachhaltigere Zukunft ist der Kompass, der unser Denken und Handeln leitet. 🌟 HERZBLUT - Unsere Leidenschaft und Hingabe spiegeln sich in jedem Aspekt unserer Arbeit wider. Bei Lieblingsglas setzen wir uns mit Herzblut für unsere Mission ein, und das macht uns einzigartig. 🚀💚  Let's connect: Schicke deine Bewerbung an hello@lieblingsglas.de

Name: IXINA España

Company description: ¡Di sí a tu sueño de emprender con ixina! La cocina es el corazón de la casa y en ixina, es nuestra pasión. Fundada en Bélgica, instalada en Francia desde 1997 y con proyección internacional desde 2008, ixina se ha desarrollado en torno a un concepto muy simple: hacer asequibles y poner al alcance de todo el mundo cocinas equipadas de calidad con una política de ventas, transparencia y respeto por el cliente, presidida por el factor humano. La receta de nuestro éxito: una marca moderna y comprometida con un posicionamiento claro y una comunicación potente para crear notoriedad y tráfico, un concepto de tienda y productos en línea acorde con los tiempos y un acompañamiento pormenorizado.  Nuestro rendimiento está también y ante todo ligado a la fuerza de nuestras redes de franquicias que comparten con nosotros sólidos valores: pasión, hospitalidad y diálogo.  En 50 años, ixina se ha impuesto como un importante agente en el sector de las cocinas y como marca líder en Bélgica. Por eso, ahora, para instalar la marca ixina y posicionarnos como líderes en el mercado español, estamos deseosos de dar la bienvenida a nuevos colaboradores, altamente motivados, con los que compartir, cultivar y desarrollar nuestros valores. Los equipos de ixina están convencidos de que el desarrollo profesional tiene que ir de la mano de unas relaciones humanas sólidas, solo así es posible el éxito comercial.  ixina te ofrece un apoyo personalizado y óptimo, sostenido por nuestro equipo de animación comercial para mejorar las competencias y optimizar tu actividad comercial.

Name: Fratelli Frattini Rubinetterie S.P.A.
Company description: Da oltre cinquant’anni protagonista nel comparto delle rubinetterie sanitarie di elevata qualità, l’azienda deve la sua storia grazie alla straordinaria intuizione dei fratelli Frattini che hanno saputo conquistarsi la fiducia dei più qualificati operatori e di milioni di utilizzatori, in virtù di una costante attenzione alla qualità del prodotto e del servizio alla Clientela.  Nei moderni reparti di produzione, che si sviluppano su un’area di oltre 20.000 mq, trovano posto le più significative tecnologie che concorrono ad un processo produttivo caratterizzato da sistematici controlli di qualità in ogni fase della produzione.  La gamma dei prodotti, mirati al segmento alto del mercato, è molto vasta e si articola in numerose serie monocomando e rubinetteria tradizionale, alle quali fanno da corollario modelli speciali, monocomandi termostatici ed elettronici, rubinetteria da cucina ed accessori da bagno. Il processo produttivo certificato ISO 9001 e le più prestigiose omologazioni internazionali costituiscono un’ulteriore testimonianza di affidabilità dei prodotti contrassegnati dal prestigioso marchio Rubinetterie F.lli Frattini.  I rubinetti, per i Fratelli Frattini, non sono più semplici oggetti fini a se stessi, ma vere e proprie opere d’arte che possono far acquisire all’ambiente nel quale vengono  inseriti, un aspetto importante determinandone il gusto e la raffinatezza dell’utilizzatore finale, al giorno d'oggi, sempre più preparato ed attento ai particolari. La costante attenzione ai cambiamenti e la collaborazione con architetti e designers con lo studio progettazione interno all’azienda, ha dato vita a numerose serie di successo che hanno permesso di diventare una tra le aziende di maggior riferimento della rubinetteria sanitaria nazionale.  La passione per questo mestiere è la grande saggezza di quest’azienda che ora, anche attraverso la seconda generazione cerca di trasmettere a chi crede nella storia della F.lli Frattini e del prodotto MADE IN ITALY

Name: Topline Heavins & Euronics
HQ Location: Ireland, Leinster, Athlone, Shannon Retail Park Dublin Road, n37e763
Company description: Topline Heavins & Euronics is a family run business based in Athlone, Co.Westmeath. The story begins back in January 1984 when Willie and Maureen Heavin started a small Hardware Store at the McCormack Centre in Athlone. Then in the early 90s they moved 300 metres away to a 5000 sq ft premises employing over 10 people (a lot of whom were family members). Fast forward to the 19th May 2007 when we opened our doors to a 17,000 sq ft superstore in Shannon Retail Park beside Smyths Toys and currently employing over 20 people guided by Paul, Derek and Paulette. We are very customer focused and offer the personal experience compared to the big chains and we pride ourselves on customer service and range of products and services such as Flat Packed Kitchens, Paint and Decor Centre, Gardening, DIY and Tools, Electrical Appliances and loads more. As you can see from our videos on the Topline Heavins & Euronics Facebook Page we love what we do and plan on continuing our success into the future.

Name: Vismap Cucine
Company description: Vismap Cucine nasce nel 1977 a Treia (in provincia di Macerata, nelle Marche), a opera di alcuni "addetti ai lavori", che decidono di dare vita a una nuova realtà imprenditoriale in grado di produrre cucine d'arredamento. Prende così l'avvio un piccolo laboratorio che, grazie al grande impegno profuso e ai costanti investimenti realizzati (sia in innovazione di strutture e macchinari, che in risorse umane), diventa negli anni la Vismap di oggi. Oggi Vismap Cucine è un'azienda che si estende su di una superficie di oltre 9000 mq, con un grande show-room interno di 150 mq a disposizione dei clienti, che può contare su macchinari all'avanguardia (che consentono una produzione di alto livello qualitativo), nonché su di una struttura interna flessibile e organizzata (composta da un team di esperti professionisti) e su di una rete commerciale preparata e attenta ai mutamenti del mercato.

Name: I Falegnami S.r.l.
HQ Location: Italy, Mantova, Castellucchio Castellucchio, 16 Via Della Repubblica, 46014
Company description: > TRASLOCHI > SERVIZIO DEPOSITO > MONTAGGIO/SMONTAGGIO ARREDI > FALEGNAMERIA SU MISURA > RESTAURO > MOVIMENTAZIONE/TRASPORTO CONTO TERZI I Falegnami sono un team consolidato di professionisti che vanta un’esperienza pluriennale nel campo dei traslochi (casa, ufficio, negozio), nel montaggio e smontaggio di mobili, nel montaggio e smontaggio di cucine, nel restauro e nel trasporto di opere d’arte e antiquariato. L‘azienda con sede a Castellucchio di Mantova si avvale di un laboratorio di falegnameria per effettuare qualsiasi tipo di adattamenti e modifiche su misura e di ampi magazzini per fornire un servizio deposito alla vostra merce. I Falegnami sono un Team di professionisti altamente qualificati con ottima esperienza sia nel coordinamento logistico che nel montaggio per svolgere lavori a regola d’arte. Prettamente in grado di gestire disegni tecnici e progetti architettonici, i falegnami intervengono con tempestività su tutta la provincia di Mantova, Verona e Cremona. L’azienda opera su larga scala in ogni settore: alberghi, negozi, stand fieristici, banche, uffici, cantieri navali e abitazioni private. I Falegnami svolgono un servizio di trasporto di complementi d’arredo conto terzi e opere d’arte. Si rivolgo principalmente ad aziende del settore: dovete effettuare un trasporto di complementi d’arredo, ma non disponete di mezzi di proprietà? Grazie ad un parco mezzi flessibile ed articolato, I Falegnami possono raggiungere qualsiasi destinazione, anche nei centri storici. Inoltre, I Falegnami credono nel valore dei ricordi di un elemento d’arredo recuperato. Restaurare significa fare riemergere la memoria dell’artigiano che ha lavorato all’oggetto prima di noi. I Falegnami con mani esperte restituiscono splendore ai vecchi complementi d’arredo, modernizzano porte e serramenti in legno e rigenerano vecchi tavoli e seggiole. www.ifalegnami.it info@ifalegnami.it Contattaci per un preventivo gratuito!

Company description: Euroedil dal 1983 all’interno dei punti vendita espone piastrelle, rivestimenti, arredamento, cucine e sanitari selezionando i prodotti delle migliori marche presenti sul mercato italiano ed internazionale.
